  <para style="mt1">MATHAYO</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Ibuku rĩa Mathayo rĩonanagia Jesũ arĩ we Mesia wa andũ a Isiraeli. Ũhoro ũrĩa ibuku rĩĩrĩ rĩheanaga ũhutĩtie maũndũ marĩa Jesũ eekaga, ta kũhonania, na kũingata ndaimono, o na maũndũ marĩa aarutanaga. Maũndũ marĩa aarutanaga maarĩ ta: ndũmĩrĩri ya Jesũ arĩ Kĩrĩma-inĩ (5–7), na ngerekano ikoniĩ ũthamaki wa igũrũ (13). Ũndũ ũmwe wĩkĩrĩirwo thĩinĩ wa ibuku rĩa Mathayo nĩ atĩ Ngai nĩendaga andũ ake mamwathĩkĩre.</para>
  <para style="ip">Jesũ nĩahũthĩrire ũhoro ũyũ rĩrĩa eerire Johana Mũbatithania atĩrĩ, “Reke gũtuĩke ũguo rĩu, tondũ nĩtwagĩrĩirwo twĩke ũndũ ũyũ nĩguo tũhingie maũndũ mothe ma ũthingu” (3:15). Ningĩ Jesũ akĩrutana arĩ Kĩrĩma-inĩ nĩaririe maita matano ũrĩa andũ maagĩrĩirwo nĩ gwĩka nĩguo mamwathĩkĩre (5:6, 10, 20; 6:1, 33). Marigĩrĩrio-inĩ Jesũ nĩaririkanirie athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene hamwe na anene a andũ atĩrĩ, “Nĩgũkorwo Johana okire kũrĩ inyuĩ amuonie njĩra ya ũthingu.”</para>
  <para style="ip">Maandĩko ma Kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa Gĩkũrũ maarĩ ma bata mũno harĩ andũ a Isiraeli, na nĩkĩo Mathayo aamahũthagĩra kuonania atĩ Jesũ nĩwe Mesia ũrĩa watũmĩtwo nĩ Ngai. Mathayo aarĩkĩrĩirie ũhoro wake na ciugo iria Jesũ eerire arũmĩrĩri ake ũrĩa magĩrĩirwo nĩ gwĩka aamatiga.</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="im">Ibuku rĩrĩ rĩandĩkirwo nĩ Mathayo.</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Mũtũũrĩre wa Jesũ wa kĩambĩrĩria-inĩ, na ũtungata wake <char style="ior"><ref loc="MAT 1:1-4:25">1:1–4:25</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mahunjio ma Jesũ arĩ Kĩrĩma-inĩ <char style="ior"><ref loc="MAT 5:1-7:29">5:1–7:29</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Ũrutani, na ngerekano, na ndeereti <char style="ior"><ref loc="MAT 8:1-18:35">8:1–18:35</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Rũgendo rwa gũthiĩ Jerusalemu, na gũtaarwo kwa mũthia <char style="ior"><ref loc="MAT 19:1-23:39">19:1–23:39</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Morathi ma maũndũ marĩa magooka <char style="ior"><ref loc="MAT 24:1-25:46">24:1–25:46</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Gũkua na kũriũka kwa Jesũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="MAT 26:1-28:20">26:1–28:20</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Rũciaro rũrĩa Jesũ Oimire</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 9:6">Isa 9:6</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 9:7">7</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 11:1">11:1</ref>; <ref loc="JER 23:5">Jer 23:5</ref>, <ref loc="JER 23:6">6</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 22:18">Kĩam 22:18</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 3:16">Agal 3:16</ref></char>
    </note>Maya nĩ maandĩko makoniĩ rũciaro rũrĩa Jesũ Kristũ, mũrũ wa Daudi, mũrũ wa Iburahĩmu oimire:</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 25:26">Kĩam 25:26</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 29:35">Kĩam 29:35</ref></char>
    </note>Iburahĩmu aarĩ ithe wa Isaaka,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Isaaka aarĩ ithe wa Jakubu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Jakubu aarĩ ithe wa Juda na ariũ a ithe,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 38:27-30">Kĩam 38:27-30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>nake Juda aarĩ ithe wa Perezu na Zera, arĩa nyina wao aarĩ Tamaru,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Perezu aarĩ ithe wa Hezironi,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Hezironi aarĩ ithe wa Ramu,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>nake Ramu aarĩ ithe wa Aminadabu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Aminadabu aarĩ ithe wa Nahashoni,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Nahashoni aarĩ ithe wa Salimoni,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 11:31">Ahib 11:31</ref>
      </char>
    </note>nake Salimoni aarĩ ithe wa Boazu, ũrĩa nyina aarĩ Rahabu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Boazu aarĩ ithe wa Obedi, ũrĩa nyina aarĩ Ruthu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Obedi aarĩ ithe wa Jesii,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 16:1">1Sam 16:1</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 12:24">2Sam 12:24</ref></char>
    </note>nake Jesii aarĩ ithe wa Mũthamaki Daudi.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">Daudi aarĩ ithe wa Solomoni, ũrĩa nyina aarĩ mũtumia wa Uria,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>nake Solomoni aarĩ ithe wa Rehoboamu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Rehoboamu aarĩ ithe wa Abija,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Abija aarĩ ithe wa Asa,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>nake Asa aarĩ ithe wa Jehoshafatu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Jehoshafatu aarĩ ithe wa Joramu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Joramu aarĩ ithe wa Uzia,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>nake Uzia aarĩ ithe wa Jothamu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Jothamu aarĩ ithe wa Ahazu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Ahazu aarĩ ithe wa Hezekia,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 20:21">2Ath 20:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>nake Hezekia aarĩ ithe wa Manase,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Manase aarĩ ithe wa Amoni,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Amoni aarĩ ithe wa Josia,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 24:14-16">2Ath 24:14-16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>nake Josia aarĩ ithe wa Jekonia na ariũ a ithe, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ maatahirwo, magĩtwarwo Babuloni.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CH 3:17">1Maũ 3:17</ref>, <ref loc="1CH 3:19">19</ref></char>
    </note>Thuutha wa gũtahwo, magĩtwarwo kũu Babuloni:</para>
  <para style="li2">Jekonia aarĩ ithe wa Shealitieli,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Shealitieli aarĩ ithe wa Zerubabeli,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>nake Zerubabeli aarĩ ithe wa Abihudu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Abihudu aarĩ ithe wa Eliakimu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Eliakimu aarĩ ithe wa Azoro,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>nake Azoro aarĩ ithe wa Zadoku,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Zadoku aarĩ ithe wa Akimu,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Akimu aarĩ ithe wa Eliudi,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>nake Eliudi aarĩ ithe wa Eleazaru,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Eleazaru aarĩ ithe wa Maathani,</para>
  <para style="li2">nake Maathani aarĩ ithe wa Jakubu,</para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 1:27">Luk 1:27</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:17">Math 27:17</ref></char>
    </note>nake Jakubu aarĩ ithe wa Jusufu, mũthuuri wa Mariamu, ũrĩa waciarire Jesũ, ũrĩa wĩtagwo Kristũ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Ũguo nĩ kuuga njiaro ciothe ciarĩ ikũmi na inya kuuma Iburahĩmu nginya Daudi, na njiaro ikũmi na inya kuuma Daudi nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ maatahirwo magĩtwarwo kũu Babuloni, na ningĩ njiaro ikũmi na inya kuuma hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ maatahirwo nginya hĩndĩ ya Kristũ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Kristũ nĩ kuuga “Ũrĩa Mũitĩrĩrie maguta”; Kĩhibirania nĩ Mesia.</char></note></para>
  <para style="s1">Gũciarwo kwa Jesũ Kristũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 1:35">Luk 1:35</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ũhoro wa gũciarwo kwa Jesũ Kristũ watariĩ ũũ: Nyina Mariamu nĩ oorĩtio nĩ Jusufu atuĩke mũtumia wake, no matanaikarania-rĩ, nĩamenyekire atĩ arĩ na nda ya Roho Mũtheru. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 24:1">Gũcook 24:1</ref></char></note>Nake Jusufu mũthuuri wake tondũ aarĩ mũndũ mũthingu na ndangĩendire kũmũconorithia kũrĩ andũ, agĩĩciiria amũtige na hitho.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 5:19">Atũm 5:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:19">Math 27:19</ref></char>
    </note>No thuutha wa gwĩciiria ũndũ ũcio, mũraika wa Mwathani akĩmuumĩrĩra kĩroto-inĩ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Jusufu, mũrũ wa Daudi, ndũkae gwĩtigĩra kũhikia Mariamu atuĩke mũtumia waku, tondũ nda ĩyo arĩ nayo nĩ ya Roho Mũtheru. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 1:31">Luk 1:31</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 130:8">Thab 130:8</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 11:14">Arom 11:14</ref></char></note>Nĩagaciara kahĩĩ, nawe nĩũgagatua Jesũ, tondũ nĩwe ũkaahonokia andũ ake kuuma mehia-inĩ mao.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 2:15">Math 2:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, maũndũ macio mothe meekĩkire nĩguo ũrĩa Mwathani aarĩtie na kanua ka mũnabii ũhinge, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ, <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 7:14">Isa 7:14</ref></char></note>“Mũirĩtu gathirange nĩakagĩa nda na nĩagaciara kahĩĩ, nao magaagatua Imanueli” ũguo naguo ũgĩtaũrwo nĩ kuuga, “Ngai hamwe na ithuĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Jusufu ookĩrire, agĩĩka o ta ũrĩa mũraika wa Mwathani aamwathĩte, nake akĩinũkia Mariamu gwake mũciĩ, agĩtuĩka mũtumia wake. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 1:31">Luk 1:31</ref></char></note>No matiigana kũmenyana nginya rĩrĩa aaciarire mwana ũcio wa kahĩĩ. Nake Jusufu agĩtua mwana ũcio Jesũ.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gũceererwo nĩ Andũ Oogĩ-a-Njata</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 2:4-7">Luk 2:4-7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, thuutha wa Jesũ gũciarwo kũu itũũra-inĩ rĩa Bethilehemu bũrũri wa Judea, hĩndĩ ya mũthamaki wetagwo Herode, andũ Oogĩ-a-Njata moimĩte irathĩro magĩũka Jerusalemu, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:49">Joh 1:49</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 24:17">Ndar 24:17</ref></char></note>makĩũria atĩrĩ, “Ũrĩa ũciarĩtwo arĩ mũthamaki wa Ayahudi-rĩ, arĩ ha? Nĩtuonire njata yake mwena wa irathĩro, na nĩtũũkĩte kũmũhooya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Mũthamaki Herode aiguire ũguo, agĩtangĩka ngoro, o hamwe na andũ Jerusalemu othe. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Na aarĩkia gwĩta athĩnjĩri-Ngai<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Athĩnjĩri-Ngai maarĩ atongoria a mahooya ma Ayahudi, na nĩo maarutagĩra Ngai magongona.</char></note> arĩa anene othe, na arutani a watho hamwe, akĩmooria kũrĩa Kristũ aarĩ aciarĩrwo. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:42">Joh 7:42</ref></char></note>Makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ Bethilehemu, bũrũri wa Judea, nĩgũkorwo nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo nĩ mũnabii, akoiga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MIC 5:2">Mik 5:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“ ‘Nawe Bethilehemu, kũu bũrũri wa Juda,</para>
  <para style="q2">tiwe ũrĩa mũnini mũno wa aathani a Juda;</para>
  <para style="q1">tondũ thĩinĩ waku nĩgũkoima ũrĩa ũgaathanaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrĩa ũgaatuĩka mũrĩithi wa andũ akwa a Isiraeli.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nake Herode agĩĩta andũ acio Oogĩ-a-Njata na hitho, na agĩtuĩria kuuma kũrĩ o ihinda rĩrĩa njata ĩyo yoonekete. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Akĩmatũma Bethilehemu akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Thiĩi mũgatuĩrie wega ũhoro wa kaana kau. Mwarĩkia gũkoona mũũke mũũmenyithie, nĩgeetha o na niĩ thiĩ ngagaturĩrie ndu ndĩkahooe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nao maarĩkia kũigua ciugo cia mũthamaki magĩthiĩ, nayo njata ĩrĩa moonete irathĩro ĩkĩmatongoria nginya ĩkĩrũgama igũrũ rĩa harĩa kaana kau kaarĩ. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa moonire njata ĩyo, magĩkena gĩkeno kĩnene mũno. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 60:3">Isa 60:3</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 72:10">Thab 72:10</ref></char></note>Nao magĩtoonya nyũmba, na makĩona kaana karĩ na nyina Mariamu, magĩkainamĩrĩra, magĩkahooya. Magĩcooka makĩohora indo ciao cia goro, magĩkahe iheo cia thahabu, na ũbumba, na manemane.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ũbumba nĩ mahuti manungi wega macinagwo na mwaki. Manemane nĩ indo ithondekagwo na kĩndũ kĩhaana ta ũũkĩ wa gĩthaka, inungaga wega na nĩ cia goro mũno.</char></note> <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 11:7">Ahib 11:7</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:19">Math 27:19</ref></char></note>Na nĩ ũndũ wa gũkaanio na kĩroto matigacookere kwa Herode, magĩcooka bũrũri wao magereire njĩra ĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũũrĩra Bũrũri wa Misiri</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 5:19">Atũm 5:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:19">Math 27:19</ref>; <ref loc="REV 12:4">Kũg 12:4</ref></char>
    </note>Maarĩkia gũthiĩ-rĩ, mũraika wa Mwathani akiumĩrĩra Jusufu kĩroto-inĩ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ũkĩra woe kaana gaka na nyina mũũrĩre Misiri. Ikarai kũu nginya rĩrĩa ngaakwĩra, nĩgũkorwo Herode nĩegũcaria kaana kau akoorage.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, agĩũkĩra, akĩoya kaana na nyina ũtukũ, magĩthiĩ Misiri, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HOS 11:1">Hos 11:1</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 4:22">Thaam 4:22</ref>, <ref loc="EXO 4:23">23</ref></char></note>kũrĩa maikarire nginya rĩrĩa Herode aakuire. Na nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ũhoro ũrĩa Mwathani oigĩte na kanua ka mũnabii ũkĩhinga, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ, “Ndeetire mũrũ wakwa oime bũrũri wa Misiri.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Herode aamenyire atĩ nĩaheenirio nĩ Oogĩ-a-Njata, akĩrakara mũno, akĩruta watho wa kũũraga tũhĩĩ tuothe kũu Bethilehemu na kũrĩa gũkuhĩ nakuo, tũrĩa twarĩ na ũkũrũ wa mĩaka ĩĩrĩ gũcooka na thĩ, kũringana na ihinda rĩrĩa eerĩtwo nĩ Oogĩ-a-Njata. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 1:22">Math 1:22</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo ũhoro ũrĩa waarĩtio na kanua ka mũnabii Jeremia ũkĩhinga, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 31:15">Jer 31:15</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 35:19">Kĩam 35:19</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũgambo nĩwaiguirwo kũu Rama,</para>
  <para style="q2">kĩrĩro na gũcakaya kũnene,</para>
  <para style="q1">Rakeli akĩrĩrĩra ciana ciake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akarega kũhoorerio, tondũ itirĩ ho.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũcooka Nazarethi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 5:19">Atũm 5:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:19">Math 27:19</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, Herode akua-rĩ, mũraika wa Mwathani akiumĩrĩra Jusufu kĩroto-inĩ kũu Misiri, <verse number="20" style="v"/>akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ũkĩra, woe kaana gaka na nyina, mũthiĩ bũrũri wa Isiraeli, nĩgũkorwo arĩa maageragia gũkooraga nĩmakuĩte.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, agĩũkĩra, akĩoya kaana na nyina, magĩthiĩ bũrũri wa Isiraeli. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 2:12">Math 2:12</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 2:13">13</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 2:19">19</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 2:39">Luk 2:39</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa aiguire atĩ Arikelau nĩwe wathamakaga Judea handũ ha ithe Herode, agĩĩtigĩra gũthiĩ kuo. Na aarĩkia gũkaanio kĩroto-inĩ-rĩ, agĩthiĩ bũrũri wa Galili, <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 1:24">Mar 1:24</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 1:45-46">Joh 1:45-46</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 1:13">Luk 1:13</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 1:57-66">57-66</ref></char></note>agĩthiĩ gũtũũra itũũra rĩĩtagwo Nazarethi. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ũhoro ũrĩa waarĩtio na tũnua twa anabii ũkĩhinga, rĩrĩa moigire atĩrĩ, “Nĩageetagwo Mũnazari.”</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Johana Mũbatithania Kũhaarĩria Njĩra</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 3:2-19">Luk 3:2-19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Matukũ-inĩ macio Johana ũrĩa Mũbatithania nĩokire, akĩhunjagia kũu Werũ-inĩ wa Judea, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:17">Math 4:17</ref></char></note>akiugaga atĩrĩ, “Mwĩrirei, nĩgũkorwo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩũkuhĩrĩirie.” <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 40:3">Isa 40:3</ref></char></note>Ũyũ nĩwe ũrĩa ũhoro wake waarĩtio nĩ mũnabii Isaia rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Kũrĩ na mũgambo wa mũndũ ũkwanĩrĩra werũ-inĩ, akoiga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">‘Haarĩriai njĩra ya Mwathani,</para>
  <para style="q2">rũngariai njĩra ciake.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TH 1:8">2Athe 1:8</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 11:22">Alaw 11:22</ref></char>
    </note>Johana eekagĩra Nguo ya guoya wa ngamĩĩra, na nĩeyohaga mũcibi wa rũũa njohero. Irio ciake ciarĩ ngigĩ na ũũkĩ wa gĩthaka. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nao andũ nĩmathiiaga kũrĩ we moimĩte Jerusalemu, na mĩena yothe ya Judea, na bũrũri wothe ũrĩa wariganĩtie na Jorodani. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Moimbũraga mehia mao, nake akamabatithĩria Rũũĩ-inĩ rwa Jorodani.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 12:34">Math 12:34</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 23:33">23:33</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 1:18">Arom 1:18</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩa oonire Afarisai na Asadukai<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Afarisai na Asadukai ciarĩ ikundi igĩrĩ cia atongoria a ndini ya Ayahudi itaiguanaga. Asadukai matietĩkĩtie ũhoro wa kũriũka kana wa araika.</char></note> aingĩ magĩũka hau nĩgeetha amabatithie, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ rũciaro rũrũ rwa nduĩra! Nũũ ũmũheete ũhoro atĩ mũũrĩre marakara marĩa makiriĩ gũũka? <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 26:20">Atũm 26:20</ref></char></note>Ciarai maciaro maringaine na kwĩrira. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 3:8">Luk 3:8</ref></char></note>Na mũtikeĩĩre na ngoro cianyu atĩrĩ, ‘Ithe witũ nĩ Iburahĩmu.’ Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, Ngai no atũme mahiga maya matuĩke ciana cia Iburahĩmu. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 7:19">Math 7:19</ref></char></note>Ithanwa nĩrĩige itina-inĩ cia mĩtĩ, na mũtĩ o wothe ũtaciaraga maciaro mega nĩũgatemwo, ũikio mwaki-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 4:4">Isa 4:4</ref>; <ref loc="1CH 1:8">1Maũ 1:8</ref></char>
    </note>“Niĩ ndĩmũbatithagia na maaĩ mwerira. No thuutha wakwa nĩgũgũũka mũndũ ũngĩ ũrĩ na hinya kũrĩ niĩ, na ndiagĩrĩire o na kũmũkuuĩra iraatũ ciake. We akaamũbatithagia na Roho Mũtheru na mwaki. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 13:30">Math 13:30</ref></char></note>Gĩtarũrũ gĩake akĩnyiitĩte na guoko, na nĩagatheria kĩhuhĩro gĩake, na acookanĩrĩrie ngano yake ikũmbĩ, acooke acine mahuti na mwaki ũtangĩhoreka.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũbatithio kwa Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akiuma Galili agĩthiĩ Rũũĩ-inĩ rwa Jorodani akabatithio nĩ Johana. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nowe Johana akĩgeria kũmũgiria, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Niĩ njagĩrĩirwo nĩkũbatithio nĩwe, nawe wagĩũka kũrĩ niĩ atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Reke gũtuĩke ũguo rĩu; tondũ nĩtwagĩrĩirwo twĩke ũndũ ũyũ nĩguo tũhingie maũndũ mothe ma ũthingu.” Hĩndĩ ĩyo Johana agĩĩtĩkĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 11:2">Isa 11:2</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 1:1">Ezek 1:1</ref></char>
    </note>Jesũ aarĩkia kũbatithio o ũguo-rĩ, akiumĩra maaĩ-inĩ. Kahinda o kau igũrũ rĩkĩhingũka, nake akĩona Roho wa Ngai agĩikũrũka ta ndutura, akĩũmba igũrũ rĩake. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 2:7">Thab 2:7</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:18">Math 12:18</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 9:35">Luk 9:35</ref></char></note>Naguo mũgambo ũkiuma igũrũ, ũkiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa, ũrĩa nyendete; na nĩngenaga mũno nĩ we.”</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Kũgerio kwa Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ nĩatongoririo nĩ Roho agĩtwarwo werũ-inĩ akagerio nĩ mũcukani. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1KI 19:8">1Ath 19:8</ref></char></note>Na aniina mĩthenya mĩrongo ĩna, ũtukũ na mũthenya, ehingĩte kũrĩa irio-rĩ, akĩigua ahũtiĩ. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 3:5">1Athe 3:5</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 3:17">Math 3:17</ref></char></note>Nake mũgerania akĩmũkora, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Angĩkorwo wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai-rĩ, ĩra mahiga maya matuĩke mĩgate.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 8:3">Gũcook 8:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: ‘To mũgate wiki ũngĩtũũria mũndũ muoyo, no nĩ kiugo gĩothe kĩrĩa kiumaga kanua ka Ngai.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NEH 11:1">Neh 11:1</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:53">Math 27:53</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo mũcukani akĩmũtwara itũũra rĩrĩa itheru, akĩmũrũgamia gathũrũmũndũ ka hekarũ, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 91:11">Thab 91:11</ref>, <ref loc="PSA 91:12">12</ref></char></note>akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Angĩkorwo wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai-rĩ, wĩgũithie thĩ. Nĩgũkorwo kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘Nĩagaatha araika ake nĩ ũndũ waku,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao nĩmagakwanĩrĩria na moko mao,</para>
  <para style="q1">nĩguo ndũkanahĩngwo kũgũrũ nĩ ihiga.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 6:16">Gũcook 6:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ningĩ nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: ‘Ndũkanagerie Mwathani Ngai waku.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Ningĩ mũcukani akĩmũtwara kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩraaya mũno, akĩmuonia mothamaki mothe ma thĩ na riiri wamo. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Maũndũ maya mothe nĩngũkũhe, ũngĩĩtĩkĩra kũnyinamĩrĩra ũũhooe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 6:13">Gũcook 6:13</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 16:23">Math 16:23</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Thiĩ Shaitani ndiga! Nĩgũkorwo nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: ‘Hooyaga Mwathani Ngai waku, na ũmũtungatagĩre o we wiki.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 22:43">Luk 22:43</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo mũcukani akĩmũtiga, nao araika magĩũka makĩmũtungatĩra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kwambĩrĩria Kũhunjia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ aiguire atĩ Johana nĩaikĩtio njeera-rĩ, agĩthiĩ Galili. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 1:21">Mar 1:21</ref></char></note>Akiuma Nazarethi, agĩthiĩ gũtũũra Kaperinaumu. Itũũra rĩu rĩarĩ hakuhĩ na iria, bũrũri-inĩ wa Zebuluni na Nafitali. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 1:22">Math 1:22</ref></char></note>Ũndũ ũcio wekĩkire nĩguo ũhoro ũrĩa waarĩtio na kanua ka mũnabii Isaia ũhinge, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>“Bũrũri wa Zebuluni, o na bũrũri wa Nafitali,</para>
  <para style="q2">njĩra ya gũthiĩ iria-inĩ, gũikũrũkania na Rũũĩ rwa Jorodani,</para>
  <para style="q2">kũu gwĩtagwo Galili-kwa-Ndũrĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 9:1">Isa 9:1</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 9:2">2</ref></char>
    </note>andũ arĩa matũũraga nduma-inĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩmonete ũtheri mũnene;</para>
  <para style="q1">nao arĩa matũũraga bũrũri ũrĩ kĩĩruru gĩa gĩkuũ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩmarĩirwo nĩ ũtheri.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:2">Math 3:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kuuma hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akĩambĩrĩria kũhunjia ũhoro akiugaga atĩrĩ, “Mwĩrirei, nĩgũkorwo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩũkuhĩrĩirie.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ gwĩta Arutwo ake a Mbere</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 7:1">Mar 7:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aaceeraga hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia Iria rĩa Galili, nĩonire andũ eerĩ a nyina ũmwe, nao nĩ Simoni ũrĩa wetagwo Petero, na mũrũ wa nyina Anderea. Maikagia neti iria-inĩ, nĩgũkorwo maarĩ ategi a thamaki. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 10:21">Mar 10:21</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 10:28">28</ref></char></note>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ũkai, mũnũmĩrĩre, na nĩngũmũtua ategi a andũ.” <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nao o rĩmwe magĩtiganĩria neti ciao, makĩmũrũmĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Na aathiathia akĩona andũ angĩ eerĩ a nyina ũmwe, Jakubu mũrũ wa Zebedi, na mũrũ wa nyina Johana. Maarĩ thĩinĩ wa gatarũ hamwe na ithe wao Zebedi makĩhaarĩria neti ciao. Nake Jesũ akĩmeeta, <verse number="22" style="v"/>na o rĩmwe magĩtiganĩria gatarũ na magĩtiga ithe wao, makĩmũrũmĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhonia Andũ Arũaru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 1:39">Mar 1:39</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 9:35">Math 9:35</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 1:14">Mar 1:14</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, Jesũ nĩathiire Galili guothe, akĩrutanaga thunagogi-inĩ ciao, akĩhunjagia Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega wa ũthamaki wa Ngai, na akĩhonagia andũ mĩrimũ yothe na ndwari ciothe iria maarĩ nacio. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 2:2">Luk 2:2</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 1:32">Mar 1:32</ref></char></note>Nayo ngumo yake ĩkĩhunjio bũrũri wothe wa Suriata, nao andũ makĩmũrehera andũ arĩa othe maarĩ arũaru ndwari cia mĩthemba mĩingĩ, na arĩa maarĩ na ruo rũingĩ, na arĩa maarĩ na ndaimono, na arĩa maarĩ na mũrimũ wa kũgũũaga, o na arĩa maarĩ na mũrimũ wa gũkua ciĩga, nake akĩmahonia othe. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 3:7">Mar 3:7</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 3:8">8</ref></char></note>Nao andũ aingĩ mũno kuuma Galili, na Dekapoli,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:25 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Dekapoli nĩ kuuga “Matũũra Ikũmi.”</char></note> na Jerusalemu, na Judea, na mũrĩmo ũũrĩa ũngĩ wa Rũũĩ rwa Jorodani makĩmũrũmĩrĩra.</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Irathimo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ oonire andũ aingĩ mũno-rĩ, akĩambata kĩrĩma-igũrũ, agĩikara thĩ. Arutwo ake magĩthiĩ harĩ we. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Nake akĩambĩrĩria kũmaruta ũhoro, akĩmeera atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>“Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa athĩĩni ngoro,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 61:2">Isa 61:2</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 61:3">3</ref></char>
    </note>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa marĩ na kĩeha,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo nĩmakaniinĩrwo kĩeha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 37:11">Thab 37:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa ahooreri,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo nĩmakagaya thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 55:1">Isa 55:1</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 55:2">2</ref></char>
    </note>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa mahũũtagĩra na makanyootera ũthingu,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo nĩmakahũũnio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa maiguanagĩra tha,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo nĩmakaiguĩrwo tha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 12:14">Ahib 12:14</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 24:3">Thab 24:3</ref>, <ref loc="PSA 24:4">4</ref></char>
    </note>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa atheru ngoro,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo nĩmakona Ngai.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 8:14">Arom 8:14</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:2">Jak 1:2</ref></char>
    </note>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa macaragia thayũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo nĩmagetwo ariũ a Ngai.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 3:14">1Pet 3:14</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 25:34">Math 25:34</ref></char>
    </note>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa manyariiragwo nĩ ũndũ wa ũthingu,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>“Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ inyuĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ mekũmũruma, na makamũnyariira, na makamũigĩrĩra maũndũ mothe mooru nĩ ũndũ wakwa. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Kenai na mũcanjamũke, tondũ kĩheo kĩanyu nĩ kĩnene igũrũ, nĩgũkorwo ũguo noguo maanyariirire anabii arĩa maarĩ kuo mbere yanyu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Cumbĩ na Ũtheri</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 9:50">Mar 9:50</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 14:34">Luk 14:34</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 14:35">35</ref></char>
    </note>“Inyuĩ nĩ inyuĩ cumbĩ wa thĩ. No cumbĩ ũngĩkorwo nĩũthirĩte mũcamo waguo-rĩ, ũngĩcooka gũcamithio ta cumbĩ nĩ kĩĩ? Ndũngĩcooka kũgĩa kĩene rĩngĩ, tiga no ũteirwo ũrangwo nĩ andũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:12">Joh 8:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Inyuĩ nĩ inyuĩ ũtheri wa thĩ. Itũũra inene rĩakĩtwo kĩrĩma igũrũ rĩtingĩhithĩka. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 4:21">Mar 4:21</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 8:16">Luk 8:16</ref></char></note>O na ningĩ andũ matiakagia tawa magacooka kũũkunĩkĩra na mbakũri; handũ ha ũguo, maũigagĩrĩra igũrũ handũ haguo, naguo ũkamũrĩkĩra andũ othe arĩa marĩ thĩinĩ wa nyũmba. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 10:31">1Akor 10:31</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 1:11">Afil 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="TIT 2:4">Tit 2:4</ref></char></note>O ũguo naguo, na inyuĩ rekei ũtheri wanyu ũmũrĩkagĩre andũ, nĩguo mone ciĩko cianyu njega, nao magoocage Ithe wanyu ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũhingia Watho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 10:34">Joh 10:34</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 3:31">Arom 3:31</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũtikae gwĩciiria njũkĩte kweheria Watho kana Mohoro ma Anabii; ndiũkĩte kũmeeheria, no njũkĩte kũmahingia. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 16:17">Luk 16:17</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa thĩ na igũrũ ikeehera, gũtirĩ kairia ka maandĩko, o na gũtirĩ gakururo kanini ga karamu gakeehera o na atĩa kuuma Watho-inĩ, nginya maũndũ mothe makaahingio. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 2:10">Jak 2:10</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe ũkoina rĩathani o na rĩmwe rĩa marĩa manini, na arute arĩa angĩ gwĩka ũguo, nĩagatuuo mũnini makĩria thĩinĩ wa ũthamaki wa igũrũ, no ũrĩa wothe wĩkaga na akarutana maathani maya-rĩ, nĩagatuuo mũnene ũthamaki-inĩ wa igũrũ. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, ũthingu wanyu waga gũkĩra ũrĩa wa Afarisai na wa arutani a watho, mũtigatoonya ũthamaki wa igũrũ o na atĩa.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũragani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 20:13">Thaam 20:13</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 5:14">Gũcook 5:14</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩmũiguĩte atĩ hĩndĩ ya tene andũ nĩmerirwo atĩrĩ, ‘Ndũkanoragane, na mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ũkooragana no nginya agaatuĩka wa gũtuĩrwo ciira.’ <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 3:15">1Joh 3:15</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 7:9">Koh 7:9</ref></char></note>No niĩ ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, ũrĩa wothe ũkarakarĩra mũrũ wa ithe nĩagatuĩka wa gũtuĩrwo ciira. Na ningĩ-rĩ, mũndũ ũrĩa wothe wĩraga mũrũ wa ithe atĩrĩ, ‘Wee ndũrĩ bata,’ nĩagaciirithio nĩ Kĩama. No ũrĩa wothe ũngiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Wee wĩ mũkĩĩgu!’ Nĩagakorwo arĩ ũgwati-inĩ wa gũikio mwaki-inĩ wa Jehanamu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, angĩkorwo nĩwĩhaarĩirie kũruta kĩheo gĩaku kĩgongona-inĩ, na hĩndĩ ĩyo ũrĩ hau ũririkane atĩ mũrũ wa thoguo arĩ na ũndũ nawe-rĩ, <verse number="24" style="v"/>tiga kĩheo gĩaku o hau mbere ya kĩgongona. Amba ũthiĩ ũkaiguane na mũrũ wa thoguo; ũcooke ũũke ũrutĩre Ngai kĩheo gĩaku.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>“Hiũha kwĩiguithania na thũ yaku ĩrĩa ĩragũtwara igooti-inĩ. Ĩka ũguo mũrĩ o njĩra-inĩ, kwaga ũguo nĩĩgũgũtwara kũrĩ mũtuanĩri-ciira, nake mũtuanĩri-ciira akũneane kũrĩ mũnene wa thigari, ũikio njeera. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ndũkoima kuo ũtarĩhĩte thiirĩ wothe hatarĩ gathendi ũgũtigia.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũtharia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 20:14">Thaam 20:14</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 5:18">Gũcook 5:18</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩmũiguĩte atĩ hĩndĩ ya tene nĩ kwerirwo atĩrĩ, ‘Ndũkanatharanie.’ <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 6:25">Thim 6:25</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 2:14">2Pet 2:14</ref></char></note>No niĩ ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, ũrĩa wothe ũkaarora mũndũ-wa-nja na amwĩrirĩrie, nĩarĩkĩtie gũtharia nake ngoro-inĩ yake. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 9:42-47">Mar 9:42-47</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 17:12">Luk 17:12</ref></char></note>Riitho rĩaku rĩa ũrĩo rĩngĩtũma wĩhie-rĩ, rĩkũũre, ũrĩte. Nĩ kaba kĩĩga kĩmwe kĩa mwĩrĩ waku kĩũre gũkĩra mwĩrĩ waku wothe ũikio Jehanamu. <verse number="30" style="v"/>Na guoko gwaku kwa ũrĩo kũngĩtũma wĩhie-rĩ, gũtinie ũgũte. Nĩ kaba kĩĩga kĩmwe kĩa mwĩrĩ waku kĩũre gũkĩra mwĩrĩ waku wothe ũikio Jehanamu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũtharia Ũhiki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 24:1-4">Gũcook 24:1-4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ningĩ nĩ kwĩrĩtwo atĩrĩ, ‘Ũrĩa wothe ũngĩtigana na mũtumia wake no nginya amũhe marũa ma kuonania nĩmatigana nake.’ <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 16:18">Luk 16:18</ref></char></note>No ngũmwĩra atĩ mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũtiganaga na mũtumia wake, o tiga nĩ ũndũ wa ũtharia-rĩ, nĩatũmaga atuĩke mũtharia, na ũrĩa wothe ũhikagia mũtumia ũrĩa ũtiganĩte na mũthuuriwe, nĩ gũtharia atharagia.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mĩĩhĩtwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 19:12">Alaw 19:12</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 30:2">Ndar 30:2</ref></char>
    </note>“Ningĩ, nĩmũiguĩte atĩ hĩndĩ ya tene andũ nĩmerirwo atĩrĩ, ‘Ndũkanehĩte tũhũ, no hingagĩria Mwathani mĩĩhĩtwa ĩrĩa wĩhĩtĩte.’ <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 5:12">Jak 5:12</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 66:1">Isa 66:1</ref></char></note>No ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mũtikanehĩte o na atĩa; mũtikanehĩte na igũrũ tondũ nĩkuo gĩtĩ kĩa ũnene kĩa Ngai; <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 48:2">Thab 48:2</ref></char></note>kana mwĩhĩte na thĩ, nĩgũkorwo nĩkuo gĩturwa gĩa kũigĩrĩra magũrũ make; o na kana mwĩhĩte na Jerusalemu, nĩgũkorwo nĩrĩo itũũra inene rĩa Mũthamaki mũnene. <verse number="36" style="v"/>Na ndũkanehĩte na mũtwe waku, nĩgũkorwo ndũngĩhota gũtũma rũcuĩrĩ o na rũmwe rwerũhe kana rũire. <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 5:12">Jak 5:12</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 6:16">Aef 6:16</ref></char></note>Reke ‘Ĩĩ’ yaku ĩtuĩke ‘Ĩĩ’, na ‘Aca’ yaku ĩtuĩke ‘Aca’; ũndũ o wothe makĩria ma ũguo-rĩ, uumaga kũrĩ ũrĩa mũũru.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũhoro wa Kwĩrĩhĩria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 21:24">Thaam 21:24</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 24:20">Alaw 24:20</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩmũiguĩte atĩ hĩndĩ ya tene nĩ kwerirwo atĩrĩ: ‘Riitho rĩrĩhagwo na riitho, narĩo igego rĩrĩhagwo na igego.’ <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 6:29">Luk 6:29</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 12:17">Arom 12:17</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 12:19">19</ref></char></note>No niĩ ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mũtikanagiane na mũndũ ũrĩa mũũru. No rĩrĩ, mũndũ angĩkũgũtha rũthĩa rwa ũrĩo-rĩ, mũhũgũkĩrie rũu rũngĩ o naruo. <verse number="40" style="v"/>Na mũndũ angĩenda gũgũthitanga oe kanjũ yaku-rĩ, mũnengere o na igooti rĩaku. <verse number="41" style="v"/>Mũndũ angĩkũhatĩrĩria ũthiĩ itĩĩna rĩmwe-rĩ, thiĩ nake matĩĩna meerĩ. <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 6:30">Luk 6:30</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 15:8">Gũcook 15:8</ref></char></note>Mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩkũhooya kĩndũ, mũhe, na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩenda ũmũkombere kĩndũ, ndũkarege kũmũkombera.</para>
  <para style="s1">Endagai Thũ Cianyu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:43 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 19:18">Alaw 19:18</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 23:6">Gũcook 23:6</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 139:21">Thab 139:21</ref>, <ref loc="PSA 139:22">22</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩmũiguĩte atĩ hĩndĩ ya tene nĩ kwerirwo atĩrĩ, ‘Endaga mũndũ wa itũũra rĩaku, na ũthũũrage thũ yaku.’ <verse number="44" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:44 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 6:27">Luk 6:27</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 6:28">28</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 7:60">Atũm 7:60</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 15:20">Joh 15:20</ref></char></note>No niĩ ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Endagai thũ cianyu, na mũhooyagĩre arĩa mamũnyariiraga, <verse number="45" style="v"/>nĩgeetha mũtuĩke ariũ a Ithe wanyu ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ. Atũmaga riũa rĩake rĩrathĩre arĩa ooru na arĩa ega, na akoiria mbura kũrĩ arĩa athingu na kũrĩ arĩa matarĩ athingu. <verse number="46" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:46 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 6:32">Luk 6:32</ref></char></note>Angĩkorwo mwendete o arĩa mamwendete-rĩ, mũgaakĩrĩhwo kĩ? Githĩ o na etia mbeeca cia igooti matiĩkaga o ũguo? <verse number="47" style="v"/>Na ningĩ angĩkorwo mũgeithagia o ariũ na aarĩ a ithe wanyu-rĩ, mũgĩkĩrĩte arĩa angĩ na kĩ? Githĩ o na arĩa matetĩkĩtie Ngai matiĩkaga o ũguo? <verse number="48" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:48 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 19:2">Alaw 19:2</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:16">1Pet 1:16</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, tuĩkai aagĩrĩru kũna, o ta ũrĩa Ithe wanyu ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ arĩ mwagĩrĩru kũna.</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gũteithia arĩa Abatari</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>“Mwĩmenyererei mũtigekage ciĩko cianyu cia ũthingu mbere ya andũ nĩguo mamuone. Mũngĩĩka ũguo-rĩ, mũtirĩ kĩheo mũkaaheo nĩ Ithe wanyu ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, rĩrĩa ũkũheana kĩndũ kũrĩ arĩa abatari, ndũkae kwanĩrĩra ũrĩa ũreka na tũrumbeta, ta ũrĩa hinga ciĩkaga thunagogi-inĩ na njĩra-inĩ, nĩguo itĩĩagwo nĩ andũ. Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, acio nĩmarĩkĩtie kwamũkĩra kĩheo kĩao gĩothe. <verse number="3" style="v"/>No hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũkũheana kĩndũ kũrĩ arĩa abatari-rĩ, ndũkareke guoko gwaku kwa ũmotho kũmenye ũrĩa guoko gwaku kwa ũrĩo kũreeka, <verse number="4" style="v"/>nĩgeetha ũheani ũcio waku ũtuĩke wa hitho-inĩ. Nake Ithe wanyu, ũrĩa wonaga maũndũ marĩa mekagĩrwo hitho-inĩ, nĩakamũhe kĩheo.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũhooya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 11:25">Mar 11:25</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 18:10-14">Luk 18:10-14</ref></char>
    </note>“Na rĩrĩa mũkũhooya-rĩ, mũtikanatuĩke ta hinga, nĩgũkorwo ciendaga kũhooya irũgamĩte thĩinĩ wa thunagogi na macemanĩrio ma njĩra nĩguo cionwo nĩ andũ. Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, icio nĩirĩkĩtie kwamũkĩra mũcaara wacio wothe. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 4:33">2Ath 4:33</ref></char></note>No hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũkũhooya, toonya nyũmba yaku, ũhinge mũrango na ũhooye Thoguo ũrĩa ũtoonekaga. Nake Thoguo ũrĩa wonaga maũndũ marĩa mekagĩrwo hitho-inĩ, nĩagakũhe mũcaara waku. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ECC 5:2">Koh 5:2</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 18:26-29">1Ath 18:26-29</ref></char></note>Na ningĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũkũhooya-rĩ, tigagai kũhũhũtĩka ta andũ arĩa matetĩkĩtie Ngai, nĩgũkorwo meciiragia nĩ mekũiguuo nĩ ũndũ wa kũraihia mahooya. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Mũtigatuĩke tao, nĩgũkorwo Ithe wanyu nĩoĩ kĩrĩa kĩmũbatairie o na mũtanamũhooya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 3:19">Jer 3:19</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:17">1Pet 1:17</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mwagĩrĩirwo nĩkũhooyaga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘Ithe witũ ũrĩ igũrũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">rĩĩtwa rĩaku nĩrĩamũrwo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:2">Math 3:2</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:39">Math 26:39</ref></char>
    </note>ũthamaki waku nĩũũke,</para>
  <para style="q1">ũrĩa wendete Wee nĩwĩkagwo</para>
  <para style="q2">gũkũ thĩ ta ũrĩa wĩkagwo kũu igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 30:8">Thim 30:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tũhe ũmũthĩ irio ciitũ cia gũtũigana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 18:21-35">Math 18:21-35</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na ũtũrekere mahĩtia maitũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ta ũrĩa o na ithuĩ tũrekagĩra arĩa matũhĩtagĩria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 1:13">Jak 1:13</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:37">Math 5:37</ref></char>
    </note>Na ndũgatũtware magerio-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">no ũtũhonokagie kuuma kũrĩ ũrĩa mũũru.’</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 11:25">Mar 11:25</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 11:26">26</ref>; <ref loc="COL 3:13">Akol 3:13</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo mũngĩrekera andũ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mamũhĩtĩria, o nake Ithe wanyu ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ nĩarĩmũrekagĩra. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 29:7">Ndar 29:7</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 18:35">Math 18:35</ref></char></note>No mũngĩaga kũrekera andũ mehia mao-rĩ, o nake Ithe wanyu ndarĩmũrekagĩra mehia manyu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kwĩhinga Kũrĩa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 58:5">Isa 58:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ningĩ rĩrĩa mũkwĩhinga kũrĩa irio-rĩ, tigagai gũtukia mothiũ manyu ta ũrĩa hinga ciĩkaga, nĩgũkorwo nĩitukagia mothiũ macio nĩguo cionie andũ atĩ nĩciĩhingĩte kũrĩa irio. Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, icio nĩirĩkĩtie kwamũkĩra mũcaara wacio wothe. <verse number="17" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa wĩhingĩte kũrĩa, wĩhakage maguta mũtwe na wĩthambage ũthiũ, <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 6:4">Math 6:4</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 6:6">6</ref></char></note>nĩguo andũ matikamenye atĩ nĩwĩhingĩte kũrĩa, tiga o Thoguo ũrĩa ũtoonekaga amenye; nake Thoguo ũrĩa wonaga maũndũ marĩa mekagĩrwo hitho-inĩ, nĩagakũhe mũcaara.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũthiithũ kũu Igũrũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 13:5">Ahib 13:5</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 5:2">Jak 5:2</ref></char>
    </note>“Tigagai kwĩigĩra mĩthiithũ gũkũ thĩ, kũrĩa indo irĩĩagwo nĩ memenyi na ikaroota, na kũrĩa aici mabunjaga makaiya. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 19:21">Math 19:21</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:19">1Tim 6:19</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 12:33">Luk 12:33</ref></char></note>No mwĩigagĩrei mĩthiithũ igũrũ, kũrĩa ĩtangĩrĩĩo nĩ memenyi kana ĩroote, na kũrĩa aici matangĩbunja maiye. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo kũrĩa mĩthiithũ yanyu ĩrĩ, nokuo ngoro cianyu o nacio irĩĩkoragwo irĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>“Riitho nĩrĩo tawa wa mwĩrĩ. Maitho maku mangĩkorwo marĩ mega, mwĩrĩ waku wothe nĩũrĩiyũragwo nĩ ũtheri. <verse number="23" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, maitho maku mangĩkorwo nĩ mathũku, mwĩrĩ waku wothe ũrĩiyũragwo nĩ nduma. Naguo ũtheri ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ waku ũngĩkorwo nĩ nduma-rĩ, nduma ĩyo kaĩ nĩ nene-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 16:13">Luk 16:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota gũtungatĩra aathani eerĩ. Nĩ ũndũ no athũũrire ũmwe, na ende ũcio ũngĩ; kana eheane harĩ ũmwe, na anyarare ũcio ũngĩ. Mũtingĩtungatĩra Ngai na mũtungatĩre mbeeca.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũtigatangĩke</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 12:11">Luk 12:11</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 12:22">22</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, tigagai gũtangĩkĩra mĩoyo yanyu, nĩ ũndũ wa kĩrĩa mũrĩrĩĩaga kana kĩrĩa mũrĩnyuuaga; kana kĩrĩa mũrĩĩhumbaga mĩĩrĩ yanyu. Githĩ muoyo ndũrĩ bata gũkĩra irio, naguo mwĩrĩ ũkagĩa bata gũkĩra nguo? <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 147:9">Thab 147:9</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 10:29-31">Math 10:29-31</ref></char></note>Ta rorai nyoni cia rĩera-inĩ; itihaandaga, kana ikagetha, kana ikaiga magetha ikũmbĩ, no Ithe wanyu ũrĩa ũrĩ Igũrũ nĩaciheaga irio. Githĩ inyuĩ mũtikĩrĩ a bata mũno gũkĩra icio? <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 39:5">Thab 39:5</ref></char></note>Nũũ wanyu ũngĩhota kuongerera muoyo wake ithaa o na rĩmwe nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtanga?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>“Na nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga mwĩtange nĩ ũndũ wa nguo? Ta rorai itoka cia gĩthaka ũrĩa ikũraga. Itirutaga wĩra kana ikogotha ndigi, <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1KI 10:4-7">1Ath 10:4-7</ref></char></note>no ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, o na Solomoni arĩ na riiri wake wothe ndagemete ta kĩmwe gĩacio. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 8:26">Math 8:26</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 12:28">Luk 12:28</ref></char></note>Angĩkorwo ũguo nĩguo Ngai ahumbaga nyeki ya gĩthaka ĩrĩa ĩrĩ ho ũmũthĩ na rũciũ ĩgaikio mwaki-inĩ-rĩ, githĩ inyuĩ ndarĩkĩmũhumbaga wega makĩria, inyuĩ mwĩtĩkĩtie o hanini? <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, tigagai gwĩtanga, mũkĩũria atĩrĩ: ‘Tũkũrĩa kĩĩ?’ kana ‘Tũkũnyua kĩĩ?’ kana ‘Tũkwĩhumba kĩĩ?’ <verse number="32" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo maũndũ maya mothe nĩmo macaragio nĩ andũ arĩa matetĩkĩtie Ngai. No Ithe wanyu wa igũrũ nĩoĩ atĩ nĩmũbataragio nĩmo. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 37:4">Thab 37:4</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 19:29">Math 19:29</ref></char></note>No ambai mũcarie ũthamaki wake na ũthingu wake, na maũndũ maya mangĩ mothe o namo nĩarĩmũheaga. <verse number="34" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio tigagai gwĩtanga nĩ ũndũ wa rũciũ, nĩgũkorwo rũciũ nĩrũgetangĩkĩra ruo rwene. O mũthenya ũrĩ na mathĩĩna maguo ma kũũigana.</para>
  <chapter number="7" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gũtuĩra Andũ arĩa angĩ Ciira</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 6:37">Luk 6:37</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 4:5">1Akor 4:5</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũtigaciirithanagie nĩgeetha na inyuĩ mũtikanaciirithio. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 35:11">Ezek 35:11</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 4:24">Mar 4:24</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo o ta ũrĩa mũtuagĩra andũ arĩa angĩ ciira, noguo na inyuĩ mũgaatuĩrwo ciira, na gĩthimi kĩrĩa mũthimanagĩra nakĩo, no kĩo mũrĩthimagĩrwo nakĩo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>“Nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga wone kĩhuti kĩrĩa kĩrĩ riitho rĩa mũrũ wa thoguo, no ũkaaga kuona mũgogo ũrĩa ũrĩ riitho rĩaku wee mwene? <verse number="4" style="v"/>Wahota atĩa kwĩra mũrũ wa thoguo atĩrĩ, ‘Reke ngũrute kĩhuti kĩu kĩrĩ riitho rĩaku,’ o rĩrĩa wee mwene ũrĩ na mũgogo riitho rĩaku? <verse number="5" style="v"/>Wee hinga ĩno, amba ũrute mũgogo ũcio ũrĩ riitho rĩaku, nĩguo wone wega na ũhote kũruta kĩhuti kĩrĩa kĩrĩ riitho rĩa mũrũ wa thoguo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>“Mũtikanahe magui kĩndũ kĩrĩa kĩamũre, na mũtikanaikĩrie ngũrwe ruru cianyu. Mũngĩĩka ũguo-rĩ, ingĩrangĩrĩria ruru na magũrũ ma cio, icooke imũgarũrũke, imũtiihangie.</para>
  <para style="s1">Hooyai, Mathaai, Ringaringai Mũrango</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 15:7">Joh 15:7</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 15:16">16</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 3:22">1Joh 3:22</ref></char>
    </note>“Hooyai na nĩmũkũheo; mathaai na nĩmũkuona; ringaringai mũrango na nĩmũkũhingũrĩrwo. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 8:17">Thim 8:17</ref>; <ref loc="JER 29:12">Jer 29:12</ref>, <ref loc="JER 29:13">13</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ũrĩa wothe ũhooyaga nĩaheagwo, na ũrĩa ũmaathaga nĩonaga, na ũrĩa ũringaringaga mũrango, nĩahingũragĩrwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>“Na rĩrĩ, nũũ wanyu ũngĩĩtio mũgate nĩ mwana wake amũhe ihiga? <verse number="10" style="v"/>Kana amwĩtie thamaki nake amũhe nyoka? <verse number="11" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo inyuĩ, o na mũrĩ ooru, nĩmũũĩ kũhe ciana cianyu iheo njega-rĩ, githĩ Ithe wanyu ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ ndagakĩrĩrĩria kũhe iheo njega kũrĩ arĩa mamũhooyaga! <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 6:31">Luk 6:31</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 13:8-10">Arom 13:8-10</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, maũndũ-inĩ mothe, ĩkagai andũ arĩa angĩ ũrĩa mũngĩenda mamwĩkage, nĩgũkorwo ũcio nĩguo Watho wa Musa na Ũrutani wa Anabii.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũromo ũrĩa Mũceke na ũrĩa Mwariĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 13:24">Luk 13:24</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:7">Joh 10:7</ref></char>
    </note>“Toonyerai mũromo ũrĩa mũceke. Nĩgũkorwo mũromo nĩ mwariĩ na njĩra nĩ njariĩ ĩrĩa yerekeire rĩũrĩro, na andũ arĩa matoonyagĩra ho nĩ aingĩ. <verse number="14" style="v"/>No mũromo nĩ mũkunderu na njĩra nĩ njeke ĩrĩa ĩkinyaga muoyo-inĩ, na andũ arĩa mamĩonaga nĩ anini.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũtĩ na Maciaro Maguo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2PE 2:1">2Pet 2:1</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 20:29">Atũm 20:29</ref></char>
    </note>“Mwĩhũgagei anabii a maheeni. Mokaga kũrĩ inyuĩ mehumbĩte njũa cia ngʼondu, no thĩinĩ wao nĩ njũũi ndĩani. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 6:43">Luk 6:43</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 6:44">44</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 3:12">Jak 3:12</ref></char></note>Nĩmũrĩmamenyaga na maciaro mao. Kaĩ thabibũ igĩtuuagwo mĩtĩ-inĩ ya mĩigua, kana ngũyũ igatuuo kuuma mahiũ-inĩ ma nyeki? <verse number="17" style="v"/>Ũguo noguo, mũtĩ wothe mwega ũciaraga maciaro mega, no mũtĩ mũũru ũciaraga maciaro mooru. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 6:43">Luk 6:43</ref></char></note>Mũtĩ mwega ndũngĩciara maciaro mooru, naguo mũtĩ mũũru ndũngĩciara maciaro mega. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:10">Math 3:10</ref></char></note>Mũtĩ o wothe ũtaciaraga maciaro mega nĩgũtemwo ũtemagwo ũgaikio mwaki-inĩ. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Ũguo nĩguo mũrĩmamenyaga nĩ ũndũ wa maciaro mao.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 25:11">Math 25:11</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:50">Math 12:50</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:22">Jak 1:22</ref></char>
    </note>“To mũndũ ũrĩa ũnjĩtaga, ‘Mwathani, Mwathani,’ ũgaatoonya ũthamaki wa igũrũ, no nĩ ũrĩa wĩkaga ũrĩa Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ endaga. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:15">Math 10:15</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 19:13">Atũm 19:13</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio aingĩ makanjĩĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathani, Mwathani, githĩ tũtiarathaga maũndũ na rĩĩtwa rĩaku, na thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩaku tũkaingata ndaimono na tũkaringa ciama nyingĩ?’ <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 6:8">Thab 6:8</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 13:25-27">Luk 13:25-27</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩngameera wega atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ ndirĩ hĩndĩ ndaamũũĩ o na rĩ. Eherai harĩ niĩ, inyuĩ mwĩkaga ũũru!’</para>
  <para style="s1">Aaki Oogĩ na Aaki Akĩĩgu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 1:22">Jak 1:22</ref>, <ref loc="JAS 1:25">25</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe ũiguaga ciugo ici ciakwa na ageeka ũrĩa ciugĩte, ahaana ta mũndũ mũũgĩ ũrĩa wakire nyũmba yake igũrũ rĩa rwaro rwa ihiga. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nayo mbura ĩkiura, na njũũĩ ikĩiyũra, naruo rũhuho rũkĩhurutana nacio ikĩhũũra nyũmba ĩyo na nditi, no nyũmba ĩyo ndĩagũire, tondũ mũthingi wayo wakĩtwo igũrũ rĩa rwaro rwa ihiga. <verse number="26" style="v"/>No mũndũ o wothe ũiguaga ciugo ici ciakwa na ndekaga ũrĩa ciugĩte ahaana ta mũndũ mũkĩĩgu ũrĩa wakire nyũmba yake mũthanga igũrũ. <verse number="27" style="v"/>Nayo mbura ĩkiura, njũũĩ ikĩiyũra, naruo rũhuho rũkĩhurutana nacio ikĩhũũra nyũmba ĩyo na nditi, nayo nyũmba ĩyo ĩkĩmomoka na kũgũa kũnene.”</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:53">Math 13:53</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 1:22">Mar 1:22</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 17:14">Luk 17:14</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aarĩkirie kuuga maũndũ macio, kĩrĩndĩ kĩu gĩkĩgega nĩ ũndũ wa ũrutani wake, <verse number="29" style="v"/>tondũ aarutanaga ta mũndũ warĩ na ũhoti, na ti ta ũrĩa arutani ao a watho maarutanaga.</para>
  <chapter number="8" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũndũ ũrĩa warĩ na Mangũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aikũrũkire kuuma kĩrĩma-inĩ, ikundi nene cia andũ ikĩmuuma thuutha. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Na mũndũ warĩ na mangũ agĩthiĩ harĩ we, agĩturia maru mbere yake, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ũngĩenda-rĩ, no ũũtherie.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mũndũ warĩ na mangũ aatuĩkaga arĩ na thaahu, na no atheririo.</char></note></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ agĩtambũrũkia guoko gwake, akĩhutia mũndũ ũcio, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩngwenda. Therio!” O hĩndĩ ĩyo akĩhonio mangũ make. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 5:43">Mar 5:43</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 4:32">Luk 4:32</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 14:2-32">Alaw 14:2-32</ref></char></note>Jesũ agĩcooka akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Menya ndũkeere mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ. No thiĩ ũkeyonanie kũrĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai, na ũrute kĩheo kĩrĩa Musa aathanire gĩtuĩke ũira kũrĩ o.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Wĩtĩkio wa Mũnene-wa-Thigari-Igana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Na Jesũ aarĩkia gũtoonya Kaperinaumu, mũnene-wa-thigari-igana agĩũka kũrĩ we, akĩmũhooya ũteithio. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:24">Math 4:24</ref></char></note>Akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ndungata yakwa ĩkomete mũciĩ ĩrũarĩte mũrimũ wa gũkua ciĩga na ĩrĩ na ruo rũingĩ mũno.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩngũthiĩ kũmĩhonia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 107:20">Thab 107:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No mũnene ũcio wa thigari igana akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, niĩ ndiagĩrĩire atĩ wee ũũke gwakwa. No uga o kiugo, na ndungata yakwa nĩĩkũhona. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo niĩ mwene ndĩ mũndũ wathagwo, na ndĩ na thigari njathaga. Ndeera ũmwe ‘Thiĩ,’ nĩathiiaga, na ndeera ũngĩ atĩrĩ, ‘Ũka,’ nĩokaga. Na ningĩ ndeera ndungata yakwa atĩrĩ, ‘Ĩka ũna,’ nĩĩkaga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 15:28">Math 15:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aiguire ũguo-rĩ, akĩgega, akĩĩra arĩa maamumĩte thuutha atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ndionete mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ gũkũ Isiraeli ũrĩ na wĩtĩkio mũnene ũũ. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 49:12">Isa 49:12</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 59:19">59:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAL 1:11">Mal 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 13:29">Luk 13:29</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, aingĩ nĩmagooka kuuma mwena wa irathĩro na wa ithũĩro, na nĩmagaikara iruga-inĩ hamwe na Iburahĩmu, na Isaaka, na Jakubu, ũthamaki-inĩ wa igũrũ. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 13:42">Math 13:42</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 13:50">50</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 22:13">22:13</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 13:28">Luk 13:28</ref></char></note>No arĩa marĩ a ũthamaki ũcio nĩmagaikio nja, kũu nduma-inĩ, kũrĩa gũgaakorwo kĩrĩro na kũhagarania magego.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ agĩcooka akĩĩra mũnene ũcio wa thigari igana atĩrĩ, “Thiĩ! Nĩũgwĩkĩrwo o ũguo wĩtĩkĩtie.” Nayo ndungata yake ĩkĩhonio o ithaa rĩu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhonia Andũ Aingĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aatoonyire nyũmba ya Petero, akĩona atĩ nyina wa mũtumia wa Petero aarĩ mũrũaru mũrimũ wa kũhiũha mwĩrĩ, agakoma gĩtanda-inĩ. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Akĩmũhutia guoko, nake agĩtiga kũhiũha mwĩrĩ, akĩarahũka, akĩambĩrĩria kũmũtungatĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Hwaĩ-inĩ ũcio, andũ aingĩ arĩa maarĩ na ndaimono makĩrehwo kũrĩ we, nake akĩingata maroho macio na kuuga o kiugo, na akĩhonia arĩa othe maarĩ arũaru. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 53:4">Isa 53:4</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 1:22">Math 1:22</ref></char></note>Ũhoro ũyũ warĩ wa kũhingia ũrĩa kwaarĩtio na kanua ka mũnabii Isaia, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“We mwene nĩoire wonje witũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akĩeheria mĩrimũ iitũ.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Thogora wa Kũrũmĩrĩra Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 4:35">Mar 4:35</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ oonire gĩkundi kĩa andũ arĩa maamũthiũrũrũkĩirie, agĩathana maringe mũrĩmo ũrĩa ũngĩ wa iria. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo mũrutani ũmwe wa watho agĩũka harĩ we, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũrutani, nĩndĩkũrũmagĩrĩra kũrĩa guothe ũrĩthiiaga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mbwe nĩ irĩ marima, na nyoni cia rĩera-inĩ nĩ irĩ itara, no Mũrũ wa Mũndũ ndarĩ handũ angĩigĩrĩra mũtwe wake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nake mũrutwo ũngĩ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, reke nyambe thiĩ ngathike baba.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 4:19">Math 4:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nowe Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nũmĩrĩra, na ũreke arĩa akuũ mathike akuũ ao ene.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhooreria Kĩhuhũkanio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo agĩtoonya gatarũ, nao arutwo ake makĩmũrũmĩrĩra. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, gũkĩgĩa kĩhuhũkanio kĩnene gĩteerĩgĩrĩirwo kũu iria-inĩ, gĩgĩtũma gatarũ kende kũhubwo nĩ makũmbĩ ma maaĩ. No Jesũ aarĩ toro. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nao arutwo magĩthiĩ, makĩmũũkĩria, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, tũhonokie! Nĩtũkũũrĩra maaĩ-inĩ!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 6:30">Math 6:30</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 65:7">Thab 65:7</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 89:9">89:9</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 107:29">107:29</ref></char>
    </note>Nake agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ mũrĩ a wĩtĩkio mũnini, nĩ kĩĩ gĩgũtũma mwĩtigĩre ũguo?” Thuutha ũcio agĩũkĩra, agĩkũũma rũhuho na makũmbĩ macio, nakuo gũkĩhoorera biũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Andũ acio makĩgega, makĩũria atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ mũndũ ũyũ akĩrĩ ũ atĩ o na rũhuho na makũmbĩ ma maaĩ nĩimwathĩkagĩra?”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhonia Andũ Eerĩ Maarĩ na Ndaimono</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 4:24">Math 4:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa aakinyire rũgongo rwa bũrũri wa Agadari-rĩ, agĩtũngwo nĩ andũ eerĩ maarĩ na ndaimono, moimĩte mbĩrĩra-inĩ. Maarĩ na ũũru mũingĩ mũno, atĩ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩagerire njĩra ĩyo. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JDG 11:12">Atiir 11:12</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 16:10">2Sam 16:10</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 1:24">Mar 1:24</ref></char></note>Nao makĩanĩrĩra, makĩũria atĩrĩ, “Ũrenda atĩa na ithuĩ, wee Mũrũ wa Ngai. Woka gũkũ gũtũnyariira ihinda rĩrĩa rĩamũre rĩtanakinya?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>Nĩ haarĩ na rũũru rũnene rwa ngũrwe rwarĩithagio<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8:30 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ndũrĩrĩ iria ciatũũraga Galili nĩcio ciarĩ arĩithi a ngũrwe.</char></note> handũ hataarĩ haraaya na hau maarĩ. <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nacio ndaimono igĩthaitha Jesũ, ikĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Akorwo nĩũgũtũingata-rĩ, tũtũme kũrĩ rũũru rũũrĩa rwa ngũrwe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Nake agĩciĩra atĩrĩ, “Thiĩi!” Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ikiuma, igĩtoonya ngũrwe, naruo rũũru ruothe rũgĩikũrũka kĩharũrũka-inĩ na ihenya, rũkĩgũa iria thĩinĩ, rũgĩkuĩra maaĩ-inĩ. <verse number="33" style="v"/>Arĩa maarĩithagia ngũrwe icio makĩũra, magĩthiĩ itũũra-inĩ, makĩheana maũndũ macio mothe o na ũrĩa gwekĩkĩte kũrĩ andũ arĩa maarĩ na ndaimono. <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 5:8">Luk 5:8</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 16:39">Atũm 16:39</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo itũũra rĩothe rĩkiumagara rĩgatũnge Jesũ. Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maamuonire, makĩmũthaitha oime rũgongo rwao.</para>
  <chapter number="9" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhonia Mũndũ Wakuĩte Ciĩga</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake agĩtoonya gatarũ, akĩringa iria, agĩkinya itũũra rĩa kwao. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Andũ amwe makĩmũrehera mũndũ warĩ na mũrimũ wa gũkua ciĩga, akuuĩtwo na kĩbarĩ. Rĩrĩa Jesũ oonire wĩtĩkio wao, akĩĩra mũndũ ũcio wakuĩte ciĩga atĩrĩ, “Mũriũ, wĩyũmĩrĩrie, nĩwarekerwo mehia maku.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo, arutani amwe a watho makĩĩra na ngoro atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ nĩaruma Ngai!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 12:25">Math 12:25</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 6:8">Luk 6:8</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 9:47">9:47</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 2:25">Joh 2:25</ref></char>
    </note>Jesũ aamenya ũrĩa meeciiragia, akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Mũreciiria ũũru ngoro-inĩ cianyu nĩkĩ? <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũrĩkũ mũhũthũ: nĩ kwĩra mũndũ, ‘Nĩwarekerwo mehia maku,’ kana kũmwĩra, ‘Ũkĩra wĩtware?’ <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 8:20">Math 8:20</ref></char></note>No nĩgeetha mũmenye atĩ Mũrũ wa Mũndũ arĩ na ũhoti gũkũ thĩ wa kũrekanĩra mehia-rĩ … .” Na o hĩndĩ ĩyo akĩĩra mũndũ ũcio wakuĩte ciĩga atĩrĩ, “Ũkĩra, oya kĩbarĩ gĩaku ũinũke mũciĩ.” <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ ũcio agĩũkĩra, akĩinũka mũciĩ. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:16">Math 5:16</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 4:21">Atũm 4:21</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa kĩrĩndĩ kĩu kĩonire ũguo, gĩkĩmaka na gĩkĩgooca Ngai, ũrĩa waheete andũ ũhoti ta ũcio.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gwĩtwo kwa Mathayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 4:19">Math 4:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ oimaga kũu, akĩona mũndũ wetagwo Mathayo aikarĩte harĩa heetagĩrio mbeeca cia igooti. Akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nũmĩrĩra,” nake Mathayo agĩũkĩra, akĩmũrũmĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ aarĩ kwa Mathayo mũciĩ makĩrĩa irio cia hwaĩ-inĩ, etia mbeeca cia igooti aingĩ na andũ ehia magĩũka kũrĩanĩra hamwe nake na arutwo ake. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 11:19">Math 11:19</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 2:15">Agal 2:15</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa Afarisai moonire ũguo, makĩũria arutwo ake atĩrĩ, “Mũrutani wanyu arĩĩanagĩra na etia mbeeca cia igooti na andũ ehia nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Jesũ aigua ũguo, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Andũ arĩa agima mĩĩrĩ ti o mabataragio nĩ ndagĩtarĩ, no nĩ arĩa arũaru. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HOS 6:6">Hos 6:6</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:7">Math 12:7</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 1:15">1Tim 1:15</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, thiĩi mũkeerute ũrĩa ciugo ici ciugĩte: ‘Kũiguanĩra tha nĩkuo nyendaga, no ti magongona.’ Nĩgũkorwo niĩ ndiokire gũcaria arĩa athingu, no ndokire nĩ ũndũ wa arĩa ehia.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũũrio Ũhoro wa Kwĩhinga Kũrĩa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:1">Math 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 18:12">Luk 18:12</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo arutwo a Johana magĩũka kũrĩ we makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ na Afarisai nĩtwĩhingaga kũrĩa, no nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga arutwo aku mage kwĩhinga kũrĩa irio?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:29">Joh 3:29</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 13:2">Atũm 13:2</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 13:3">3</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ageni a mũhikania mangĩhota atĩa kũigua kĩeha rĩrĩa mũhikania arĩ hamwe nao? Ihinda nĩrĩgakinya rĩrĩa mũhikania akeeherio kũrĩ o; hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩguo makeehinga kũrĩa irio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>“Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũtumagĩrĩra nguo ngũrũ kĩraka kĩa nguo njerũ, nĩgũkorwo kĩraka kĩu no kĩguucie nguo ĩyo gĩtũme ĩtarũke makĩria. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Ningĩ andũ matiĩkagĩra ndibei ya mũhihano mondo-inĩ ngũrũ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9:17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ndibei yekagĩrwo mondo ciatumagwo na njũũa cia mbũri.</char></note> Mangĩĩka ũguo, mondo icio no itarũke, nayo ndibei ĩitĩke, na mondo icio cia ndibei cianangĩke o biũ. No andũ mekagĩra ndibei ya mũhihano mondo-inĩ njerũ, nacio cierĩ igaikara irĩ njega.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũirĩtu Wakuĩte na Mũtumia warĩ Mũrũaru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:23">Math 5:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩa aaragia maũndũ macio, hagĩũka mũndũ warĩ mũnene, akĩmũturĩria ndu, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũirĩtu wakwa no hĩndĩ aakua; no ũka ũkamũigĩrĩre guoko, na nĩekũriũka.” <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ agĩũkĩra, agĩthiĩ nake, arĩ na arutwo ake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 14:36">Math 14:36</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 6:19">Luk 6:19</ref></char>
    </note>O hĩndĩ ĩyo mũtumia watũire oiraga thakame mĩaka ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ agĩũka na thuutha wa Jesũ, akĩhutia gĩcũrĩ kĩa nguo yake. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Tondũ eĩĩraga atĩrĩ, “Ingĩhutia o nguo yake, no hone.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 7:50">Luk 7:50</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 17:19">17:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 15:28">Math 15:28</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩĩhũgũra, akĩmuona, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwarĩ ũyũ, wĩyũmĩrĩrie gwĩtĩkia gwaku nĩkuo gwatũma ũhone.” Nake mũtumia ũcio akĩhonio o hĩndĩ ĩyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CH 35:25">2Maũ 35:25</ref>; <ref loc="JER 9:17-18">Jer 9:17-18</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ aatoonyire nyũmba ya mũnene ũcio, akĩona ahuhi mĩtũrirũ na gĩkundi kĩa andũ kĩrĩa kĩanegenaga, <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DAN 12:2">Dan 12:2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:11-14">Joh 11:11-14</ref></char></note>akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Eherai. Mũirĩtũ ũyũ ti mũkuũ, nĩ gũkoma akomete.” Nao andũ acio makĩmũthekerera. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Thuutha wa andũ acio kuumio nja, agĩtoonya thĩinĩ, akĩnyiita mũirĩtu ũcio guoko, nake agĩũkĩra. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:24">Math 4:24</ref></char></note>Ũhoro ũcio ũkĩhunja bũrũri ũcio wothe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhonia Atumumu na Mũndũ Ũtaaragia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 15:22">Math 15:22</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 10:47">Mar 10:47</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ oimire kũu, aathianga-rĩ, andũ eerĩ atumumu makĩmũrũmĩrĩra, makĩanagĩrĩra, makiugaga atĩrĩ, “Tũiguĩre tha, wee Mũrũ wa Daudi!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 14:9">Atũm 14:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aatoonyire nyũmba, atumumu acio magĩũka kũrĩ we, nake akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nĩmwĩtĩkĩtie atĩ no hote gwĩka ũguo?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ-ni, Mwathani.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 9:22">Math 9:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo akĩmahutia maitho, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Mũroĩkwo o ũguo mwĩtĩkĩtie;” <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 8:4">Math 8:4</ref></char></note>namo maitho mao makĩhingũka magĩcooka kuona. Nake Jesũ akĩmakaania na hinya, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mũtikareke mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ amenye ũhoro ũyũ.” <verse number="31" style="v"/>No-o makiumagara na makĩhunjia ũhoro wake bũrũri ũcio wothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 12:22-24">Math 12:22-24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa moimaga hau, Jesũ akĩreherwo mũndũ warĩ na ndaimono, na ndaaragia. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 2:12">Mar 2:12</ref></char></note>Nayo ndaimono yaingatwo, mũndũ ũcio ũtaaragia, akĩaria. Kĩrĩndĩ gĩkĩgega, gĩkiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũndũ ta ũyũ ndũrĩ woneka Isiraeli.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 12:24">Math 12:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No Afarisai makiuga atĩrĩ, “Aingataga ndaimono na hinya wa mũnene wa ndaimono.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Aruti Wĩra nĩ Anini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ agĩtuĩkania matũũra-inĩ mothe na mĩciĩ-inĩ yothe, akĩrutanaga thĩinĩ wa thunagogi ciao, akĩhunjagia Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega wa ũthamaki, na akĩhonagia mĩrimũ na ndwari cia mĩthemba yothe. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 14:14">Math 14:14</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 27:17">Ndar 27:17</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩa oonire ũrĩa kĩrĩndĩ kĩu kĩaiganaga, agĩkĩiguĩra tha tondũ kĩarĩ gĩthĩĩnĩku na gĩkaaga ũteithio, ta ngʼondu itarĩ na mũrĩithi. <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 4:35">Joh 4:35</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 10:2">Luk 10:2</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo akĩĩra arutwo ake atĩrĩ, “Magetha nĩ maingĩ, no aruti a wĩra nĩ anini. <verse number="38" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, hooyai Mwathani wa magetha atũme aruti wĩra mathiĩ magetha-inĩ make.”</para>
  <chapter number="10" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũtũma Arutwo arĩa Ikũmi na Eerĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 3:13-15">Mar 3:13-15</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:23">Math 4:23</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ nĩetire arutwo ake ikũmi na eerĩ moke harĩ we, nake akĩmahe ũhoti wa kũingata ngoma thũku na kũhonia mĩrimũ yothe na ndwari ciothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Maya nĩmo marĩĩtwa ma arutwo acio ikũmi na eerĩ: Wa mbere nĩ Simoni (ũrĩa wĩtagwo Petero), na mũrũ wa nyina Anderea; na Jakubu mũrũ wa Zebedi, na mũrũ wa nyina Johana; <verse number="3" style="v"/>na Filipu, na Baritholomayo; na Toma, na Mathayo ũrĩa mwĩtia wa mbeeca cia igooti; na Jakubu mũrũ wa Alifayo, na Thadayo; <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:2">Joh 13:2</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 13:26">26</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 13:27">27</ref></char></note>na Simoni ũrĩa Mũzelote, na Judasi Mũisikariota, ũrĩa wamũkunyanĩire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 9:52">Luk 9:52</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Aya ikũmi na eerĩ nĩo Jesũ aatũmire na akĩmataara ũũ: “Mũtigathiĩ kũrĩ andũ-a-Ndũrĩrĩ kana mũtoonye itũũra rĩa Asamaria. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 15:24">Math 15:24</ref></char></note>Nĩ kaba mũthiĩ kũrĩ ngʼondu iria ciũrĩte cia Isiraeli. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:2">Math 3:2</ref></char></note>Mwathiĩ-rĩ, hunjagiai ndũmĩrĩri ĩno: ‘Ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩũkuhĩrĩirie.’ <verse number="8" style="v"/>Honagiai andũ arĩa arũaru, na mũriũkagie arĩa akuũ, na mũtheragie arĩa marĩ na mangũ, na mũingatage ndaimono. Mũheetwo tũhũ, heanagai tũhũ. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Mũtigekuuĩre thahabu, kana betha, kana gĩcango mĩcibi-inĩ yanyu; <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 5:18">1Tim 5:18</ref></char></note>O na ningĩ mũtigekuuĩre mũhuko rũgendo-inĩ, kana nguo igĩrĩ, kana iraatũ, kana mũtirima; nĩgũkorwo mũruti wa wĩra nĩabataire kũheo gĩa kũmũtũũria muoyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>“Itũũra o rĩothe kana gatũũra karĩa mũngĩtoonya-rĩ, tuĩriai mũmenye mũndũ ũrĩa mwagĩrĩru kuo, mũikare gwake nginya rĩrĩa mũkoima kuo. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1SA 25:6">1Sam 25:6</ref></char></note>Mwatoonya mũciĩ ũcio-rĩ, geithagiai ene kuo. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo mũciĩ ũcio nĩwagĩrĩire-rĩ, ũrathimei na thayũ wanyu; angĩkorwo ndwagĩrĩire-rĩ, rekei kĩrathimo kĩanyu kĩmũcookerere. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 13:51">Atũm 13:51</ref></char></note>Mũndũ o wothe angĩrega kũmũnyiita ũgeni kana arege gũthikĩrĩria ciugo cianyu-rĩ, mũkiuma mũciĩ ũcio kana itũũra rĩu-rĩ, mũkaaribariba magũrũ manyu nĩguo rũkũngũ rũitĩke.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Kũribariba rũkũngũ magũrũ nĩ ũndũ wekagwo nĩ Afarisai moima ciikaro cia Ndũrĩrĩ metherie tondũ metĩkĩtie nĩmakuuĩte thaahu. Ũndũ ũyũ warĩ wa kuonia andũ ũrĩa mageekwo marega ndũmĩrĩri ya Ngai.</char></note> <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 18:20">Kĩam 18:20</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:36">Math 12:36</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 11:22">Math 11:22</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 11:24">24</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma ituĩro rĩa itũũra rĩu rĩgaakorwo rĩrĩ inene gũkĩra rĩa Sodomu na Gomora mũthenya ũrĩa wa ciira. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 20:29">Atũm 20:29</ref></char></note>Atĩrĩrĩ ndamũtũma o ta ngʼondu gatagatĩ ka njũũi. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, gĩai na ũũgĩ ta nyoka, na mwage ũũru ta ndutura.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:22">Math 5:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mwĩmenyererei andũ; tondũ nĩmakamũneana ciama-inĩ, na mamũhũũre na iboko thunagogi-inĩ ciao. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoro wakwa-rĩ, nĩmũgatwarwo mbere ya aathani na athamaki nĩgeetha mũtuĩke aira kũrĩ o na kũrĩ andũ-a-Ndũrĩrĩ. <verse number="19" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa makaamũnyiita-rĩ, mũtikanetange nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa mũkoiga kana ũrĩa mũgaacookia. Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩmũkeerwo ũrĩa mũkoiga, <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 4:8">Atũm 4:8</ref></char></note>nĩgũkorwo ti inyuĩ mũgaakorwo mũkĩaria, no nĩ Roho wa Ithe wanyu ũkaaria arĩ thĩinĩ wanyu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MIC 7:6">Mik 7:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mũndũ nĩagakunyanĩra mũrũ wa nyina ooragwo, na ithe wa mũndũ akunyanĩre mwana wake; ciana nĩikaremera aciari a cio na imoragithie. <verse number="22" style="v"/>Andũ othe nĩmakamũmena nĩ ũndũ wakwa, no ũrĩa ũgaakirĩrĩria nginya hĩndĩ ya mũthia nĩakahonoka. <verse number="23" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mwanyariirwo itũũra-inĩ rĩmwe-rĩ, ũrĩrai rĩrĩa rĩngĩ. Ngũmwĩra na ma atĩ, mũtigaakorwo mũthiĩte matũũra mothe ma Isiraeli, Mũrũ wa Mũndũ atookĩte.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:16">Joh 13:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mũrutwo ti mũnene kũrĩ mũrutani wake, o na ndungata ti nene kũrĩ mũmĩathi. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 3:22">Mar 3:22</ref></char></note>Nĩkũiganĩire mũrutwo aiganane na mũrutani wake, o na ndungata ĩiganane na mũmĩathi. Angĩkorwo mwene nyũmba nĩetĩtwo Beelizebuli-rĩ,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:25 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Rĩĩtwa Beelizebuli rĩgĩtaũrwo nĩ kuuga “Mũnene wa ndaimono,” no Kĩhibirania Beelizebubu rĩataũragwo “Mũnene wa ngi.”</char></note> githĩ andũ a nyũmba yake matigetwo marĩĩtwa mooru gũkĩra rĩu!</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 8:17">Luk 8:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, mũtikametigĩre. Gũtirĩ ũndũ mũhithanie ũtakaguũrio, kana ũndũ mũhithe ũtakamenyeka. <verse number="27" style="v"/>Ũrĩa ngũmwĩra nduma-inĩ-rĩ, wariei mũthenya barigici, na ũrĩa warĩtio na mĩheehũ matũ-inĩ manyu-rĩ, wanĩrĩrei mũrĩ nyũmba-igũrũ. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 10:31">Ahib 10:31</ref></char></note>Mũtigetigĩre arĩa moragaga o mwĩrĩ, no matingĩhota kũũraga ngoro. Nĩ kaba gwĩtigĩra Ũrĩa ũngĩananga ngoro na mwĩrĩ kũu Jehanamu. <verse number="29" style="v"/>Githĩ tũnyoni twĩrĩ tũtiendagio thendi ĩmwe? No gũtirĩ o na kamwe gatuo kangĩgũa thĩ Ithe wanyu atetĩkĩrĩte. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 21:18">Luk 21:18</ref></char></note>O na njuĩrĩ cianyu cia mũtwe nĩndare. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 6:26">Math 6:26</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũtigetigĩre; mũrĩ a bata gũkĩra tũnyoni tũingĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 10:9">Arom 10:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ũrĩa wothe ũkaanyumbũra mbere ya andũ, o na niĩ nĩngamumbũra mbere ya Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ kũu igũrũ. <verse number="33" style="v"/>No ũrĩa wothe ũkangaana mbere ya andũ, na niĩ nĩngamũkaana mbere ya Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>“Mũtigeciirie atĩ njũkĩte kũrehe thayũ gũkũ thĩ. Ndiokire kũrehe thayũ, no ndookire kũrehe rũhiũ rwa njora. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:21">Math 10:21</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo njũkĩte gũtũma</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘mũndũ okanĩrĩre na ithe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mũirĩtu okanĩrĩre na nyina,</para>
  <para style="q1">nake mũtumia okanĩrĩre na nyaciarawe;</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MIC 7:6">Mik 7:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>thũ cia mũndũ igaakorwo irĩ andũ a nyũmba yake kĩũmbe.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>“Ũrĩa wothe wendete ithe kana nyina kũngĩra ndagĩrĩire gũtuĩka wakwa; na ũrĩa wothe wendete mũriũ kana mwarĩ kũngĩra ndagĩrĩire gũtuĩka wakwa; <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 14:27">Luk 14:27</ref></char></note>nake ũrĩa wothe ũtagakuua mũtharaba wake wa kwambĩrwo aanũmĩrĩre ndagĩrĩire gũtuĩka wakwa. <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:25">Joh 12:25</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe ũgeragia gũtũũria muoyo wake nĩakoorwo nĩguo; no ũrĩa wothe ũkoorwo nĩ muoyo wake nĩ ũndũ wakwa nĩakaũtũũria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:40 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 16:8">Thaam 16:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mũndũ ũrĩa ũmwamũkagĩra, nĩ niĩ amũkagĩra. Nake ũrĩa ũnyamũkagĩra, amũkagĩra ũrĩa wandũmire. <verse number="41" style="v"/>Ũrĩa wothe ũkaamũkĩra mũnabii tondũ nĩ mũnabii, nĩakamũkĩra kĩheo kĩrĩa kĩheagwo mũnabii, nake ũrĩa wothe ũkaamũkĩra mũndũ mũthingu tondũ nĩ mũthingu-rĩ, nĩakamũkĩra kĩheo kĩrĩa kĩheagwo mũndũ mũthingu. <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 25:40">Math 25:40</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 6:10">Ahib 6:10</ref></char></note>Nake ũrĩa wothe ũheaga ũmwe wa aya anini o na gĩkombe kĩa maaĩ mahehu tondũ nĩ mũrutwo wakwa-rĩ, ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ndakaaga kũheo kĩheo gĩake.”</para>
  <chapter number="11" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ na Johana Mũbatithania</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, Jesũ aarĩkia gwatha arutwo acio ake ikũmi na eerĩ-rĩ, akiuma kũu agĩthiĩ kũrutana na kũhunjia matũũra-inĩ ma Galili.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 14:3">Math 14:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩa Johana aiguĩre arĩ njeera maũndũ marĩa Kristũ eekaga-rĩ, agĩtũma arutwo ake, <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 10:37">Ahib 10:37</ref></char></note>makamũũrie atĩrĩ, “Wee nĩwe warĩ ũũke, kana tweterere mũndũ ũngĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Cookai mũkeere Johana maũndũ marĩa mwaigua na marĩa muona: <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 35:4-6">Isa 35:4-6</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 4:18-19">Luk 4:18-19</ref></char></note>Atumumu nĩmaroona, na arĩa mathuaga nĩmaretwara, na arĩa marĩ na mangũ nĩmarahonio magathera, na arĩa mataiguaga nĩ maraigua, na arĩa akuũ nĩmarariũkio, na Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega nĩũrahunjĩrio arĩa athĩĩni. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:31">Math 26:31</ref></char></note>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũtekũhĩngwo arakare nĩ ũndũ wakwa.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:1">Math 3:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa arutwo a Johana moimaga hau, Jesũ akĩambĩrĩria kwarĩria kĩrĩndĩ ũhoro wa Johana, akĩmooria atĩrĩ: “Mwathiĩte werũ-inĩ kuona kĩ? Mwathiĩte kuona kamũrangi kainainagio nĩ rũhuho? <verse number="8" style="v"/>Akorwo ti ũguo-rĩ, mwathiĩte kuona kĩ? Hihi nĩ mũndũ wehumbĩte nguo njega? Aca, arĩa mehumbaga nguo njega makoragwo thĩinĩ wa nyũmba cia ũthamaki. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 1:76">Luk 1:76</ref></char></note>Mwagĩthiĩte kuona kĩ? Hihi mwathiĩte kuona mũnabii? Ĩĩ, ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, muonire mũndũ ũkĩrĩte mũnabii. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAL 3:1">Mal 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 1:2">Mar 1:2</ref></char></note>Ũyũ nĩwe ũhoro wake waandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘Nĩngũtũma mũtũmwo wakwa athiĩ mbere yaku,</para>
  <para style="q2">agagũthondekere njĩra yaku.’</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma: Harĩ andũ arĩa manaciarwo nĩ andũ-a-nja, gũtirĩ kuoneka mũndũ mũnene gũkĩra Johana Mũbatithania; no rĩrĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mũnini mũno ũthamaki-inĩ wa igũrũ-rĩ, nĩ mũnene kũmũkĩra. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Kuuma matukũ ma Johana Mũbatithania gwata rĩu, ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩũkoretwo ũkĩĩhatĩrĩria gũtheerema, nao andũ arĩa mehatagĩrĩria nĩo mawĩgwatagĩra na hinya. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 16:16">Luk 16:16</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Anabii othe, hamwe na Watho wa Musa, nĩmatũire marathaga ũhoro nginya hĩndĩ ya Johana. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAL 4:5">Mal 4:5</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 1:17">Luk 1:17</ref></char></note>Na angĩkorwo no mwende kwamũkĩra ũhoro ũcio-rĩ, ũcio nĩwe Elija ũrĩa werĩtwo nĩagooka. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 13:9">Math 13:9</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 13:43">43</ref>; <ref loc="REV 2:7">Kũg 2:7</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa ũrĩ na matũ ma kũigua nĩaigue.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>“Rĩu-rĩ, ingĩgerekania rũciaro rũrũ na kĩ? Rũhaana ta ciana ciikarĩte ndũnyũ igĩĩtaga iria ingĩ, igaciĩra atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>“ ‘Twamũhuhĩire mũtũrirũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũkĩaga kũina;</para>
  <para style="q1">o na twamũinĩire nyĩmbo cia macakaya,</para>
  <para style="q2">no mũtiacakaire.’</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:4">Math 3:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo Johana ookire atekũrĩa na atekũnyua, nao andũ makiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Arĩ na ndaimono.’ <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:11">Math 9:11</ref></char></note>Mũrũ wa Mũndũ ookire akĩrĩĩaga na akĩnyuuaga, nao makiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Onei mũndũ mũkoroku na mũrĩĩu, nĩ mũrata wa etia mbeeca cia igooti na “andũ ehia”.’ No ũũgĩ wonekaga nĩ wa ma nĩ ũndũ wa ciĩko ciaguo.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Haaro kũrĩ Matũũra Manene marĩa Materirĩte</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akĩambĩrĩria gũtetia matũũra manene marĩa maaringĩirwo ciama ciake iria nyingĩ, tondũ andũ akuo matiigana kwĩrira, akiuga atĩrĩ, <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 6:45">Mar 6:45</ref>; <ref loc="JOL 3:4">Joel 3:4</ref>; <ref loc="JON 3:5-9">Jon 3:5-9</ref></char></note>“Inyuĩ andũ a Korazini, kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ! O na inyuĩ andũ a Bethisaida, kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ! Nĩ ũndũ korwo ciama iria mwaringĩirwo nĩcio ciaringĩirwo andũ a Turo na Sidoni, mangĩeririre tene, mehumbĩte nguo cia makũnia na mehurĩrie mũhu mĩtwe. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:15">Math 10:15</ref></char></note>No ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, andũ a Turo na Sidoni nĩmagakorwo marĩ murũ mũthenya ũcio wa ciira gũkĩra inyuĩ. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 14:13-15">Isa 14:13-15</ref></char></note>Na inyuĩ, andũ a Kaperinaumu, nĩmũkambarario nginya matu-inĩ? Aca, mũkaaharũrũkio mũkinye kũrĩa kũriku mũno. Ciama iria mwaringĩirwo ingĩaringĩirwo Sodomu, nĩkũngĩtũũraga nginya ũmũthĩ. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:15">Math 10:15</ref></char></note>No ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, Sodomu nĩgũgakorwo murũ mũthenya ũcio wa ciira kũmũkĩra.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũhurũka kwa arĩa anogu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 22:42">Luk 22:42</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Baba, wee Mwathani wa igũrũ na thĩ, nĩngũkũgaatha tondũ nĩũhithĩte andũ arĩa oogĩ na marĩ na ũmenyo maũndũ maya, na ũkamaguũrĩria tũkenge. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Ĩĩ, Baba, nĩgũkorwo ũyũ nĩ wendi waku.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 28:18">Math 28:18</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:35">Joh 3:35</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:15">Joh 10:15</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩnengeretwo maũndũ mothe nĩ Baba. Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũũĩ Mũriũ tiga Ithe, na gũtirĩ mũndũ ũũĩ Ithe tiga Mũriũ, na arĩa Mũriũ, endaga kũguũrĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 7:37">Joh 7:37</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 33:14">Thaam 33:14</ref></char>
    </note>“Ũkai kũrĩ niĩ, inyuothe anogu na mũkuuĩte mĩrigo mĩritũ, na nĩngũmũhurũkia. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:15">Joh 13:15</ref>; <ref loc="JER 6:16">Jer 6:16</ref></char></note>Oyai icooki rĩakwa mwĩigĩrĩre na mwĩrute na niĩ, nĩgũkorwo ndĩ mũhooreri na mwĩnyiihia ngoro-inĩ, nacio ngoro cianyu nĩikũhurũkio. <verse number="30" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo icooki rĩakwa nĩ ihũthũ, na mũrigo wakwa nĩ mũhũthũ.”</para>
  <chapter number="12" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mwathani wa Thabatũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 23:25">Gũcook 23:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ihinda rĩu Jesũ nĩatuĩkanĩirie mĩgũnda-inĩ ya ngano mũthenya wa Thabatũ, na arutwo ake maarĩ ahũtu, na makĩambĩrĩria gũtua ngira cia ngano, magĩcirigitha, makĩrĩa ngano. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 12:10">Math 12:10</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 13:14">Luk 13:14</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 5:10">Joh 5:10</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa Afarisai moonire ũguo, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ta rora! Arutwo aku nĩmareeka ũrĩa watho ũtetĩkĩrĩtie gwĩkwo mũthenya wa Thabatũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 21:6">1Sam 21:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ mũtathomete ũrĩa Daudi eekire rĩrĩa we na arĩa maarĩ nake maarĩ ahũtu? <verse number="4" style="v"/>Aatoonyire nyũmba ya Ngai, na arĩ hamwe na arĩa maarĩ nake, makĩrĩa mĩgate ĩrĩa yamũrĩirwo Ngai ĩrĩa mateetĩkĩrĩtio kũrĩa nĩ watho, tiga no athĩnjĩri-Ngai meetĩkĩrĩtio kũmĩrĩa. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 28:9-10">Ndar 28:9-10</ref></char></note>O na ningĩ kaĩ mũthomete Watho-inĩ atĩ mũthenya wa Thabatũ, athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa marĩ thĩinĩ wa hekarũ nĩmathaahagia mũthenya ũcio na matituagwo ahĩtia? <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, ũmwe mũnene gũkĩra hekarũ arĩ haha. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HOS 6:6">Hos 6:6</ref></char></note>Korwo nĩmwamenyete gĩtũmi gĩa ciugo ici, atĩrĩ, ‘Kũiguanĩra tha nĩkuo nyendaga, no ti magongona,’ mũtingĩatuĩrĩire andũ mateehĩtie mahĩtia. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩwe Mwathani wa mũthenya wa Thabatũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Oima kũu-rĩ, agĩthiĩ agĩtoonya thunagogi yao, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 11:54">Luk 11:54</ref></char></note>na nĩ haarĩ mũndũ wonjete guoko. Na tondũ nĩmacaragia gĩtũmi gĩa gũthitangĩra Jesũ-rĩ, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Watho nĩwĩtĩkĩrĩtie kũhonania mũthenya wa Thabatũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nake akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nũũ wanyu ũngĩkorwo na ngʼondu, nayo ĩgwe irima mũthenya wa Thabatũ-rĩ, ũtangĩmĩruta irima? <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 6:26">Math 6:26</ref></char></note>Kaĩ mũndũ atakĩrĩ wa bata mũno gũkĩra ngʼondu! Nĩ ũndũ ũcio watho nĩwĩtĩkĩrĩtie gwĩka wega mũthenya wa Thabatũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Agĩcooka akĩĩra mũndũ ũcio atĩrĩ, “Tambũrũkia guoko gwaku.” Nake agĩtambũrũkia guoko, nakuo gũgĩtuĩka kũgima, o ta kũu kũngĩ. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 3:6">Mar 3:6</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:53">Joh 11:53</ref></char></note>No Afarisai makiuma nja, magĩcookania ndundu ya ũrĩa mangĩũragithia Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ndungata ya Ngai ĩrĩa Thuure</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ aamenya ũhoro ũcio, akĩehera kũu. Andũ aingĩ makĩmũrũmĩrĩra, nake akĩhonia arũaru ao othe, <verse number="16" style="v"/>agĩcooka akĩmakaania atĩ matikoige we nĩwe ũ. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Ũndũ ũyũ nĩguo wahingirie ũhoro ũrĩa waarĩtio na kanua ka mũnabii Isaia, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:17">Math 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:34">Joh 3:34</ref></char>
    </note>“Ĩno nĩyo ndungata yakwa ĩrĩa ndĩĩthuurĩire,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩrĩa nyendete, na nĩyo ĩkenagia ngoro yakwa;</para>
  <para style="q1">nĩngamĩitĩrĩria Roho wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo nĩĩkamenyithia ndũrĩrĩ ciira wa kĩhooto.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Ndĩgaatetania kana ĩgũũthũke;</para>
  <para style="q2">na gũtirĩ mũndũ ũkaigua mũgambo wayo njĩra-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>ndĩkoina kamũrangi kagondoku,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ĩhorie rũtambĩ rũrĩa rũgũtooga,</para>
  <para style="q1">nginya rĩrĩa ĩgaatũma itua rĩakwa rĩhootane.</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 42:14">Isa 42:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩayo ndũrĩrĩ nĩikaagĩa na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ na Beelizebuli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 4:24">Math 4:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Magĩcooka makĩmũrehera mũndũ warĩ na ndaimono, na aarĩ mũtumumu, na ndaaragia, nake Jesũ akĩmũhonia, akĩhota kwaria na kuona. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:27">Math 9:27</ref></char></note>Andũ othe makĩgega, makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ no akorwo arĩ we Mũrũ wa Daudi?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 9:34">Math 9:34</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩa Afarisai maaiguire ũguo, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ aingataga ndaimono na hinya wa Beelizebuli ũrĩa mũnene wa ndaimono.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 9:4">Math 9:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ aamenya ũrĩa meciiragia, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ũthamaki o wothe ũngĩgayũkana ũũkanĩrĩre guo mwene no ũharagane, narĩo itũũra o rĩothe kana nyũmba ĩngĩgayũkana ndĩngĩĩhaanda. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:10">Math 4:10</ref></char></note>Angĩkorwo Shaitani nĩwe ũingataga Shaitani-rĩ, nĩagayũkanĩte we mwene. Ũthamaki wake ũngĩkĩĩhaanda atĩa? <verse number="27" style="v"/>Na angĩkorwo niĩ nyiingataga ndaimono na hinya wa Beelizebuli-rĩ, nao andũ anyu maingataga ndaimono na hinya wa ũ? Nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo-rĩ, acio nĩo makaamũtuĩra ciira. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:2">Math 3:2</ref></char></note>No niĩ ingĩkorwo nyiingataga ndaimono na Roho wa Ngai-rĩ, ũthamaki wa Ngai nĩũkinyĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>“Ningĩ-rĩ, mũndũ aahota atĩa gũtoonya nyũmba ya mũndũ njamba na amũtunye indo ciake ataambĩte kuoha mũndũ ũcio njamba? Hĩndĩ ĩyo no rĩo angĩhota kũmũtunya indo cia nyũmba yake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>“Mũndũ ũrĩa ũtarĩ hamwe na niĩ, ũcio nĩ thũ yakwa, nake ũrĩa ũtacookanagĩrĩria hamwe na niĩ, ũcio nĩkũhurunja ahurunjaga. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 12:10">Luk 12:10</ref></char></note>Ningĩ ngũmwĩra atĩ, rĩĩhia o rĩothe o na kũruma Ngai, andũ no marekerwo, no mũndũ ũrĩa ũkaaruma Roho, ũcio ndakarekerwo. <verse number="32" style="v"/>Mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa ũgacaambia Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩakarekerwo, no ũrĩa wothe ũgaacambia Roho Mũtheru, ũcio ndakaarekerwo, ihinda rĩrĩ tũrĩ kana ihinda rĩrĩa rĩgooka.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 7:16">Math 7:16</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 7:17">17</ref></char>
    </note>“Agĩriai mũtĩ na maciaro maguo nĩmekwagĩra, kana mũthũkie mũtĩ na mũthũkie maciaro maguo mooru, nĩgũkorwo mũtĩ ũmenyekaga na maciaro maguo. <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:7">Math 3:7</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 6:45">Luk 6:45</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ rũciaro rũrũ rwa nduĩra, mwahota atĩa kwaria maũndũ mega, na mũrĩ ooru? Nĩgũkorwo kanua kaaragia maũndũ marĩa maiyũrĩte ngoro-inĩ. <verse number="35" style="v"/>Mũndũ mwega aaragia maũndũ mega moimĩte mũthiithũ-inĩ wake mwega, nake mũndũ mũũru aaragia maũndũ mooru moimĩte mũthiithũ-inĩ wake mũũru. <verse number="36" style="v"/>No ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, mũthenya wa itua rĩa ciira, andũ nĩmakaheana ũhoro wa ciugo ciothe cia tũhũ iria manaaria. <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 15:6">Ayub 15:6</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ciugo ciaku nĩcio igaatũma ũtuuo ndũrĩ na mahĩtia, na ciugo ciaku no cio igaatũma ũtuuo mũhĩtia.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Kĩama kĩa Jona</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 8:11">Mar 8:11</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 8:12">12</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 1:22">1Akor 1:22</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Afarisai amwe na arutani a watho makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũrutani, tũkwenda ũtũringĩre kĩama.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:39 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:4">Math 16:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Rũciaro rwaganu na rwa ũtharia rũrenda rũringĩrwo kĩama! No gũtirĩ kĩama rũkũringĩrwo tiga o kĩama kĩrĩa kĩa mũnabii Jona. <verse number="40" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:40 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 8:20">Math 8:20</ref>; <ref loc="JON 1:17">Jon 1:17</ref></char></note>Nĩ gũkorwo o ta ũrĩa Jona aikarire matukũ matatũ, mũthenya na ũtukũ, arĩ nda ya thamaki ĩrĩa nene, ũguo noguo Mũrũ wa Mũndũ agaikara matukũ matatũ, mũthenya na ũtukũ, arĩ tĩĩri-inĩ. <verse number="41" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:41 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JON 3:5">Jon 3:5</ref></char></note>Andũ a Nineve nĩmakarũgama hĩndĩ ya ciira hamwe na rũciaro rũrũ marũtuĩre ciira; nĩgũkorwo nĩmeririre rĩrĩa maahunjĩirio nĩ Jona, na rĩu ũmwe mũnene gũkĩra Jona arĩ haha. <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1KI 10:1">1Ath 10:1</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 9:1">2Maũ 9:1</ref></char></note>Mũthamaki mũndũ-wa-nja wa mwena wa Gũthini nĩakarũgama hĩndĩ ya ciira hamwe na rũciaro rũrũ arũtuĩre ciira; nĩgũkorwo nĩoimire ituri cia thĩ oke athikĩrĩrie ũũgĩ wa Solomoni, na rĩu ũmwe mũnene gũkĩra Solomoni arĩ haha.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>“Na rĩrĩ, roho mũũru woima thĩinĩ wa mũndũ, ũtuĩkanagĩria werũ-inĩ ũgĩcaria ũhurũko, na ũkaaga. <verse number="44" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo ũkoiga atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩngũcooka nyũmba ĩrĩa ndoimire.’ Na wacooka-rĩ, ũgakora nyũmba ĩyo ĩrĩ theri, ĩrĩ haate, ĩgathera na ĩgathondekwo wega. <verse number="45" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:45 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 2:20">2Pet 2:20</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo roho ũcio ũkagĩĩra maroho mangĩ mũgwanja mooru makĩria maguo mwene, magatoonya magaikara kũu. Naguo mũikarĩre wa mũndũ ũcio ũgathũka gũkĩra wa mbere. Ũguo nĩguo gũkahaana kũrĩ rũciaro rũrũ rwaganu.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Nyina wa Jesũ na Ariũ a Nyina</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:46 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:55">Math 13:55</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 2:12">Joh 2:12</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 1:14">Atũm 1:14</ref></char>
    </note>O hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ aaragĩria andũ-rĩ, nyina na ariũ a nyina makĩrũgama nja makĩenda kwaria nake. <verse number="47" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ ũmwe akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Maitũguo na ariũ a maitũguo marũngiĩ haha nja, makĩenda kwaria nawe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Maitũ nũũ, na ariũ a maitũ nĩ a?” <verse number="49" style="v"/>Agĩcooka akĩorota arutwo ake, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Aya nĩo maitũ na ariũ a maitũ. <verse number="50" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:50 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 15:14">Joh 15:14</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ wothe wĩkaga ũrĩa Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ endaga, ũcio nĩwe mũrũ na mwarĩ wa maitũ, na nĩ we maitũ.”</para>
  <chapter number="13" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Mũhuri wa Mbeũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Mũthenya o ro ũcio-rĩ, Jesũ nĩoimire nyũmba agĩthiĩ agĩikara thĩ hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 5:3">Luk 5:3</ref></char></note>Ikundi cia andũ aingĩ mũno ikĩũngana harĩa aarĩ nginya ĩgĩtũma atoonye gatarũ na agĩikara thĩ thĩinĩ wayo, nao andũ acio othe makĩrũgama hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nake akĩmaruta maũndũ maingĩ na ngerekano, akĩmeera atĩrĩ: “Mũrĩmi nĩoimagarire akahure mbeũ ciake. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa aahuraga mbeũ icio-rĩ, imwe ikĩgũa mũkĩra-inĩ wa njĩra, nacio nyoni igĩũka ĩgĩcirĩa. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Ingĩ ikĩgũa rũnyanjara-inĩ kũrĩa gũtaarĩ na tĩĩri mũingĩ. Nacio ikĩmera o narua tondũ tĩĩri ndwarĩ mũriku. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa riũa rĩarire, rĩgĩcina mĩmera ĩyo, nayo ĩkĩũma tondũ ndĩarĩ na mĩri. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Na mbeũ ingĩ ikĩgũa mĩigua-inĩ, nayo mĩigua ĩgĩkũra, ĩgĩthararia mbeũ icio rĩrĩa ciamerire. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 26:12">Kĩam 26:12</ref></char></note>Ingĩ nacio ikĩgũa tĩĩri-inĩ ũrĩa mũnoru, ikĩgĩa na maciaro imwe ĩgĩciara maita igana, iria ingĩ igĩciara maita mĩrongo ĩtandatũ, na iria ingĩ igĩciara maita mĩrongo ĩtatũ ma iria ciahaandirwo. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 11:15">Math 11:15</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa ũrĩ na matũ ma kũigua, nĩaigue.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nao arutwo ake magĩũka kũrĩ we, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Waragĩria andũ na ngerekano nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 2:10">1Akor 2:10</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 2:14">14</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 2:20">1Joh 2:20</ref>, <ref loc="1JN 2:27">27</ref></char>
    </note>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ nĩmũheetwo ũmenyo wa kũmenya hitho cia ũthamaki wa igũrũ, no-o matiheetwo. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 25:29">Math 25:29</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe ũrĩ na indo nĩakoongererwo nyingĩ aingĩhie makĩria. Nake ũrĩa wothe ũtarĩ, nĩagatuunywo o na kĩrĩa arĩ nakĩo. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 5:21">Jer 5:21</ref></char></note>Gĩkĩ nĩkĩo gĩtũmaga ndĩmaarĩrie na ngerekano:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Nĩ ũndũ o na gũkorwo nĩmoonaga-rĩ, mationaga;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũkorwo nĩmaiguaga-rĩ, matiiguaga kana makamenya.</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nĩo makinyĩirwo nĩ ũhoro ũrĩa warathirwo nĩ mũnabii Isaia, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘Kũigua mũgũtũũra mũiguaga, no mũtikaamenya ũndũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">kuona mũgũtũũra muonaga, no mũtigakuũkĩrwo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 6:9">Isa 6:9</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 6:10">10</ref></char>
    </note>“ ‘Nĩgũkorwo ngoro cia andũ aya nĩ ngingitaru;</para>
  <para style="q2">matũ mao matiiguaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩmahingĩte maitho mao.</para>
  <para style="q1">Tondũ maahota kuona na maitho mao,</para>
  <para style="q2">na maigue na matũ mao,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ngoro ciao igĩe na ũmenyo,</para>
  <para style="q1">manjookerere, na niĩ ndĩmahonie.’</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:17">Math 16:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No kũrathimwo nĩ maitho manyu tondũ nĩmoonaga, na matũ manyu tondũ nĩmaiguaga. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 11:13">Ahib 11:13</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:10-12">1Pet 1:10-12</ref></char></note>Tondũ ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, anabii na andũ aingĩ athingu nĩmerirĩirie kuona maũndũ marĩa mũrona no-o matiamonire, na nĩmerirĩirie kũigua maũndũ marĩa mũraigua no matiamaiguire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ta iguai ngĩtaarĩria ũhoro wa ngerekano ĩyo ya mũhuri wa mbeũ: <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:37">Math 5:37</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũndũ o wothe aigua ndũmĩrĩri ya ũthamaki na akaaga kũmĩmenya-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩyo ũrĩa mũũru okaga akamũtunya kĩrĩa kĩhaande ngoro-inĩ yake. Ĩno nĩyo mbeũ ĩrĩa yahurirwo mũkĩra-inĩ wa njĩra. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Ũrĩa wamũkĩrire mbeũ ĩrĩa yagũire rũnyanjara-inĩ nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũiguaga kiugo, na o rĩmwe agakĩamũkĩra arĩ na gĩkeno. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 11:6">Math 11:6</ref></char></note>No tondũ ndarĩ mĩri-rĩ, aikaraga o kahinda kanini. Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa thĩĩna woka, kana kwagĩa na kĩnyariirano nĩ ũndũ wa kiugo-rĩ, agagĩtiganĩria o narua. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 19:23">Math 19:23</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:9">1Tim 6:9</ref>, <ref loc="1TI 6:10">10</ref>, <ref loc="1TI 6:17">17</ref></char></note>Nake ũrĩa wamũkagĩra mbeũ ĩrĩa yagũire mĩigua-inĩ-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũiguaga kiugo, no mĩhangʼo ya mũtũũrĩre ũyũ, na kũheenererio nĩ ũtonga, igagĩthararia, ikagiria kĩgĩe na maciaro. <verse number="23" style="v"/>No ũrĩa wamũkĩrire mbeũ ĩrĩa yagũire tĩĩri-inĩ ũrĩa mũnoru-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũiguaga kiugo, na agakĩmenya. Nake agaciara maciaro, ũmwe akaruta maita igana, ũngĩ maita mĩrongo ĩtandatũ, na ũngĩ maita mĩrongo ĩtatũ ma mbeũ ĩrĩa yahaandĩtwo.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Riya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 4:26">Mar 4:26</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 4:30">30</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Jesũ akĩmahe ngerekano ĩngĩ, akĩmeera atĩrĩ: “Ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũhaana ta mũndũ ũrĩa wahaandire mbeũ njega mũgũnda wake. <verse number="25" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa andũ othe maakomete-rĩ, thũ yake ĩgĩũka, ĩkĩhura itindiĩ thĩinĩ wa ngano, na ĩgĩĩthiĩra. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ngano yamerire na igĩciara-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩyo itindiĩ o narĩo rĩkĩonekana.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>“Ndungata cia mwene mũgũnda igĩũka kũrĩ we, ikĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathi witũ, githĩ ndwahaandire mbeũ njega mũgũnda waku? Kaĩ itindiĩ rĩkiumĩte kũ?’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>“Agĩcookia atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩ mũndũ ũrĩ ũthũ na niĩ wekire ũguo.’</para>
  <para style="p">“Ndungata icio ikĩmũũria atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩũkwenda tũthiĩ, tũkarĩmunye?’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>“Nake agĩcookia atĩrĩ, ‘Aca, tondũ mũkĩmunya itindiĩ rĩu, mwahota kũrĩmunyanĩria na ngano. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:12">Math 3:12</ref></char></note>Rekei ikũranĩre nginya hĩndĩ ya magetha. Hĩndĩ ĩyo-rĩ, nĩngeera agethi atĩrĩ: Ambai mũmunye itindiĩ na mũrĩohe itĩĩa, nĩguo rĩcinwo; mũcooke mũcookanĩrĩrie ngano, mũmĩige ikũmbĩ rĩakwa.’ ”</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Mbeũ ya Karatarĩ, na ya Ndawa ya Kũimbia Mĩgate</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 17:6">Luk 17:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩamaheire ngerekano ĩngĩ, akĩmeera atĩrĩ: “Ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũtariĩ ta mbeũ ya karatarĩ, ĩrĩa mũndũ oire akĩhaanda mũgũnda wake. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 17:23">Ezek 17:23</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 4:12">Dan 4:12</ref></char></note>O na akorwo mbeũ ĩyo nĩyo nini mũno kũrĩ mbeũ ciothe-rĩ, rĩrĩa yakũra, nĩĩnenehaga kũrĩ mĩmera ĩrĩa ĩngĩ ya mũgũnda na ĩgatuĩka mũtĩ, nacio nyoni cia rĩera-inĩ igooka igaaka itara honge-inĩ ciaguo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 18:6">Kĩam 18:6</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 5:9">Agal 5:9</ref></char>
    </note>Agĩcooka akĩmahe ngerekano o ĩngĩ, akĩmeera atĩrĩ: “Ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũhaana ta ndawa ya kũimbia mĩgate ĩrĩa mũndũ-wa-nja oire na akĩmĩtukania na mũtu mũingĩ o nginya mũtu ũcio wothe ũkĩimbio nĩyo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 16:25">Joh 16:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ aaragĩria kĩrĩndĩ maũndũ macio mothe na ngerekano na ndaamaragĩria ũndũ o na ũmwe atekũhũthĩra ngerekano. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 78:2">Thab 78:2</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 2:7">1Akor 2:7</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 1:26">1:26</ref></char></note>Nĩguo ũhoro ũrĩa waaririo na kanua ka mũnabii ũhinge rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ngaatumũra kanua gakwa njarie na ngerekano,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩngaaria maũndũ marĩa matũire marĩ mahithe kuuma rĩrĩa thĩ yombirwo.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũtaarĩria Ngerekano ya Itindiĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 15:15">Math 15:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo agĩtiga kĩrĩndĩ, agĩtoonya nyũmba. Arutwo ake magĩũka kũrĩ we, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Tũtaarĩrie ngerekano ya itindiĩ rĩrĩa rĩarĩ thĩinĩ wa mũgũnda.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũrĩa wahaandire mbeũ njega nĩ Mũrũ wa Mũndũ. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:44-45">Joh 8:44-45</ref></char></note>Mũgũnda nĩ thĩ, nayo mbeũ njega nĩcio ciana cia ũthamaki. Itindiĩ nĩ ciana cia ũrĩa mũũru, <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOL 3:13">Joel 3:13</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 24:3">Math 24:3</ref>; <ref loc="REV 14:15">Kũg 14:15</ref></char></note>nayo thũ ĩrĩa ĩrĩhaandaga nĩ ũrĩa mũũru. Magetha nĩ ithirĩro rĩa mahinda maya, na agethi nĩ araika.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio o ta ũrĩa itindiĩ rĩmunyagwo rĩgacinwo na mwaki-rĩ, ũguo noguo gũkahaana hĩndĩ ya ithirĩro rĩa mahinda maya. <verse number="41" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:41 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 24:31">Math 24:31</ref></char></note>Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩagatũma araika ake, na nĩmakeheria maũndũ mothe marĩa marehaga mehia na andũ arĩa othe mekaga ũũru ũthamaki-inĩ wake. <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 8:12">Math 8:12</ref></char></note>Nĩmakamaikia thĩinĩ wa icua rĩa mwaki, kũrĩa gũgaakorwo kĩrĩro na kũhagarania magego. <verse number="43" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:43 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DAN 12:3">Dan 12:3</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 11:15">Math 11:15</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo arĩa athingu magaakenga ta riũa thĩinĩ wa ũthamaki wa Ithe wao. Ũrĩa ũrĩ na matũ nĩ aigue.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Mũthiithũ Mũhithe, na Ruru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:44 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 55:1">Isa 55:1</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 3:7">Afil 3:7</ref>, <ref loc="PHP 3:8">8</ref></char>
    </note>“Ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũhaanaine na mũthiithũ wahithĩtwo mũgũnda. Na rĩrĩa mũndũ aawoonire, akĩũhitha rĩngĩ, na nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa akenete, agĩthiĩ akĩendia indo ciothe iria arĩ nacio akĩgũra mũgũnda ũcio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>“Ningĩ ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũhaanaine na mwonjorithia wacaragia ruru njega. <verse number="46" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa oonire ĩmwe ya thogora mũnene-rĩ, agĩthiĩ akĩendia indo ciake ciothe iria aarĩ nacio, akĩmĩgũra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Neti</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:47 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 22:10">Math 22:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“O rĩngĩ, ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũhaanaine na neti ĩrĩa yaikirio iria-inĩ, nayo ĩgĩtega thamaki cia mĩthemba yothe. <verse number="48" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa yaiyũrire, ategi acio a thamaki makĩmĩguucia hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria. Hĩndĩ ĩyo magĩikara thĩ, magĩthuura thamaki iria njega, magĩciĩkĩra ikabũ-inĩ, no iria njũru magĩcite. <verse number="49" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:49 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 25:32">Math 25:32</ref></char></note>Ũguo nĩguo gũgaakorwo hĩndĩ ya ithirĩro rĩa mahinda maya. Araika nĩmagooka maamũranie arĩa aaganu kuuma kũrĩ arĩa athingu, <verse number="50" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:50 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 8:12">Math 8:12</ref></char></note>na maikie arĩa aaganu icua-inĩ rĩa mwaki, kũrĩa gũgaakorwo na kĩrĩro na kũhagarania magego.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v"/>Jesũ akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nĩmwataũkĩrwo nĩ maũndũ macio mothe?”</para>
  <para style="p">Magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ, nĩtwataũkĩrwo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v"/>Akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, mũrutani wa watho o wothe ũrĩa ũrutĩtwo ũhoro wa ũthamaki wa igũrũ-rĩ, ahaanaine na mwene nyũmba ũrĩa ũrutaga mũthiithũ-inĩ wake indo iria njerũ o na iria ngũrũ.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũnabii ũtarĩ Mũtĩĩe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:53 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 7:28">Math 7:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ aarĩkia kũheana ngerekano icio-rĩ, akiuma kũu. <verse number="54" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:54 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:23">Math 4:23</ref></char></note>Aakinya itũũra rĩa kwao-rĩ, akĩambĩrĩria kũrutana thunagogi-inĩ ciao, nao makĩgega. Makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ arutĩte kũ ũũgĩ ũyũ na ciĩko ici cia hinya? <verse number="55" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:55 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:42">Joh 6:42</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:46">Math 12:46</ref></char></note>Githĩ ũyũ ti we mũrũ wa mũtharamara? Githĩ rĩĩtwa rĩa nyina ti Mariamu, na githĩ ariũ a nyina ti Jakubu, na Jusufu, na Simoni, na Juda? <verse number="56" style="v"/>Na githĩ aarĩ a nyina othe tũtirĩ nao? Mũndũ ũyũ akĩrutĩte maũndũ maya mothe kũ?” <verse number="57" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:57 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 4:44">Joh 4:44</ref></char></note>Nao makĩmũrega.</para>
  <para style="p">No Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Kũndũ mũnabii ataheagwo gĩtĩĩo no itũũra-inĩ rĩake na gwake mũciĩ.” <verse number="58" style="v"/>Nake ndaaringire ciama nyingĩ kũu, tondũ wa ũrĩa maagĩte gwĩtĩkia.</para>
  <chapter number="14" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Johana Mũbatithania Kũrengwo Mũtwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 8:15">Mar 8:15</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 9:7-9">Luk 9:7-9</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩyo, Mũthamaki Herode nĩaiguire ngumo ya Jesũ, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:1">Math 3:1</ref></char></note>nake akĩĩra arĩa maamũtungataga atĩrĩ, “Ũcio nĩ Johana Mũbatithania; nĩ ariũkĩte kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ! Nĩkĩo arĩ na hinya mũnene ũguo wa kũringa ciama.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 3:19-20">Luk 3:19-20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, Herode nĩanyiitĩte Johana akamuoha, na akamũikia njeera nĩ ũndũ wa Herodia, ũrĩa warĩ mũtumia wa mũrũ wa nyina Filipu, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 18:16">Alaw 18:16</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 20:21">20:21</ref></char></note>tondũ Johana nĩamwĩrĩte atĩrĩ: “Watho ndũgwĩtĩkĩrĩtie ũmũhikie.” <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 17:9">Math 17:9</ref></char></note>Herode nĩendaga kũũraga Johana, no nĩetigagĩra andũ, tondũ nĩmeetĩkĩtie atĩ Johana aarĩ mũnabii.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Mũthenya wa gũkũngũĩra gũciarwo kwa Herode-rĩ, mwarĩ wa Herodia nĩainĩire andũ, na agĩkenia Herode mũno. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Herode akĩĩhĩta na mwĩhĩtwa atĩ nĩekũmũhe kĩrĩa gĩothe angĩendire. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Nake mũirĩtu ũcio aarĩkia gũtaarwo nĩ nyina, akiuga atĩrĩ, “He mũtwe wa Johana Mũbatithania o rĩu ũrĩ thĩinĩ wa kiuga.” <verse number="9" style="v"/>Mũthamaki nĩataangĩkire mũno, no nĩ ũndũ wa mwĩhĩtwa wake, na ageni arĩa maarĩ iruga-inĩ rĩake-rĩ, agĩathana atĩ mũirĩtu ũcio aheo kĩrĩa eetĩtie. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 17:12">Math 17:12</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio agĩtũmana kũu njeera na Johana akĩrengwo mũtwe. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Naguo mũtwe ũcio wake ũkĩrehwo na kiuga, ũkĩnengerwo mũirĩtu ũcio, nake akĩũtwarĩra nyina. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 8:2">Atũm 8:2</ref></char></note>Nao arutwo a Johana magĩthiĩ makĩoya kĩimba gĩake, magĩgĩthika, magĩcooka magĩthiĩ makĩĩra Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhũũnia Andũ Ngiri Ithano</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ aiguire ũhoro ũcio, akiuma kũu ahaicĩte gatarũ andũ matekũmenya, agĩthiĩ handũ hataarĩ na andũ. Nakĩo kĩrĩndĩ kĩaigua ũguo-rĩ, gĩkiuma matũũra-inĩ gĩkĩmũrũmĩrĩra na magũrũ. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:36">Math 9:36</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ oimire gatarũ na akĩona andũ aingĩ, akĩmaiguĩra tha, na akĩhonia arũaru ao.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Na gwakuhĩrĩria gũtuka-rĩ, arutwo ake magĩthiĩ harĩ we, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Gũkũ nĩ kũndũ gũtarĩ mĩciĩ, na nĩkũratuka. Ĩra andũ aya mathiĩ, nĩgeetha makegũrĩre irio tũtũũra-inĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Hatirĩ bata wa mathiĩ. Mahei gĩa kũrĩa inyuĩ ene.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:9">Math 16:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Haha tũrĩ na mĩgate ĩtano tu na thamaki igĩrĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ndeherai haha.” <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1SA 9:14">1Sam 9:14</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 24:30">Luk 24:30</ref></char></note>Nake agĩathana andũ maikare thĩ nyeki-inĩ. Akĩoya mĩgate ĩyo ĩtano na thamaki icio igĩrĩ, akĩrora igũrũ, agĩcookia ngaatho, akĩenyũranga mĩgate ĩyo. Agĩcooka akĩmĩnengera arutwo, nao arutwo makĩhe andũ. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Othe makĩrĩa makĩhũũna, nao arutwo makĩũngania cienyũ iria ciatigarĩte makĩiyũria ciondo ikũmi na igĩrĩ. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Mũigana wa andũ arĩa maarĩire maarĩ ta arũme ngiri ithano, andũ-a-nja na ciana matatarĩtwo.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũgerera Maaĩ Igũrũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>O hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akĩĩra arutwo ake matoonye gatarũ, mathiĩ mbere yake mũrĩmo ũrĩa ũngĩ wa iria mũira wa oigĩre kĩrĩndĩ ũhoro. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 3:21">Luk 3:21</ref></char></note>Thuutha wa kũmoigĩra ũhoro-rĩ, akĩambata kĩrĩma-inĩ arĩ wiki nĩguo akahooe. Na gũgĩtuka aarĩ o ho wiki, <verse number="24" style="v"/>no gatarũ nĩkarĩkĩtie gũthiĩ itĩĩna iraiharaihu kuuma thĩ nyũmũ, gakĩhũũragwo nĩ makũmbĩ ma maaĩ tondũ kerekeire na kũrĩa rũhuho ruoimaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, ta thaa kenda cia ũtukũ-rĩ, Jesũ agĩthiĩ kũrĩ o agereire maaĩ igũrũ. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:37">Luk 24:37</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa arutwo maamuonire agĩthiĩ agereire maaĩ igũrũ, makĩnyiitwo nĩ guoya, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Ĩrĩa nĩ ngoma,” na magĩkaya nĩ gwĩtigĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 9:2">Math 9:2</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 10:12">Dan 10:12</ref>; <ref loc="REV 1:17">Kũg 1:17</ref></char>
    </note>No hĩndĩ o ĩyo Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ũmĩrĩriai! Nĩ niĩ. Tigai gwĩtigĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Petero akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, akorwo nĩwe-rĩ, njĩĩra njũke kũrĩ we ngereire maaĩ igũrũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ũka.”</para>
  <para style="p">Hĩndĩ ĩyo, Petero akiuma gatarũ, agĩthiĩ agereire maaĩ igũrũ erekeire harĩ Jesũ. <verse number="30" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa oonire rũhuho, agĩĩtigĩra, na akĩambĩrĩria gũtoonyerera maaĩ-inĩ, agĩkaya, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, honokia!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 6:30">Math 6:30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O rĩmwe, Jesũ agĩtambũrũkia guoko, akĩmũnyiita, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Wee kaĩ ũrĩ na wĩtĩkio mũnini-ĩ! Wagĩa na nganja nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maahaicire gatarũ-rĩ, rũhuho rũgĩtiga kũhurutana. <verse number="33" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo arĩa maarĩ thĩinĩ wa gatarũ makĩmũgooca, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩ ma wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>Na maarĩkia kũringa mũrĩmo ũrĩa ũngĩ, magĩkinya bũrũri wa Genesareti. <verse number="35" style="v"/>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ a kũu maamenyire atĩ nĩ Jesũ, makĩhunjia ũhoro ngʼongo ciothe iria ciamarigiicĩirie. Nao makĩmũrehera andũ othe arĩa maarĩ arũaru, <verse number="36" style="v"/>na makĩmũthaitha areke arũaru mahutie gĩcũrĩ kĩa nguo yake, na arĩa othe maamũhutirie makĩhonio.</para>
  <chapter number="15" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ũhoro wa Thaahu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, thuutha ũcio Afarisai amwe na arutani a watho magĩũka kũrĩ Jesũ moimĩte Jerusalemu, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 11:38">Luk 11:38</ref></char></note>“Nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga arutwo aku mathũkie kĩrĩra gĩa athuuri? Matiĩthambaga moko rĩrĩa mekũrĩa irio!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Na inyuĩ mũthũkagia watho wa Ngai nĩ ũndũ wa irĩra cianyu nĩkĩ? <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 20:12">Thaam 20:12</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 20:9">Alaw 20:9</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Ngai oigire atĩrĩ, ‘Tĩĩa thoguo na nyũkwa’ na ‘Mũndũ wa kũruma ithe kana nyina no nginya ooragwo.’ <verse number="5" style="v"/>No inyuĩ muugaga atĩ mũndũ angĩĩra ithe kana nyina atĩrĩ, ‘Ũteithio ũrĩa ingĩagũteithia naguo, nĩ kĩheo kĩamũrĩre Ngai,’ <verse number="6" style="v"/>mũndũ ũcio ndarĩ bata wa ‘gũtĩĩa ithe’ naguo. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũgagĩtua kiugo kĩa Ngai gĩa tũhũ nĩ ũndũ wa kĩrĩra kĩanyu. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Inyuĩ hinga ici! Isaia nĩamenyete wega hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aarathire ũhoro wanyu, akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>“ ‘Andũ aya maaheaga gĩtĩĩo na mĩromo,</para>
  <para style="q2">no ngoro ciao irĩ kũraya na niĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 2:20-22">Akol 2:20-22</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 29:13">Isa 29:13</ref></char>
    </note>Nao maahooyaga o tũhũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">morutani marĩa marutanaga no mawatho ma andũ.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ agĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ kĩu gĩũke harĩ we, agĩkĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Thikĩrĩriai na mũtaũkĩrwo. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 10:14-15">Atũm 10:14-15</ref></char></note>Kĩrĩa gĩtoonyaga na kanua ka mũndũ ti kĩo ‘kĩmũthaahagia’, no kĩrĩa kiumaga kanua gake nĩkĩo ‘kĩmũthaahagia.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Na hĩndĩ ĩyo arutwo ake magĩthiĩ harĩ we, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩũĩ atĩ Afarisai nĩmararakarire rĩrĩa maraiguire ũhoro ũcio?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 60:21">Isa 60:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũmera o wothe ũtaahandĩtwo nĩ Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ nĩũkamunywo na mĩri. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 23:16">Math 23:16</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 23:24">24</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 6:39">Luk 6:39</ref></char></note>Tiganai nao; acio nĩ atongoria atumumu. Mũtumumu angĩtongoria mũtumumu ũngĩ, eerĩ no kũgũa mangĩgũa irima.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:36">Math 13:36</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Petero akiuga atĩrĩ, “Tũtaũrĩre ngerekano ĩyo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:9">Math 16:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “O na inyuĩ mũtirĩ mũrataũkĩrwo o na rĩu? <verse number="17" style="v"/>Kaĩ mũtooĩ atĩ kĩndũ kĩrĩa gĩtoonyaga na kanua gĩthiiaga nda, gĩgacooka gĩkoima mwĩrĩ? <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 12:34">Math 12:34</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 3:6">Jak 3:6</ref></char></note>No maũndũ marĩa moimaga kanua moimaga ngoro-inĩ, na nĩmo ‘mathaahagia’ mũndũ. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 5:19-21">Agal 5:19-21</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ngoro-inĩ nĩkuo kuumaga meciiria mooru, na ũragani, na ũtharia, na ũhũũri maraya, na ũici, na kũiganĩrĩra igenyo, na njambanio. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 14:14">Arom 14:14</ref></char></note>Macio nĩmo maũndũ marĩa ‘mathaahagia’ mũndũ; no kũrĩa irio na moko matarĩ mathambie matingĩtũma mũndũ agĩe na ‘thaahu’.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Wĩtĩkio wa Mũndũ-wa-Nja Mũkaanani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 11:21">Math 11:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ Jesũ akiuma kũu, agĩthiĩ ndeere-inĩ cia Turo na Sidoni. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:27">Math 9:27</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:24">Math 4:24</ref></char></note>Mũndũ-wa-nja Mũkaanani woimĩte gũkuhĩ na kũu agĩũka kũrĩ we, akĩmũkayagĩra, akiugaga atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, Mũrũ wa Daudi, njiguĩra tha! Mũirĩtu wakwa nĩarathĩĩnio mũno nĩ ndaimono.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>No Jesũ ndarĩ ũndũ o na ũmwe oigire. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio arutwo ake magĩthiĩ kũrĩ we makĩmũringĩrĩria, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwĩre athiĩ, tondũ nĩaratũrũmĩrĩra agĩkayaga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:6">Math 10:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Ndaatũmirwo o kũrĩ ngʼondu cia nyũmba ya Isiraeli iria ciũrĩte tu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 8:2">Math 8:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake mũndũ-wa-nja ũcio agĩũka, akĩmũturĩria ndu, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ndeithia!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Gũtiagĩrĩire kuoya mũgate wa ciana ũikĩrie ngui.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15:26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ayahudi meetaga andũ-a-Ndũrĩrĩ “Ngui” nĩ ũndũ wa kũmamena.</char></note></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ-wa-nja ũcio akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ nĩguo Mwathani; no o na ngui nĩirĩĩaga rũitĩki rũrĩa rũgũaga kuuma metha-inĩ ya mwene cio.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 9:22">Math 9:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũtumia ũyũ, wĩtĩkio waku nĩ mũnene! Ihooya rĩaku nĩrĩahingio.” Nake mwarĩ akĩhonio ithaa o rĩu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ kũhe Andũ Ngiri Inya Irio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Jesũ akiuma kũu, agĩthiĩ agereire hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria rĩa Galili, agĩcooka akĩambata kĩrĩma-inĩ, agĩikara thĩ. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:23">Math 4:23</ref></char></note>Nakĩo kĩrĩndĩ kĩnene gĩgĩũka kũrĩ we, gĩkĩmũrehera andũ arĩa maathuaga, na atumumu, na arĩa maarĩ onju na arĩa mataaragia, na angĩ aingĩ, makĩmaiga magũrũ-inĩ make; nake akĩmahonia. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:8">Math 9:8</ref></char></note>Nao andũ makĩgega rĩrĩa moonire arĩa mataaragia makĩaria, na arĩa onju mahonetio, na arĩa maathuaga magĩĩtwara, na atumumu makĩona. Nao makĩgooca Ngai wa Isiraeli.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 9:36">Math 9:36</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ agĩĩta arutwo ake moke harĩ we, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩndĩraiguĩra andũ aya tha tondũ makoretwo hamwe na niĩ mĩthenya ĩtatũ, na matirĩ na kĩndũ gĩa kũrĩa. Ndikwenda mathiĩ marĩ ahũtu, tondũ maahota kũringĩkĩra njĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>Nao arutwo ake magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Tũngĩruta kũ mĩgate ya kũhũũnia kĩrĩndĩ ta gĩkĩ, gũkũ werũ-inĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmooria, atĩrĩ, “Mũrĩ na mĩgate ĩigana?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Tũrĩ na mĩgate mũgwanja, na tũthamaki tũnini tũtarĩ tũingĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>Nake akĩĩra kĩrĩndĩ kĩu gĩikare thĩ. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 14:9">Math 14:9</ref></char></note>Agĩcooka akĩoya mĩgate ĩyo mũgwanja na tũthamaki tũu, na aarĩkia gũcookia ngaatho-rĩ, akĩmĩenyũranga, akĩmĩnengera arutwo nao makĩhe andũ. <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:10">Math 16:10</ref></char></note>Othe makĩrĩa makĩhũũna. Thuutha ũcio arutwo makĩũngania cienyũ iria ciatigarĩte makĩiyũria ciondo mũgwanja. <verse number="38" style="v"/>Mũigana wa andũ arĩa maarĩire maarĩ andũ ngiri inya, andũ-a-nja na ciana matatarĩtwo. <verse number="39" style="v"/>Jesũ aarĩkia kuugĩra kĩrĩndĩ ũhoro, agĩtoonya gatarũ, agĩthiĩ mwena wa Magadani.</para>
  <chapter number="16" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũũrio Aringe Kĩama</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 4:1">Atũm 4:1</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:38">Math 12:38</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, Afarisai na Asadukai magĩũka kũrĩ Jesũ, makĩmũgeria na kũmwĩra amaringĩre kĩama kiumĩte igũrũ makĩone.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa gwatuka, muugaga atĩrĩ, ‘Kaĩ nĩgũkaara-ĩ, tondũ igũrũ nĩ gũtune’. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 12:54-56">Luk 12:54-56</ref></char></note>Ningĩ rũciinĩ muugaga atĩrĩ, ‘Ũmũthĩ nĩgũkũgĩa kĩhuhũkanio, tondũ igũrũ nĩ gũtune na gũgathimba.’ Nĩmũũĩ gũtaũra ũrĩa igũrũ rĩtariĩ, no mũtingĩhota gũtaũra imenyithia cia mahinda maya tũrĩ. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 12:39">Math 12:39</ref></char></note>Rũciaro rũrũ rwaganu na rwa ũtharia rũũragia rũringĩrwo kĩama, no gũtirĩ kĩama rũkũringĩrwo tiga kĩama kĩrĩa kĩa Jona.” Nake Jesũ akĩmatiga, agĩĩthiĩra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ndawa ya Kũimbia Mĩgate ya Afarisai na Asadukai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa maaringire iria, arutwo ake magĩkorwo nĩmariganĩirwo nĩgũkuua mĩgate. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 12:1">Luk 12:1</ref></char></note>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mwĩmenyererei, na mwĩhũgage ndawa ya kũimbia mĩgate ya Afarisai na Asadukai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nao makĩaranĩria, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Hihi nĩ tondũ tũtinoka na mĩgate.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 6:30">Math 6:30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ aamenya ũrĩa meeranaga, akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ a wĩtĩkio mũnini, nĩ kĩĩ kĩratũma mwaranĩrie ũhoro wa kwaga mĩgate? <verse number="9" style="v"/>Kaĩ mũtarĩ mwataũkĩrwo? Mũtingĩririkana mĩgate ĩtano ĩrĩa yarĩirwo nĩ andũ ngiri ithano, na nĩ ciondo ciigana muonganirie? <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 15:34-38">Math 15:34-38</ref></char></note>Kana mĩgate mũgwanja ĩrĩa yarĩirwo nĩ andũ ngiri inya, na nĩ ciondo ciigana muonganirie? <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩ kĩĩ kĩragiria mũmenye atĩ ndikwaragia ũhoro wa mĩgate? No mwĩhũgagei ndawa ĩyo ya kũimbia mĩgate ya Afarisai na Asadukai.” <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 4:1">Atũm 4:1</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo makĩmenya atĩ ndaameeraga mehũũge nĩ ũndũ wa ndawa ya kũimbia mĩgate, no nĩ memenyagĩrĩre ũrutani wa Afarisai na Asadukai.</para>
  <para style="s1">Petero Kuumbũra Kristũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ aakinyire rũgongo rwa Kaisarea-Filipi, nĩoririe arutwo ake atĩrĩ, “Andũ moigaga Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:1">Math 3:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Amwe moigaga atĩ nĩwe Johana Mũbatithania; angĩ makoiga nĩwe Elija, o na angĩ makoiga nĩwe Jeremia, kana ũmwe wa anabii.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nake akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ na inyuĩ muugaga atĩa? Muugaga niĩ nĩ niĩ ũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 4:3">Math 4:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Simoni Petero akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Wee nĩwe Kristũ, Mũrũ wa Ngai ũrĩa wĩ muoyo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 15:50">1Akor 15:50</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩwe Simoni mũrũ wa Jona, nĩgũkorwo ndũguũrĩirio ũndũ ũyũ nĩ mũndũ, no nĩ Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:42">Joh 1:42</ref></char></note>Na niĩ ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ, wee nĩwe Petero, na igũrũ rĩa ihiga rĩrĩ nĩngaka kanitha wakwa, nacio ihingo cia kwa ngoma itikaũtooria. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 18:18">Math 18:18</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 20:23">Joh 20:23</ref></char></note>Nĩngakũnengera cabi cia ũthamaki wa igũrũ; na kĩrĩa gĩothe ũkooha gũkũ thĩ nĩgĩkoohwo igũrũ, na kĩrĩa gĩothe ũkoohora gũkũ thĩ, nĩgĩkoohorwo igũrũ.” <verse number="20" style="v"/>Agĩcooka agĩkaania arutwo ake matikeere mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ atĩ we nĩwe Kristũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kuumbũra Ũhoro wa Gĩkuũ Gĩake</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 17:25">Luk 17:25</ref>; <ref loc="HOS 6:2">Hos 6:2</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 9:31">Mar 9:31</ref></char>
    </note>Kuuma hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akĩambĩrĩria gũtaarĩria arutwo ake atĩ no nginya athiĩ Jerusalemu, na athĩĩnio mũno nĩ athuuri, na athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene, na arutani a watho, na atĩ no nginya ooragwo, na thuutha wa mĩthenya ĩtatũ ariũke.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nake Petero akĩmũtwara keheri-inĩ, akĩmũkaania, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, kũroaga gũtuĩka ũguo! Ũndũ ũcio ndũkanagũkore!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩĩhũgũrĩra Petero, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Cooka thuutha wakwa, Shaitani! Wee wĩ mũhĩnga harĩ niĩ; wee ndwĩciiragia maũndũ moimĩte kũrĩ Ngai, tiga maũndũ moimĩte kũrĩ andũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:38">Math 10:38</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 14:27">Luk 14:27</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akĩĩra arutwo ake atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ o wothe ũngĩenda kũnũmĩrĩra, no nginya eerege we mwene, oe mũtharaba wake aanũmĩrĩre. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:25">Joh 12:25</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ ũrĩa wothe wendaga kũhonokia muoyo wake nĩakoorwo nĩguo; no ũrĩa wothe ũkoorwo nĩ muoyo wake nĩ ũndũ wakwa nĩakaũhonokia. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, mũndũ angĩĩguna nakĩ o na angĩĩgwatĩra thĩ yothe, na orwo nĩ muoyo wake? Kana nĩ kĩĩ mũndũ angĩkũũrania muoyo wake nakĩo? <verse number="27" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩagooka na riiri wa Ithe hamwe na araika ake, na hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩakahe o mũndũ kĩheo gĩake kũringana na ciĩko ciake. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, amwe marũngiĩ haha matigacama gĩkuũ matonete Mũrũ wa Mũndũ agĩũka na ũthamaki wake.”</para>
  <chapter number="17" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũgarũrũka ũrĩa Aatariĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Thuutha wa mĩthenya ĩtandatũ, Jesũ nĩathiire na Petero, na Jakubu, na mũrũ wa nyina Johana, akĩmatwara kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩraaya handũ hataarĩ na andũ. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Arĩ hau mbere yao akĩgarũrũka ũrĩa aahaanaga. Ũthiũ wake ũkĩara ta riũa, na nguo ciake ikĩerũha cua, ta ũtheri. <verse number="3" style="v"/>O hĩndĩ ĩyo hau mbere yao makiumĩrĩrwo nĩ Musa na Elija makĩaranĩria na Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nake Petero akĩĩra Jesũ atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, nĩ wega tũikare gũkũ; ũngĩenda-rĩ, no njake ithũnũ ithatũ, kĩmwe gĩaku, na kĩmwe kĩa Musa, na kĩrĩa kĩngĩ kĩa Elija.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:17">Math 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 3:22">Atũm 3:22</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 3:23">23</ref></char>
    </note>O akĩaragia-rĩ, itu ikengu rĩgĩũka rĩkĩmahumbĩra, na mũgambo ũkiuma itu-inĩ rĩu ũkiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa ũrĩa nyendete; na nĩngenagio mũno nĩwe. Mũiguagei!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa arutwo maiguire ũguo-rĩ, makĩinamĩrĩra, magĩturumithia mothiũ mao thĩ mamakĩte mũno. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 14:27">Math 14:27</ref></char></note>No Jesũ agĩũka, akĩmahutia na akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Arahũkai, tigai gwĩtigĩra.” <verse number="8" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa maatiirire maitho-rĩ, mationire mũndũ ũngĩ tiga o Jesũ wiki.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 8:30">Mar 8:30</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 16:21">Math 16:21</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa maikũrũkaga kuuma kĩrĩma-inĩ, Jesũ akĩmaatha akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mũtikae kwĩra mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ũrĩa muona, nginya rĩrĩa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ akaariũkio oime kũrĩ arĩa akuũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nao arutwo makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩkĩ gĩtũmaga arutani a watho moige atĩ Elija no nginya aambe ooke?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAL 4:6">Mal 4:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ti-itherũ, Elija no nginya aambe ooke, ahaarĩrie maũndũ mothe. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 14:3">Math 14:3</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 14:10">10</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 16:21">Math 16:21</ref></char></note>No ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, Elija nĩarĩkĩtie gũũka, no andũ makĩaga kũmũmenya, no nĩmamwĩkire ũrĩa wothe meendaga kũmwĩka. O ũguo noguo nake Mũrũ wa Mũndũ akaanyariirwo nĩo.” <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:1">Math 3:1</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo arutwo makĩmenya atĩ aamaheaga ũhoro wa Johana Mũbatithania.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũhonia Kamwana kaarĩ na Ndaimono</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa maakinyire harĩa kĩrĩndĩ kĩarĩ, mũndũ ũmwe agĩthiĩ harĩ Jesũ, akĩmũturĩria ndu, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:24">Math 4:24</ref></char></note>akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani iguĩra mũrũ wakwa tha, arĩ na mũrimũ wa kĩbaba na nĩũmũthĩĩnagia mũno. Kaingĩ nĩagũũaga mwaki-inĩ kana akagũa maaĩ-inĩ. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nĩndĩramũreheire arutwo aku, no matinahota kũmũhonia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Rũciaro rũrũ rũtetĩkĩtie na rũremi, nĩ nginya rĩ ngũikara na inyuĩ? Ngũmũkirĩrĩria nginya rĩ? Ndeherai kamwana kau.” <verse number="18" style="v"/>Jesũ agĩkũũma ndaimono ĩyo, nayo ĩkiuma kamwana kau, na gakĩhonio o hĩndĩ ĩyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nao arutwo magĩthiĩ kũrĩ Jesũ keheri-inĩ, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Tũremirwo nĩkũingata ndaimono ĩyo nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 21:21">Math 21:21</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 13:2">1Akor 13:2</ref></char>
    </note>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ tondũ wĩtĩkio wanyu nĩ mũnini. Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, mũngĩkorwo na wĩtĩkio mũnini ta mbeũ ya karatarĩ, no mũhote kwĩra kĩrĩma gĩkĩ atĩrĩ, ‘Ehera haha, ũthiĩ haarĩa’ na gĩthiĩ. Gũtirĩ ũndũ ũkaamũrema.” (<verse number="21" style="v"/>No ndaimono mũthemba ũcio ndĩngĩingatĩka na kĩndũ kĩngĩ, tiga mahooya na kwĩhinga kũrĩa irio.”)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 8:20">Math 8:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa macookanĩrĩire kũu Galili, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩegũkunyanĩrwo aneanwo moko-inĩ ma andũ. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:23">Atũm 2:23</ref></char></note>Nĩmakamũũraga, na mũthenya wa ĩtatũ nĩakariũkio.” Nao arutwo makĩiyũrwo nĩ kĩeha.</para>
  <para style="s1">Igooti rĩa Hekarũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 30:13">Thaam 30:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, Jesũ na arutwo ake maarĩkia gũkinya Kaperinaumu, arĩa meetagia andũ daraki igĩrĩ cia igooti rĩa hekarũ magĩthiĩ kũrĩ Petero, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ mũrutani wanyu atarutaga igooti rĩa hekarũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 22:17-21">Math 22:17-21</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 13:7">Arom 13:7</ref></char>
    </note>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ, nĩarutaga.”</para>
  <para style="p">Rĩrĩa Petero aatoonyire nyũmba, Jesũ akĩmũhĩta kwaria akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũgwĩciiria atĩa, wee Simoni? Athamaki a thĩ-rĩ, metagia igooti kuuma kũrĩ a? Metagia ariũ ao, kana metagia andũ arĩa angĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Nake Petero akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kuuma kũrĩ andũ arĩa angĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ariũ ao matirĩhaga. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:61">Joh 6:61</ref></char></note>No nĩguo tũtikamarakarie-rĩ, thiĩ iria-inĩ ũikie ndwano kuo, na thamaki ĩrĩa ũkũnyiita mbere, ũmĩtumũre kanua kayo, na nĩũkuona mbeeca, daraki inya; cioe ũthiĩ ũrĩhe igooti rĩakwa na rĩaku.”</para>
  <chapter number="18" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũndũ ũrĩa Mũnene mũno Ũthamaki-inĩ wa Igũrũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ihinda o rĩu arutwo magĩũka kũrĩ Jesũ, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nũũ mũnene gũkĩra arĩa angĩ ũthamaki-inĩ wa igũrũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Nake agĩĩta kaana, agĩkarũgamia gatagatĩ kao. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 2:2">1Pet 2:2</ref></char></note>Agĩcooka akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, tiga mũgarũrũkire mũtuĩke o ta twana, mũtigatoonya ũthamaki wa igũrũ. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 9:35">Mar 9:35</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 3:2">Math 3:2</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ũrĩa wothe wĩnyiihagia ta kaana gaka nĩwe mũnene gũkĩra arĩa angĩ ũthamaki-inĩ wa igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:10">Math 10:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nake ũrĩa wothe wamũkagĩra kaana ta gaka thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, nĩ niĩ aamũkagĩra. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 17:2">Luk 17:2</ref></char></note>No ũrĩa wothe ũngĩhĩtithia kamwe ga twana tũtũ tũnjĩtĩkĩtie keehie, nĩ kaba mũndũ ũcio aharũkio ihiga rĩa gĩthĩi ngingo aikio iria-inĩ kũrĩa kũriku.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 17:1">Luk 17:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Kaĩ gũkũ thĩ kũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ marĩa matũmaga andũ mehie! Maũndũ ta macio no nginya moke, no mũndũ ũrĩa ũtũmaga moke kaĩ arĩ na haaro-ĩ! <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:29">Math 5:29</ref></char></note>Guoko gwaku kana kũgũrũ gwaku kũngĩtũma wĩhie-rĩ, gũtinie ũgũte. Nĩ kaba ũtoonye muoyo-inĩ wĩ gĩthua kana wĩ kĩonje, gũkĩra ũkorwo na moko meerĩ kana magũrũ meerĩ na ũikio mwaki-inĩ wa tene na tene. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:29">Math 5:29</ref></char></note>Narĩo riitho rĩaku rĩngĩtũma wĩhie-rĩ, rĩkũũre, ũrĩte. Nĩ kaba ũtoonye muoyo-inĩ na riitho rĩmwe, gũkĩra ũkorwo na maitho meerĩ na ũikio mwaki-inĩ wa kwa ngoma.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Ngʼondu ĩrĩa Yorĩte</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 34:7">Thab 34:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Menyererai mũtikae kũnyarara o na kamwe ga twana tũtũ tũnini. Nĩgũkorwo ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, araika a tuo nĩmonaga ũthiũ wa Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ, hĩndĩ ciothe.” (<verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo Mũrũ wa Mũndũ ookire kũhonokia kĩrĩa kĩorĩte.)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>“Rĩu-rĩ, mũgwĩciiria atĩa? Mũndũ angĩkorwo arĩ na ngʼondu igana rĩmwe, na ĩmwe yacio yũre-rĩ, githĩ ndangĩtiga icio mĩrongo kenda na kenda kũu irĩma-inĩ, athiĩ agacarie ĩyo yũrĩte? <verse number="13" style="v"/>Na angĩmĩona-rĩ, ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, akenagĩra ngʼondu ĩyo ĩmwe ĩrorĩte kũrĩ ũrĩa akenagĩra icio mĩrongo kenda na kenda itaroorĩte. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Ũguo noguo Ithe wanyu ũrĩa ũrĩ Igũrũ atangĩenda o na kamwe ga twana tũtũ tũnini koore.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũndũ Wanyu Akũhĩtĩirie</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 19:17">Alaw 19:17</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 5:19-20">Jak 5:19-20</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa thoguo angĩkũhĩtĩria-rĩ, thiĩ ũmuonie ihĩtia rĩake mũrĩ o inyuĩ eerĩ. Angĩgũthikĩrĩria-rĩ, nĩmwacookanwo nake. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 19:15">Gũcook 19:15</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 8:17">Joh 8:17</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 10:28">Ahib 10:28</ref></char></note>No angĩrega gũgũthikĩrĩria, oya mũndũ ũngĩ ũmwe kana eerĩ mũthiĩ nao, nĩguo ũndũ o wothe ũrũgamagĩrĩrwo nĩ ũira wa andũ eerĩ kana atatũ. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:17">Arom 16:17</ref></char></note>Angĩrega kũmathikĩrĩria-rĩ, ĩra kanitha ũndũ ũcio; na angĩkĩrega gũthikĩrĩria o na kanitha-rĩ, mũtue o ta mũndũ ũtetĩkĩtie kana ta mwĩtia wa mbeeca cia igooti.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:19">Math 16:19</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 20:23">Joh 20:23</ref></char>
    </note>“Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ũndũ o wothe mũkooha gũkũ thĩ, o na igũrũ nĩũkoohwo, na ũrĩa wothe mũkoohora gũkũ thĩ, o na igũrũ nĩũkohorwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>“O rĩngĩ ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, andũ eerĩ anyu mangĩiguanĩra gũkũ thĩ ũndũ o wothe ũrĩa marahooya, nĩmakahingĩrio nĩ Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo harĩa andũ eerĩ kana atatũ monganĩte thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa-rĩ, ngoragwo ndĩ ho gatagatĩ kao.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Ndungata ĩtarĩ Tha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 6:14">Math 6:14</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 17:4">Luk 17:4</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Petero agĩũka harĩ Jesũ, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa baba angĩhĩtĩria maita maigana ngĩmũrekagĩra? Hihi nĩ maita mũgwanja?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 4:24">Kĩam 4:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ, ti maita mũgwanja, no nĩ mĩrongo mũgwanja, maita mũgwanja.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 25:19">Math 25:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũhaananĩtio na mũthamaki ũrĩa wendaga kuonio mathabu ma mbeeca ciake nĩ ndungata ciake. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Aambĩrĩria kũrora mathabu-rĩ, mũndũ warĩ na thiirĩ wake wa taranda ngiri ikũmi<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">18:24 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Taranda nĩ mbeeca yarĩ makĩria ma mũcaara wa mĩaka ikũmi na ĩtano wa mũruti wĩra, kana mina mĩrongo ĩtandatũ. Ũmũthĩ nĩ ciringi milioni nyingĩ.</char></note> akĩrehwo kũrĩ we. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 7:42">Luk 7:42</ref>; <ref loc="2KI 4:1">2Ath 4:1</ref></char></note>Na tondũ nĩaremetwo nĩ kũrĩha-rĩ, mwathi wake agĩathana atĩ mũndũ ũcio, endio hamwe na mũtumia wake, na ciana ciake, na kĩrĩa gĩothe aarĩ nakĩo nĩguo thiirĩ ũrĩhĩke.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>“Ndungata ĩyo ĩkĩĩgũithia mbere yake, ĩkĩmũthaitha, ĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Ngirĩrĩria, na nĩndĩĩkũrĩha thiirĩ wothe.’ <verse number="27" style="v"/>Nake mwathi ũcio wa ndungata ĩyo akĩmĩiguĩra tha, akĩmĩrekera thiirĩ ũcio akĩreka ĩthiĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>“No ndungata ĩyo yoima nja, ĩgĩcemania na ndungata ĩngĩ yarutaga wĩra nayo yarĩ na thiirĩ wayo wa dinari igana rĩmwe.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">18:28 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Dinari yarĩ mũcaara wa mũthenya ũmwe.</char></note> Ĩkĩmĩnyiita mũmero ĩmĩite, ĩkĩmĩĩra na hinya atĩrĩ, ‘Ndĩha thiirĩ wakwa ũrĩa ũrĩ naguo!’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>“Ndungata ĩyo ĩkĩĩgũithia thĩ, ĩkĩmĩthaitha, ĩkĩmĩĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Ngirĩrĩria, na nĩndĩĩkũrĩha.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>“Nowe akĩrega. Handũ ha ũguo, agĩthiĩ ĩkĩmĩikithia njeera nginya rĩrĩa ĩkaarĩha thiirĩ ũcio. <verse number="31" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa ndungata iria ingĩ cioonire ũrĩa gwekĩka-rĩ, ikĩigua ũũru mũno, igĩthiĩ ikĩĩra mwathi wacio ũrĩa wothe gwekĩkĩte.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>“Nake mwathi wao agĩĩta ndungata ĩyo, akĩmĩĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Wee ndungata ĩno njaganu, ngũrekeire thiirĩ waku wothe tondũ nĩũũthaithire. <verse number="33" style="v"/>Githĩ nawe ndũkwagĩrĩirwo ũiguĩre ndungata ĩrĩa ĩngĩ tha o ta ũrĩa niĩ ngũiguĩrĩire tha?’ <verse number="34" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa kũrakara, mwathi wayo akĩmĩneana kũrĩ anene a njeera nĩguo ĩkaherithio o nginya rĩrĩa ĩkaarĩha thiirĩ wothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 6:14">Math 6:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ũguo nĩguo Baba ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ ageeka o ũmwe wanyu, mũngĩaga kũrekera mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa ithe wanyu na ma kuuma ngoro-inĩ cianyu.”</para>
  <chapter number="19" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gũtigana kwa Mũthuuri na Mũtumia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, Jesũ aarĩkia kũmeera maũndũ macio-rĩ, akiuma Galili, agĩthiĩ rũgongo rwa Judea mũrĩmo ũũrĩa ũngĩ wa Rũũĩ rwa Jorodani. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:23">Math 4:23</ref></char></note>Nao andũ aingĩ makĩmũrũmĩrĩra, nake akĩmahoneria kuo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:31">Math 5:31</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na Afarisai amwe magĩthiĩ kũrĩ we nĩguo mamũgerie. Makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Watho nĩwĩtĩkĩrĩtie mũndũ atigane na mũtumia wake nĩ ũndũ wa gĩtũmi o na kĩrĩkũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 1:27">Kĩam 1:27</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 5:2">5:2</ref></char>
    </note>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ mũtathomete, atĩ o kĩambĩrĩria Mũũmbi ‘ombire mũndũ-mũrũme na mũndũ-wa-nja’, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 2:24">Kĩam 2:24</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 6:16">1Akor 6:16</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 5:31">Aef 5:31</ref></char></note>na akiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩ ũndũ wa gĩtũmi kĩu mũndũ mũrũme nĩagatigana na ithe na nyina, na anyiitane na mũtumia wake, nao eerĩ matuĩke mwĩrĩ ũmwe’? <verse number="6" style="v"/>Na nĩ ũndũ ũcio, acio ti andũ eerĩ rĩngĩ, no nĩ mũndũ ũmwe. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, arĩa Ngai anyiitithanĩtie, mũndũ ndakanamatigithanie.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 24:1-4">Gũcook 24:1-4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩĩ gĩatũmire Musa aathane atĩ mũndũ no ahe mũtumia wake marũa ma gũtigana nake, amũte?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Musa aamwĩtĩkĩririe mũtiganage na atumia anyu tondũ wa ũmũ wa ngoro cianyu. No gũtiarĩ ũguo kuuma kĩambĩrĩria. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 16:18">Luk 16:18</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, mũndũ o wothe angĩtigana na mũtumia wake, tiga amũteire nĩ ũndũ wa ũtharia, nake ahikie mũtumia ũngĩ-rĩ, mũndũ ũcio nĩatharĩtie.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nao arutwo makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Angĩkorwo ũguo nĩguo kũrĩ gatagatĩ ka mũthuuri na mũtumia-rĩ, nĩ kaba kwaga kũhikania.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:11">Math 13:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ti mũndũ o wothe ũngĩhota gwĩtĩkĩra ũhoro ũyũ, tiga no arĩa maheetwo ũhoti ũcio. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo andũ amwe maaciarirwo mahaana ta marĩ ahakũre; angĩ maahakũrirwo nĩ andũ; na angĩ makarega kũhikania nĩ ũndũ wa ũthamaki wa igũrũ. Mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩhota gwĩtĩkĩra ũndũ ũyũ, nĩawĩtĩkĩre.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhoera Twana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akĩreherwo twana nĩguo atũigĩrĩre moko na atũhooere. No arutwo magĩkũũma arĩa maatũrehete.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 18:3">Math 18:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nowe Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Rekei twana tũũke kũrĩ niĩ, tigai gũtũgiria, nĩgũkorwo ũthamaki wa Igũrũ nĩ wa arĩa mahaana ta tuo.” <verse number="15" style="v"/>Aarĩkia gũtũigĩrĩra moko, akiuma kũu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mwanake warĩ Gĩtonga</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 25:46">Math 25:46</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 10:25">Luk 10:25</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, mũndũ ũmwe nĩokire kũrĩ Jesũ, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mũrutani, nĩ ũndũ ũrĩkũ mwega ingĩĩka nĩgeetha ngĩe na muoyo wa tene na tene?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 18:5">Alaw 18:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũkũnjũũria ũhoro wa ũndũ ũrĩa mwega nĩkĩ? Kũrĩ o Ũmwe mwega. Ũngĩenda gũtoonya muoyo-inĩ-rĩ, athĩkagĩra maathani.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 2:11">Jak 2:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũndũ ũcio akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ maathani marĩkũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “ ‘Ndũkanoragane, na ndũkanatharanie, na ndũkanaiye, na ndũkanaigĩrĩre mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ kĩgeenyo, <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 19:18">Alaw 19:18</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:43">Math 5:43</ref></char></note>na tĩĩa thoguo na nyũkwa,’ o na ‘endaga mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa wĩyendete wee mwene.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Mwanake ũcio akiuga atĩrĩ, “Maũndũ macio mothe ndũire ndĩmarũmĩtie, nĩ kĩĩ kĩngĩ ndigairie?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 2:45">Atũm 2:45</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 6:20">Math 6:20</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũngĩenda kwagĩrĩra kũna, thiĩ wendie indo ciaku ũhe athĩĩni mbeeca icio, na nĩũkagĩa na mũthiithũ igũrũ. Ũcooke ũũke ũnũmĩrĩre.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa mwanake ũcio aiguire ũguo-rĩ, agĩthiĩ arĩ na kĩeha, tondũ aarĩ na ũtonga mũingĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:22">Math 13:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩĩra arutwo ake atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, nĩ ũndũ ũrĩ hinya gĩtonga gũtoonya ũthamaki-inĩ wa igũrũ. <verse number="24" style="v"/>O rĩngĩ ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, nĩ ũhũthũ ngamĩĩra ĩhungurĩre irima rĩa cindano, gũkĩra gĩtonga gũtoonya ũthamaki wa Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa arutwo maiguire ũguo-rĩ, makĩmaka mũno, makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Rĩu-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩkĩhonoka?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 18:14">Kĩam 18:14</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 42:2">Ayub 42:2</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmarora akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ũndũ ũcio ndũngĩhoteka nĩ andũ, no maũndũ mothe nĩmahotekaga nĩ Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Petero akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ nĩtũtigĩte maũndũ mothe, tũgakũrũmĩrĩra! Ithuĩ-rĩ, nĩ kĩĩ tũkaaheo?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 22:28-30">Luk 22:28-30</ref>; <ref loc="REV 3:21">Kũg 3:21</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ agaikarĩra gĩtĩ gĩake kĩa ũnene kĩrĩ riiri, thĩinĩ wa thĩ njerũ, inyuĩ arĩa mũnũmagĩrĩra nĩ inyuĩ mũgaikarĩra itĩ ikũmi na igĩrĩ cia ũnene, na nĩmũgatuĩra mĩhĩrĩga ĩrĩa ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ ya Isiraeli ciira. <verse number="29" style="v"/>Na ũrĩa wothe ũtigĩte nyũmba, kana ariũ a nyina, kana aarĩ a nyina, kana ithe, kana nyina, kana ciana, kana mĩgũnda nĩ ũndũ wakwa nĩakamũkĩra maita igana ma iria atigĩte, na agae muoyo wa tene na tene. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 20:16">Math 20:16</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 13:30">Luk 13:30</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, andũ aingĩ arĩa marĩ mbere nĩo makaarigia thuutha, na aingĩ arĩa marĩ thuutha nĩo magaatongoria.</para>
  <chapter number="20" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Aruti Wĩra a Mũgũnda wa Mĩthabibũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:24">Math 13:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩgũkorwo ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũhaana ta mũndũ warĩ na gĩthaka, ũrĩa woimagarire rũciinĩ tene akaandĩke andũ a kũruta wĩra mũgũnda wake wa mĩthabibũ. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Na aarĩkanĩra nao atĩ nĩekũmarĩha dinari mũthenya ũcio, akĩmatũma makarute wĩra mũgũnda-inĩ wake wa mĩthabibũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>“Ta thaa ithatũ nĩoimagarire na akĩona andũ angĩ marũngiĩ thoko-inĩ matarĩ ũndũ meekaga. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Akĩmeera atĩrĩ, ‘O na inyuĩ-rĩ, thiĩi mũkarute wĩra mũgũnda-inĩ wakwa wa mĩthabibũ, na nĩngũmũrĩha o kĩrĩa kĩagĩrĩire.’ <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio magĩthiĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">“Ningĩ akiumagara rĩngĩ ta thaa thita, na thaa kenda agĩĩka o ũguo. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Na ta thaa ikũmi na ĩmwe, akiumagara na akĩona andũ angĩ marũngiĩ o hau. Akĩmooria atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmĩte mũtinde mũrũngiĩ haha mũthenya mũgima mũtarĩ ũndũ mũreka?’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>“Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, ‘Tondũ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũtwandĩkire.’</para>
  <para style="p">“Akĩmeera atĩrĩ, ‘O na inyuĩ thiĩi mũkarute wĩra mũgũnda-inĩ wakwa wa mĩthabibũ.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 24:15">Gũcook 24:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Gwatuka-rĩ, mwene mũgũnda ũcio wa mĩthabibũ akĩĩra mũrũgamĩrĩri wa wĩra wake atĩrĩ, ‘Ĩta aruti a wĩra ũmarĩhe mũcaara, wambĩrĩirie na arĩa maandĩkirwo thuutha, ũrĩkie na arĩa maandĩkirwo mbere.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>“Aruti a wĩra arĩa maandĩkĩtwo thaa ikũmi na ĩmwe moka, makĩrĩhwo dinari ĩmwe o mũndũ. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, rĩrĩa arĩa maandĩkĩtwo mbere mookire-rĩ, meeciirĩtie mekũrĩhwo makĩria. No rĩrĩ, o nao maarĩhirwo dinari ĩmwe o mũndũ. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Maarĩkia kũrĩhwo, makĩambĩrĩria kũnugunĩkĩra mwene mũgũnda. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 1:11">Jak 1:11</ref></char></note>Makiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Andũ arĩa marigirie kwandĩkwo-rĩ, marutire wĩra o ithaa rĩmwe, na wamaiganania na ithuĩ arĩa twatinda wĩra na mĩnoga na kũhĩa nĩ riũa.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>“Nake agĩcookeria ũmwe wao atĩrĩ, ‘Mũrata wakwa, ndinagwĩka ũũru. Githĩ tũtirĩkanĩire atĩ ngũrĩhe dinari ĩmwe? <verse number="14" style="v"/>Kĩoe mũcaara waku ũthiĩ. Nĩ niĩ ndenda kũrĩha mũndũ ũcio wandĩkirwo thuutha o ta ũguo ndakũrĩha. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 15:9">Gũcook 15:9</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 7:22">Mar 7:22</ref></char></note>Githĩ ndirĩ na kĩhooto gĩa gwĩka ũrĩa ngwenda na mbeeca ciakwa? Kana ũraigua ũiru tondũ ndĩ mũtaana?’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 19:30">Math 19:30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio arĩa marĩ thuutha, magaatuĩka a mbere, na arĩa marĩ mbere magaatuĩka a thuutha.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kuumbũra Ũhoro wa Gĩkuũ Gĩake rĩngĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ aambataga Jerusalemu-rĩ, nĩetire arutwo ake arĩa ikũmi na eerĩ keheri-inĩ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 9:51">Luk 9:51</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:1">Math 27:1</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 27:2">2</ref></char></note>“Twerekeire kwambata Jerusalemu, na kũu Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩagakunyanĩrwo aneanwo kũrĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na arutani a watho. Nao nĩmakamũtuĩra kũũragwo <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:21">Math 16:21</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 2:23">Atũm 2:23</ref></char></note>na nĩmakamũneana kũrĩ andũ-a-Ndũrĩrĩ anyũrũrio na ahũũrwo na kĩboko na mamwambe mũtĩ igũrũ. Na mũthenya wa gatatũ nĩakariũkio!”</para>
  <para style="s1">Ihooya rĩa Nyina wa Ciana cia Zebedi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 4:21">Math 4:21</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 8:12">8:12</ref></char>
    </note>Thuutha ũcio, nyina wa ciana cia Zebedi nĩokire kũrĩ Jesũ arĩ na ariũ ake, agĩturia ndu, akĩmũthaitha amũhingĩrie ũndũ mũna.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 19:28">Math 19:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ ũndũ ũrĩkũ ũkwenda?”</para>
  <para style="p">Akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ĩtĩkĩra atĩ ũmwe wa aanake aya akwa eerĩ magaikara ũmwe mwena waku wa ũrĩo, na ũcio ũngĩ mwena waku wa ũmotho ũthamaki-inĩ waku.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:39">Math 26:39</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 26:42">42</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 22:42">Luk 22:42</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũtiũĩ ũrĩa mũrahooya. No mũhote kũnyuĩra gĩkombe kĩrĩa ngũnyuĩra?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ, no tũhote.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 12:2">Atũm 12:2</ref>; <ref loc="REV 1:9">Kũg 1:9</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ti-itherũ nĩ mũkaanyuĩra gĩkombe gĩakwa, no gũikara mwena wakwa wa ũrĩo kana wa ũmotho ti niĩ heanaga. Itĩ icio ikaaheo arĩa mathondekeirwo cio nĩ Baba.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 22:24">Luk 22:24</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 22:25">25</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa arutwo acio angĩ ikũmi maiguire ũhoro ũcio, makĩrakarĩra arutwo acio eerĩ a nyina ũmwe. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeeta hamwe, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩmũũĩ atĩ aathani a Ndũrĩrĩ nĩ metũũgagĩria igũrũ rĩa andũ ao, na anene ao nĩmamaathaga na hinya. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 9:35">Mar 9:35</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, gũtikanahaane ũguo gatagatĩ kanyu. Handũ ha ũguo, ũrĩa ũngĩenda gũtuĩka mũnene thĩinĩ wanyu-rĩ, nĩ atuĩke ndungata yanyu, <verse number="27" style="v"/>na ũrĩa ũngĩenda gũtuĩka wa mbere thĩinĩ wanyu nĩatuĩke ngombo yanyu, <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:28">Math 26:28</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 30:12">Thaam 30:12</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:13-16">Joh 13:13-16</ref></char></note>o ta ũrĩa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ atookire gũtungatĩrwo, no ookire gũtungata, na arute muoyo wake ũtuĩke thogora wa gũkũũra andũ aingĩ.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Atumumu Eerĩ Kũhonio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ na arutwo ake moimaga Jeriko-rĩ, andũ aingĩ makĩmũrũmĩrĩra. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:27">Math 9:27</ref></char></note>Nao andũ eerĩ atumumu maikarĩte mũkĩra-inĩ wa njĩra, na rĩrĩa maiguire atĩ nĩ Jesũ wahĩtũkaga-rĩ, makĩanĩrĩra, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, Mũrũ wa Daudi, tũiguĩre tha!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>Gĩkundi kĩu kĩa andũ gĩkĩmakaania, gĩkĩmeera makire, no-o magĩkĩrĩrĩria kwanĩrĩra, makiugaga atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, Mũrũ wa Daudi, tũiguĩre tha!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩrũgama, akĩmeeta. Akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Mũrenda ndĩmwĩkĩre atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>Makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, tũrakũhooya o tũcooke kuona.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmaiguĩra tha, akĩmahutia maitho. Na kahinda o kau makĩambĩrĩria kuona, makĩmũrũmĩrĩra.</para>
  <chapter number="21" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũtoonya Jerusalemu na Ũhootani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa maakuhĩrĩirie Jerusalemu, maakinya itũũra rĩa Bethifage kũu Kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Mĩtamaiyũ-rĩ, Jesũ agĩtũma arutwo ake eerĩ, <verse number="2" style="v"/>akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Thiĩi itũũra rĩrĩa rĩrĩ mbere yanyu, na mwaingĩra o ũguo nĩmũgũkora ndigiri yohetwo, ĩrĩ na njaũ yayo. Ciohorei mũndehere. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Na mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ angĩmũũria ũndũ-rĩ, mwĩrei atĩ Mwathani nĩabatarĩtio nĩcio, na nĩegũcicookia o narua.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ũndũ ũyũ wekĩkire nĩgeetha ũrathi ũrĩa waarĩtio na kanua ka mũnabii ũhinge, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 9:9">Zek 9:9</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 62:11">Isa 62:11</ref></char>
    </note>“Ĩrai Mwarĩ wa Zayuni atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Mũthamaki waku nĩarooka kũrĩwe,</para>
  <para style="q1">nĩ mũhooreri na akuuĩtwo nĩ ndigiri,</para>
  <para style="q2">o njaũ ya ndigiri.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nao arutwo magĩthiĩ magĩĩka o ũrĩa Jesũ aamerĩte. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Makĩrehe ndigiri na njaũ yayo, na makĩara nguo ciao igũrũ rĩayo, nake Jesũ agĩkuuo nĩyo. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 9:13">2Ath 9:13</ref></char></note>Na andũ gĩkundi kĩnene mũno makĩara nguo ciao njĩra-inĩ, nao arĩa angĩ magĩtua mathĩgĩ ma mĩtĩ makĩmaara njĩra-inĩ. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 118:26">Thab 118:26</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 2:14">Luk 2:14</ref></char></note>Nacio ikundi cia andũ arĩa maamũtongoretie na arĩa maamũrũmĩrĩire maanagĩrĩra makoiga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Hosana, Mũrũ wa Daudi!”</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">“Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũgũũka na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani!”</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">“Hosana igũrũ, o igũrũ mũno!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aatoonyire Jerusalemu, andũ a itũũra rĩu inene rĩothe makĩambũrũrũka, makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nake nũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 6:14">Joh 6:14</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:40">7:40</ref></char>
    </note>Nakĩo kĩrĩndĩ kĩu gĩgĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩwe Jesũ ũrĩa mũnabii wa kuuma Nazarethi itũũra rĩa Galili.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ arĩ thĩinĩ wa Hekarũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 30:13">Thaam 30:13</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 1:14">Alaw 1:14</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ agĩtoonya kũu hekarũ-inĩ akĩrutũrũra andũ othe arĩa maagũraga na meendagia indo kuo, akĩngʼaũrania metha cia arĩa maakũũranagia mbeeca, na akĩngʼaũrania itĩ cia arĩa meendagia ndutura. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 56:7">Isa 56:7</ref>; <ref loc="JER 7:11">Jer 7:11</ref></char></note>Akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ, ‘Nyũmba yakwa ĩgeetagwo nyũmba ya kũhooyagĩrwo,’ no inyuĩ mũmĩtuĩte ‘ngurunga ya atunyani.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 4:23">Math 4:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao atumumu na cionje magĩthiĩ kũrĩ we kũu hekarũ-inĩ, nake akĩmahonia. <verse number="15" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na arutani a watho moonire maũndũ ma magegania marĩa eekaga, na maigua ũrĩa ciana cianagĩrĩra kũu hekarũ-inĩ ikiugaga atĩrĩ, “Hosana Mũrũ wa Daudi,” makĩrakara.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 8:2">Thab 8:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩũraigua ũrĩa ciana ici iroiga?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ, nĩndĩraigua. Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtathomete ciugo iria ciugĩte atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘Kuuma tũnua-inĩ twa twana na twa ngenge</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩũtũmĩte hoime ũgooci’?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Agĩcooka akĩmatiga, akiuma itũũra rĩu inene, agĩthiĩ Bethania, akĩraara kuo.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũkũyũ Kũhooha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Na rũciinĩ tene, arĩ njĩra agĩcooka kũu itũũra inene, akĩigua arĩ mũhũũtu. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 34:4">Isa 34:4</ref></char></note>Nake akĩona mũkũyũ mũkĩra wa njĩra, agĩthiĩ harĩ guo, no ndaigana kuona kĩndũ thĩinĩ waguo tiga o mathangũ. Nake akĩwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ũroaga gũgaaciara maciaro rĩngĩ!” O hĩndĩ ĩyo mũtĩ ũcio ũkĩhoha.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa arutwo ake moonire ũguo makĩgega, makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ mũkũyũ ũyũ wahooha narua atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 17:20">Math 17:20</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 17:20">Luk 17:20</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:6">Jak 1:6</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, mũngĩkorwo na wĩtĩkio na mũtigathanganie-rĩ, to ũguo mũkũyũ ũyũ wĩkĩtwo mũngĩhota gwĩka, no rĩrĩ, o na no mũhote kwĩra kĩrĩma gĩkĩ atĩrĩ, ‘Ũrokũũrũka ũikio iria-inĩ,’ na gwĩkĩke ũguo. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 7:7">Math 7:7</ref></char></note>Maũndũ mothe marĩa mũrĩhooyaga mwĩtĩkĩtie nĩmũkaheo.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Kĩũria Gĩkoniĩ Ũhoti wa Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 4:7">Atũm 4:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ aatoonyire hekarũ-inĩ-rĩ, athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na athuuri a andũ makĩmũkora akĩrutana, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũreka maũndũ maya na ũhoti ũrĩkũ? Na nũũ ũkũheete ũhoti ũcio?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “O na niĩ nĩngũmũũria kĩũria. Mwanjookeria-rĩ, nĩngũmwĩra njĩkaga maũndũ maya na ũhoti ũrĩkũ. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Ũbatithio wa Johana-rĩ, woimĩte kũ? Woimĩte igũrũ-ĩ, kana woimĩte kũrĩ andũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Makĩaranĩria o ene ũhoro ũcio, makĩĩrana atĩrĩ, “Tũngiuga atĩ, ‘Woimĩte igũrũ’, egũtũũria atĩrĩ, ‘Mwakĩregire kũmwĩtĩkia nĩkĩ?’ <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 11:6">Math 11:6</ref></char></note>No tũngiuga atĩ, ‘Woimĩte kũrĩ andũ’, nĩtũgwĩtigĩra andũ, nĩgũkorwo othe nĩmeetĩkĩtie atĩ Johana aarĩ mũnabii.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio magĩcookeria Jesũ atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ tũtiũĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “O na niĩ ndikũmwĩra njĩkaga maũndũ maya na ũhoti ũrĩkũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Ariũ arĩa Eerĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 21:33">Math 21:33</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Na rĩrĩ, mũgwĩciiria atĩa? Nĩ kwarĩ na mũndũ warĩ na ariũ eerĩ. Agĩthiĩ harĩ ũrĩa wa mbere, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Mũriũ, thiĩ ũkarute wĩra ũmũthĩ mũgũnda-inĩ wa mĩthabibũ.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>“Nake agĩcookia, akiuga, ‘Ndigũthiĩ,’ no thuutha akĩĩricũkwo, agĩthiĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>“Ningĩ mũthuuri ũcio agĩthiĩ kũrĩ mũriũ ũcio ũngĩ akĩmwĩra o ũguo. Nake agĩcookia akiuga, ‘Ĩĩ baba, nĩngũthiĩ,’ no ndaathiire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 7:29">Luk 7:29</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 7:50">50</ref></char>
    </note>“Acio eerĩ-rĩ, nũũ wekire ũrĩa ithe eendaga?”</para>
  <para style="p">Magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Nĩ ũrĩa wa mbere.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, etia mbeeca cia igooti na maraya nĩmaratoonya ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai mbere yanyu. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:1-12">Math 3:1-12</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 3:12-13">Luk 3:12-13</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Johana ookire kũrĩ inyuĩ amwonie njĩra ya ũthingu, no mũtiamwĩtĩkirie, no etia mbeeca cia igooti na maraya nĩmamwĩtĩkirie. Na inyuĩ o na muona ũguo, mũtiigana kwĩrira mũmwĩtĩkie.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Akombori Mũgũnda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 80:8">Thab 80:8</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 5:1-7">Isa 5:1-7</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 25:14-15">Math 25:14-15</ref></char>
    </note>“Ta thikĩrĩriai ngerekano ĩngĩ: Mũndũ warĩ mwene mũgũnda nĩahaandire mũgũnda ũcio wake mĩthabibũ. Agĩaka rũgiri rũgĩthiũrũrũkĩria mũgũnda ũcio, akĩenja kĩhihĩro gĩa thabibũ o kũu thĩinĩ, na agĩaka nyũmba ndaaya na igũrũ ya arangĩri. Agĩcooka agĩkomborithia mũgũnda ũcio wa mĩthabibũ kũrĩ arĩmi na agĩthiĩ rũgendo. <verse number="34" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ya kũgetha yakuhĩrĩria-rĩ, agĩtũma ndungata ciake kũrĩ akombori acio nĩguo ikanengerwo maciaro make.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CH 24:21">2Maũ 24:21</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 23:34">Math 23:34</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 23:37">37</ref></char>
    </note>“Akombori acio makĩnyiita ndungata ciake; makĩhũũra ĩmwe, na makĩũraga ĩrĩa ĩngĩ, na ya gatatũ makĩmĩhũũra na mahiga nyuguto. <verse number="36" style="v"/>Agĩcooka akĩmatũmĩra ndungata ingĩ nyingĩ kũrĩ iria aatũmĩte mbere, nao akombori acio magĩciĩka o ro ũguo. <verse number="37" style="v"/>Mũthia-inĩ akĩmatũmĩra mũrũwe, akiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩmagatĩĩa mũrũ wakwa.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 1:2">Ahib 1:2</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 2:8">Thab 2:8</ref></char>
    </note>“No rĩrĩa akombori acio moonire mũriũ, makĩĩrana atĩrĩ, ‘Ũyũ nĩwe ũkaagaya mũgũnda ũyũ. Ũkai tũmũũrage, twĩyoere igai rĩake.’ <verse number="39" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makĩmũnyiita, makĩmũikia nja ya mũgũnda ũcio wa mĩthabibũ, na makĩmũũraga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, rĩrĩa mwene mũgũnda ũcio wa mĩthabibũ agooka-rĩ, ageeka akombori acio atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:41 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 8:11-12">Math 8:11-12</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 13:46">Atũm 13:46</ref></char>
    </note>Nao magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Nĩakaniina andũ acio aaganu, na acooke akomborithie andũ angĩ mũgũnda ũcio, arĩa marĩmũgayagĩra maciaro hĩndĩ ya magetha yakinya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:42 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 118:22">Thab 118:22</ref>, <ref loc="PSA 118:23">23</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 4:11">Atũm 4:11</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ mũtathomete thĩinĩ wa Maandĩko atĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘Ihiga rĩrĩa aaki maaregire</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩrĩo rĩtuĩkĩte ihiga inene rĩa koine;</para>
  <para style="q1">Mwathani nĩ we wĩkĩte ũndũ ũcio,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ wa magegania tũkĩwona’?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, ũthamaki wa Ngai nĩũkeeherio kũrĩ inyuĩ, ũheo andũ angĩ arĩa magaaciaraga maciaro maguo. <verse number="44" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũrĩa ũkaagwĩra ihiga rĩrĩ nĩagathuthĩka, no ũrĩa ũkaagwĩrwo nĩrĩo nĩrĩkamũthethera.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na Afarisai maaiguire ngerekano icio cia Jesũ, makĩmenya atĩ aaragia ũhoro wao. <verse number="46" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:46 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 21:11">Math 21:11</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 21:26">26</ref></char></note>Magĩcaria ũrĩa mangĩmũnyiita, no nĩmetigagĩra kĩrĩndĩ kĩu, tondũ andũ nĩmeetĩkĩtie atĩ aarĩ mũnabii.</para>
  <chapter number="22" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Iruga rĩa Ũhiki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmaarĩria rĩngĩ na ngerekano, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũhaanaine na mũthamaki warugire iruga nĩ ũndũ wa ũhiki wa mũriũ. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Agĩcooka agĩtũma ndungata ciake kũrĩ andũ arĩa meetĩtwo iruga-inĩ, ikameere moke, nao makĩrega gũũka.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>“Ningĩ agĩtũma ndungata ingĩ agĩciĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Ĩrai acio metĩtwo atĩ nĩndĩkĩtie kũhaarĩria iruga: Ndegwa ciakwa na ngʼombe iria noru nĩirĩkĩtie gũthĩnjwo na maũndũ mothe nĩmahaarĩrie. Ũkai iruga-inĩ rĩa ũhiki.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>“No andũ acio matiarũmbũirie ũhoro ũcio magĩĩthiĩra, ũmwe agĩthiĩ mũgũnda wake, na ũrĩa ũngĩ agĩthiĩ wonjoria-inĩ wake. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Acio angĩ magĩtharĩkĩra ndungata ciake, magĩcinyariira na magĩciũraga. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 19:27">Luk 19:27</ref></char></note>Mũthamaki ũcio nĩarakarire mũno, agĩtũma mbũtũ yake ĩkaniine oragani acio, na ĩgĩcina itũũra rĩao inene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>“Hĩndĩ ĩyo akĩĩra ndungata ciake atĩrĩ, ‘Iruga rĩa ũhiki nĩrĩhaarĩrie no rĩrĩ, arĩa ndĩretire-rĩ, matiraagĩrĩirwo nĩ gũũka. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Thiĩi magomano-inĩ ma njĩra mwĩre mũndũ o wothe mũkuona oke iruga-inĩ rĩa kĩhikanio.’ <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndungata icio ikiumagara, igĩthiĩ njĩra-inĩ, igĩcookanĩrĩria andũ othe arĩa ciahotire kuona, igĩĩta arĩa ega o na arĩa ooru, nayo nyũmba ya kĩhikanĩrio ĩkĩiyũra ageni.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>“No rĩrĩa mũthamaki aatoonyire nĩguo one ageni-rĩ, akĩona kuo mũndũ ũmwe ũtehumbĩte nguo cia ũhiki. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 13:47-48">Math 13:47-48</ref></char></note>Akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, ‘Mũrata wakwa, ũtoonyire atĩa gũkũ ũtarĩ na nguo cia kĩhikanio?’ Mũndũ ũcio agĩkira ki.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 8:12">Math 8:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Hĩndĩ ĩyo mũthamaki ũcio akĩĩra ndungata ciake atĩrĩ, ‘Muohei moko na magũrũ, mũmũikie nja kũu nduma-inĩ, kũu nĩkuo gũgaakorwo kĩrĩro na kũhagarania magego.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 17:14">Kũg 17:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩgũkorwo aingĩ nĩmetĩtwo, no arĩa athuure nĩ anini.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Kĩũria gĩkoniĩ Kũrĩha Igooti rĩa Kaisari</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Afarisai makiuma nja, magĩthugunda ũrĩa mangĩmũtega na ciugo ciake. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 3:6">Mar 3:6</ref></char></note>Magĩtũma arutwo ao hamwe na Aherodia kũrĩ we. Magĩthiĩ makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũrutani, nĩtũũĩ atĩ wee wĩ mũndũ wa ma, na ũrutanaga ũhoro wa Ngai na ma. Wee ndwĩtigagĩra andũ, tondũ ndũrũmbũyagia ũrĩa mahaana. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 17:25">Math 17:25</ref></char></note>Rĩu-rĩ, ta gĩtwĩre ũrĩa ũgwĩciiria. Nĩ kwagĩrĩire tũrutagĩre Kaisari igooti, kana aca?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>No Jesũ, nĩ ũndũ wa kũmenya meciiria mao mooru, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ hinga ici, mũrenda kũngeria nĩkĩ? <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nyoniai mbeeca ĩrĩa ĩhũthagĩrwo ya kũrĩha igooti.” Nao makĩmũtwarĩra dinari, <verse number="20" style="v"/>nake akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Mbica ĩno na rĩĩtwa rĩĩrĩ nĩ cia ũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 13:7">Arom 13:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ cia Kaisari.”</para>
  <para style="p">Agĩcooka akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Rutagĩrai Kaisari kĩrĩa kĩrĩ gĩake, na mũrutagĩre Ngai kĩrĩa kĩrĩ gĩake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 12:12">Mar 12:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa maiguire ũguo-rĩ, makĩgega. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio magĩtigana nake, magĩĩthiĩra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kĩũria gĩkoniĩ Kũriũka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 23:8">Atũm 23:8</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 15:12">1Akor 15:12</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya o ro ũcio Asadukai, arĩa moigaga atĩ gũtirĩ ũhoro wa kũriũka, magĩũka kũrĩ Jesũ makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 25:5">Gũcook 25:5</ref>, <ref loc="DEU 25:6">6</ref></char></note>“Mũrutani, Musa aatwĩrire atĩ mũndũ angĩkua atarĩ na ciana, mũrũ wa nyina no nginya ahikie mũtumia ũcio wa ndigwa, nĩguo aciarĩre mũrũ wa nyina ciana. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, kwarĩ aanake mũgwanja a nyina ũmwe gatagatĩ-inĩ gaitũ. Nake ũrĩa mũkũrũ akĩhikania na agĩkua, na tondũ ndaarĩ na ciana, agĩtigĩra mũrũ wa nyina mũtumia. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Na gũkĩhaana o ũguo kũrĩ mũrũ wa nyina wa keerĩ, na wa gatatũ, makĩrũmanĩrĩra, magĩkua othe mũgwanja. <verse number="27" style="v"/>Marigĩrĩrio-rĩ, mũtumia ũcio nake agĩkua. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Rĩu-rĩ, hĩndĩ ya kũriũka-rĩ, mũtumia ũcio agaakorwo arĩ wa ũ harĩ acio mũgwanja, tondũ othe nĩmamũhikĩtie?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ mũhĩtĩtie tondũ mũtiũĩ Maandĩko o na kana hinya wa Ngai. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 24:38">Math 24:38</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ya kũriũka andũ matikahikania kana mahike; magaatuĩka ta araika arĩa marĩ kũu igũrũ. <verse number="31" style="v"/>No ha ũhoro wa kũriũka kwa arĩa akuũ-rĩ, kaĩ mũtathomete ũrĩa Ngai oigire atĩrĩ, <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 3:6">Thaam 3:6</ref></char></note>‘Niĩ nĩ niĩ Ngai wa Iburahĩmu, na Ngai wa Isaaka, na Ngai wa Jakubu?’ We ti Ngai wa arĩa akuũ, no nĩ Ngai wa arĩa marĩ muoyo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 7:28">Math 7:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa kĩrĩndĩ kĩu kĩaiguire ũguo, gĩkĩgegio nĩ ũrutani wake.</para>
  <para style="s1">Rĩathani Rĩrĩa Inene</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Afarisai maaiguire atĩ Jesũ nĩahootete Asadukai, magĩcookanĩrĩra hamwe. <verse number="35" style="v"/>Ũmwe wao, warĩ njorua ya watho, akĩmũgeria na kũmũũria kĩũria gĩkĩ: <verse number="36" style="v"/>“Mũrutani, nĩ rĩathani rĩrĩkũ inene thĩinĩ wa Watho?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:37 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 6:5">Gũcook 6:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “ ‘Endaga Mwathani Ngai waku na ngoro yaku yothe, na muoyo waku wothe, na meciiria maku mothe.’ <verse number="38" style="v"/>Rĩĩrĩ nĩrĩo rĩathani rĩa mbere na rĩrĩa inene. <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 19:18">Alaw 19:18</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:43">Math 5:43</ref></char></note>Narĩo rĩa keerĩ no ta rĩu: ‘Endaga mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa wĩyendete wee mwene.’ <verse number="40" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:40 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 7:12">Math 7:12</ref></char></note>Watho wothe na ũrutani wa Anabii ũhingĩtio nĩ maathani macio meerĩ.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Kristũ nĩ Mũrũ wa Ũ?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>Na hĩndĩ ĩyo Afarisai monganĩte hamwe-rĩ, Jesũ akĩmooria atĩrĩ, <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:27">Math 9:27</ref></char></note>“Mwĩciiragia atĩa ũhoro wa Kristũ? Muugaga nĩ mũrũ wa ũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ mũrũ wa Daudi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>Nake akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩĩ gĩagĩtũmire Daudi akĩaria arĩ na Roho amwĩte ‘Mwathani’? Nĩgũkorwo oigire atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="44" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:44 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 110:1">Thab 110:1</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 1:13">Ahib 1:13</ref></char>
    </note>“ ‘Mwathani eerire Mwathani wakwa atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q2">“Ikara guoko-inĩ gwakwa kwa ũrĩo,</para>
  <para style="q1">nginya ngaiga thũ ciaku</para>
  <para style="q2">rungu rwa makinya maku.” ’</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo Daudi amwĩtaga ‘Mwathani-rĩ’, angĩgĩtuĩka mũriũ wake atĩa?” <verse number="46" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">22:46 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 12:34">Mar 12:34</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ wahotire kũmũcookeria, na kuuma mũthenya ũcio gũtirĩ mũndũ wacookire kũgeria kũmũũria ciũria ingĩ.</para>
  <chapter number="23" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Haaro Mĩthemba Mũgwanja</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Jesũ akĩĩra ikundi cia andũ o hamwe na arutwo ake atĩrĩ: <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Arutani a watho na Afarisai maikaragĩra gĩtĩ kĩa Musa. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, maathĩkagĩrei na mwĩkage ũrĩa wothe marĩmwĩraga. No mũtigekage ũrĩa mekaga, nĩgũkorwo matiĩkaga ũrĩa mahunjagia. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 11:46">Luk 11:46</ref></char></note>Mohaga mĩrigo mĩritũ mũno makamĩigĩrĩra ciande cia andũ, no-o ene matiendaga o na kũmĩhutia na kaara.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 6:1">Math 6:1</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 6:2">2</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 6:5">5</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 6:8">Gũcook 6:8</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 15:38">Ndar 15:38</ref></char>
    </note>“Ũrĩa wothe mekaga, mekaga nĩguo monwo nĩ andũ: Maaraaramagia tũthandũkũ tũrĩa meyohaga thiithi tũrĩ na maandĩko thĩinĩ, na makaraihia ciohe cia ndigi cia nguo ciao, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 11:43">Luk 11:43</ref></char></note>na nĩmendete gũikara handũ ha gũtĩĩo maruga-inĩ, na gũikarĩra itĩ cia mbere thĩinĩ wa thunagogi; <verse number="7" style="v"/>na nĩmendete kũgeithio ndũnyũ-inĩ, na gwĩtwo nĩ andũ ‘Rabii’.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>“No inyuĩ mũtikanetwo ‘Rabii’, nĩgũkorwo Mũnene wanyu no ũmwe, na inyuothe mũrĩ a ithe ũmwe. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 1:6">Mar 1:6</ref></char></note>Na mũtikaneete mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ gũkũ thĩ ‘baba’, nĩgũkorwo mũrĩ na Ithe o ũmwe, nake arĩ igũrũ. <verse number="10" style="v"/>O na mũtikanetwo ‘mũrutani’, nĩgũkorwo mũrĩ na ‘Mũrutani’ o ũmwe, nake nĩwe Kristũ. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Ũrĩa mũnene thĩinĩ wanyu nĩatuĩkage ndungata yanyu. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 14:11">Luk 14:11</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ũrĩa wothe wĩtũgagĩria nĩakanyiihio, na ũrĩa wothe wĩnyiihagia nĩagatũũgĩrio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 11:52">Luk 11:52</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ arutani a watho na Afarisai, hinga ici! Mũhingagĩrĩria andũ gũtoonya ũthamaki wa igũrũ, na inyuĩ-ene mũtitoonyaga, o na mũtirekaga arĩa marenda gũtoonya matoonye.</para>
  <para style="p">(<verse number="14" style="v"/>“Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ arutani a watho na Afarisai, hinga ici! Mũtoonyagĩrĩra nyũmba cia atumia a ndigwa, mũkamatunya indo ciao, na mũkahooyaga mahooya maraihu ma kwĩonania. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio nĩmũkaherithio makĩria ma andũ arĩa angĩ.)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 2:11">Atũm 2:11</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:22">Math 5:22</ref></char>
    </note>“Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ arutani a watho na Afarisai hinga ici! Mũtuĩkanagia bũrũri na mũkaringa iria mũgĩcaria mũndũ ũmwe mũmũgarũre amũrũmĩrĩre, na aamũrũmĩrĩra mũkamũtua mũrũ wa Jehanamu maita meerĩ manyu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 23:24">Math 23:24</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:33-35">Math 5:33-35</ref></char>
    </note>“Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ atongoria atumumu! Muugaga atĩrĩ, ‘Mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ angĩĩhĩta na hekarũ, ũcio ti ũndũ; no mũndũ angĩĩhĩta na thahabu ya hekarũ-rĩ, ũcio nĩekuohwo nĩ mwĩhĩtwa wake.’ <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 30:29">Thaam 30:29</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ atumumu aya akĩĩgu! Nĩ kĩĩ kĩnene? Nĩ thahabu ĩyo, kana nĩ hekarũ ĩrĩa ĩtũmaga thahabu ĩtuĩke nyamũre? <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ningĩ muugaga atĩrĩ, ‘Mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ angĩĩhĩta na kĩgongona-rĩ, ũcio ti ũndũ; no mũndũ angĩĩhĩta na kĩheo kĩrĩa kĩrĩ kĩgongona-igũrũ, ũcio nĩekuohwo nĩ mwĩhĩtwa wake.’ <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 29:37">Thaam 29:37</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ andũ aya atumumu! Nĩ kĩĩ kĩnene? Nĩ kĩheo kĩu, kana nĩ kĩgongona kĩrĩa gĩtũmaga kĩheo kĩu gĩtuĩke kĩamũre? <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ũrĩa wĩhĩtaga na kĩgongona, ehĩtaga nakĩo na akehĩta na kĩrĩa gĩothe kĩrĩ kĩgongona-igũrũ. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nake ũrĩa wĩhĩtaga na hekarũ, ehĩtaga nayo na akehĩta na ũrĩa ũikaraga thĩinĩ wayo. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:34">Math 5:34</ref></char></note>Nake ũrĩa wĩhĩtaga na igũrũ, ehĩtaga na gĩtĩ kĩa ũnene kĩa Ngai, na akehĩta na ũrĩa ũgĩikaragĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MIC 6:8">Mik 6:8</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 11:42">Luk 11:42</ref></char>
    </note>“Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ arutani a watho na Afarisai, hinga ici! Mũrutaga gĩcunjĩ gĩa ikũmi kĩa nyeni; na nĩcio terere, na bitharĩ, na thuu. No nĩmũtiganĩirie maũndũ marĩa ma bata makĩria marĩa makoniĩ watho na nĩmo kĩhooto, na kũiguanĩra tha, na wĩhokeku. Maya-rĩ, nĩmo mwagĩrĩirwo nĩ gwĩka mũtegũtiganĩria macio mangĩ. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Inyuĩ atongoria aya atumumu! Inyuĩ mũcungaga rũmuru, no mũkameria ngamĩĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 7:4">Mar 7:4</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 11:39">Luk 11:39</ref></char>
    </note>“Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ arutani a watho na Afarisai, hinga ici! Mũthambagia gĩkombe na mbakũri mwena wa nja, no thĩinĩ-rĩ, kũiyũrĩte ũkoroku na kwenda kwĩhũũnia. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Wee Mũfarisai ũyũ mũtumumu! Amba ũthambie gĩkombe na mbakũri mwena wa thĩinĩ, naguo mwena wa nja o naguo nĩũgũthera.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 11:44">Luk 11:44</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ arutani a watho na Afarisai, hinga ici! Mũhaana mbĩrĩra hake mũnyũ mwerũ, iria cionekaga irĩ thaka mwena wa nja, no thĩinĩ ciyũrĩte mahĩndĩ ma andũ akuũ, na gĩko kĩa mĩthemba yothe. <verse number="28" style="v"/>No taguo andũ mamuonaga mũrĩ athingu mwena wa nja, no mwena wa thĩinĩ mũiyũirwo nĩ ũhinga na waganu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 11:47-48">Luk 11:47-48</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ arutani a watho na Afarisai, hinga ici! Mwakagĩra anabii mbĩrĩra na mũkagemia mbĩrĩra cia arĩa athingu. <verse number="30" style="v"/>Mũgacooka mũkoiga atĩrĩ, ‘Tũngĩarĩ muoyo hĩndĩ ya maithe maitũ-rĩ, tũtingĩagwatanĩire nao gũita thakame ya anabii.’ <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũkaruta ũira wa atĩ inyuĩ mũrĩ njiaro cia arĩa mooragire anabii. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 20:4">Ezek 20:4</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, kĩiyũrĩrĩriei kĩgeri kĩa mehia ma maithe manyu ma tene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:7">Math 3:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Inyuĩ nyoka ici! Inyuĩ ciana cia nduĩra! Mũgaagĩtheema atĩa gũtuĩrwo ciira wa gũikio Jehanamu? <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CH 36:16">2Maũ 36:16</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 11:49">Luk 11:49</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 10:17">Math 10:17</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 10:23">23</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, ngũmũtũmĩra anabii, na andũ arĩa oogĩ, o na arutani. Amwe ao nĩmũkamooraga na mwambe amwe ao mũtĩ-igũrũ, na arĩa angĩ mũmahũũre na iboko thĩinĩ wa thunagogi cianyu na mũmaingate kuuma itũũra rĩmwe nginya rĩrĩa rĩngĩ. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 4:8">Kĩam 4:8</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 1:1">Zek 1:1</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 24:21">2Maũ 24:21</ref></char></note>Na nĩmũgagĩcookererwo nĩ thakame yothe ya andũ arĩa athingu, ĩrĩa ĩrĩkĩtie gũitwo gũkũ thĩ, kuuma thakame ya Habili ũrĩa warĩ mũthingu, nginya thakame ya Zekaria mũrũ wa Barakia, ũrĩa mworagĩire gatagatĩ ka Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru na kĩgongona. <verse number="36" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, maũndũ maya mothe nĩmagakinyĩra rũciaro rũrũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:37 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CH 24:21">2Maũ 24:21</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 118:26">Thab 118:26</ref></char>
    </note>“Wee Jerusalemu, Jerusalemu, wee ũragaga anabii, na ũkahũũra arĩa matũmĩtwo kũrĩ wee na mahiga nyuguto, nĩ maita maingĩ atĩa ndanenda gũcookanĩrĩria ciana ciaku hamwe, ta ũrĩa ngũkũ ĩcookanagĩrĩria tũcui twayo rungu rwa mathagu mayo, no ndũnjĩtĩkagĩria! <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 22:5">Jer 22:5</ref></char></note>Atĩrĩrĩ, nyũmba yaku ĩtigĩtwo ĩkirĩte ihooru. <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">23:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 118:26">Thab 118:26</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 21:9">Math 21:9</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 19:44">Luk 19:44</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, kuuma rĩu mũtikanyona rĩngĩ nginya rĩrĩa mũkoiga atĩrĩ, ‘Kũrathimwo nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũgũũka na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani.’ ”</para>
  <chapter number="24" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Marũũri ma Mahinda ma Mũthia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akiuma hekarũ, na rĩrĩa aathiiaga arutwo ake magĩũka kũrĩ we nĩguo mamuonie mĩako ya hekarũ. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 19:44">Luk 19:44</ref></char></note>Akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nĩmũkuona indo ici ciothe? Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, gũtirĩ ihiga o na rĩmwe rĩa maya rĩgaakorwo rĩrĩ igũrũ wa rĩrĩa rĩngĩ; mothe nĩmakamomorwo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Jesũ aikarĩte thĩ Kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Mĩtamaiyũ-rĩ, arutwo ake magĩũka harĩ we hatarĩ andũ angĩ, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ta twĩre, maũndũ macio mageekĩka rĩ, na kĩmenyithia gĩa gũcooka gwaku na kĩa mũthia wa mahinda maya nĩ kĩrĩkũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 13:5">Mar 13:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Mwĩmenyagĩrĩrei mũtikanaheenio nĩ mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 24:11">Math 24:11</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 24:23">23</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 24:24">24</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo andũ aingĩ nĩmagooka na rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, makiugaga atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ nĩ niĩ Kristũ,’ na nĩ makaheenia andũ aingĩ. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nĩmũkaigua ũhoro wa mbaara, na mũhuhu ũkoniĩ mbaara, no inyuĩ mũtikanamake. Maũndũ ta macio no nginya mageekĩka, no ithirĩro ti rĩkinyu. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 19:2">Isa 19:2</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 11:28">Atũm 11:28</ref></char></note>Rũrĩrĩ nĩrũgookĩrĩra rũrĩa rũngĩ, na ũthamaki ũũkĩrĩre ũrĩa ũngĩ. Nĩgũkaagĩa ngʼaragu na ithingithia kũndũ na kũndũ. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Maũndũ macio mothe nĩ kĩambĩrĩria kĩa ruo ta rwa mũndũ-wa-nja akĩrũmwo agĩe mwana.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:17">Math 10:17</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:2">Joh 16:2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 15:21">Joh 15:21</ref></char>
    </note>“Ningĩ nĩmũkaneanwo mũnyariirwo na mũũragwo, na mũmenwo nĩ ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ ũndũ wakwa. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo-rĩ, andũ aingĩ nĩmagatiganĩria wĩtĩkio na makunyananĩre mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ, na mamenane. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 7:15">Math 7:15</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 13:5">Math 13:5</ref></char></note>Na anabii aingĩ a maheeni nĩmakoimĩra na nĩmakaheenia andũ aingĩ. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Na tondũ waganu nĩũkaingĩha mũno-rĩ, wendani wa andũ aingĩ nĩũkanyiiha, <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:22">Math 10:22</ref></char></note>no ũrĩa ũgaakirĩrĩria nginya hĩndĩ ya ithirĩro-rĩ, ũcio nĩakahonoka. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:23">Math 4:23</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 10:16">Arom 10:16</ref></char></note>Naguo Ũhoro-ũyũ-Mwega wa ũthamaki nĩũkahunjio thĩ yothe ũtuĩke ũira kũrĩ ndũrĩrĩ ciothe, na thuutha ũcio ithirĩro rĩkinye.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 6:13">Atũm 6:13</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 9:27">Dan 9:27</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio rĩrĩa mũkoona ‘kĩndũ kĩrĩa kĩrĩ thaahu na gĩa kũrehe ihooru’ kĩrũgamĩte Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru, o kĩrĩa kĩarĩtio na kanua ka mũnabii Danieli (ũrĩa ũrathoma nĩamenye ũhoro ũcio), <verse number="16" style="v"/>hĩndĩ ĩyo arĩa marĩ Judea nĩmorĩre irĩma-inĩ. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1SA 9:25">1Sam 9:25</ref></char></note>Mũndũ ũrĩa ũrĩ nyũmba yake igũrũ ndakaharũrũke atĩ akarute kĩndũ kuuma nyũmba yake. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nake ũrĩa wĩ mũgũnda ndagacooke mũciĩ kũgĩĩra nguo ciake. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 23:29">Luk 23:29</ref></char></note>Kaĩ atumia arĩa magaakorwo na nda na arĩa magaakorwo makĩongithia hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩmagakorwo na thĩĩna-ĩ! <verse number="20" style="v"/>Hooyai nĩguo gwĩthara kwanyu gũtikanakorwo kũrĩ hĩndĩ ya heho kana mũthenya wa Thabatũ. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOL 2:2">Joel 2:2</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩgũkagĩa na mĩnyamaro mĩnene, ĩtarĩ yoneka kuuma kĩambĩrĩria gĩa thĩ nginya rĩu, na ĩtakooneka rĩngĩ. <verse number="22" style="v"/>Na tiga matukũ macio makuhĩhirio-rĩ, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩkaahonoka, no nĩ tondũ wa andũ arĩa aamũre, matukũ macio nĩmagakuhĩhio. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 17:23">Luk 17:23</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ angĩkamwĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Kristũ arĩ na haha!’ kana, ‘Arĩ harĩa!’ Mũtikanetĩkie ũhoro ũcio. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TH 2:9-11">2Athe 2:9-11</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Kristũ a maheeni na anabii a maheeni nĩmakeyumĩria monanie morirũ manene na maringe ciama, nĩguo maheenie o na arĩa aamũre, korwo no kũhoteke. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, inyuĩ ndaamũmenyithia ũhoro ũcio mbere ya hĩndĩ ĩyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ angĩkamwĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Arĩ werũ-inĩ,’ mũtikanathiĩ kuo; kana angĩmwĩra, ‘Arĩ nyũmba thĩinĩ,’ mũtikanetĩkie ũhoro ũcio. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 17:24">Luk 17:24</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 8:20">Math 8:20</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo o ta ũrĩa rũheni ruumĩte irathĩro ruonekaga ithũĩro-rĩ, ũguo noguo gũũka kwa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ gũgaakorwo kũhaana. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 17:37">Luk 17:37</ref></char></note>Harĩa hothe harĩ kĩimba, hau nĩho nderi ciũnganaga.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 32:7">Ezek 32:7</ref>; <ref loc="JOL 2:10">Joel 2:10</ref>, <ref loc="JOL 2:31">31</ref></char>
    </note>“Na rĩrĩ, o rĩmwe thuutha wa mĩnyamaro ya matukũ macio,</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘riũa nĩrĩkagĩa nduma,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo mweri ũtige kwara;</para>
  <para style="q1">nacio njata nĩikaagũa kuuma igũrũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">namo maahinya ma igũrũ nĩmakenyenyio.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 1:7">Kũg 1:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Hĩndĩ ĩyo kĩmenyithia kĩa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩgĩkooneka kũu igũrũ, na ndũrĩrĩ ciothe cia thĩ nĩigacakaya. Nĩikoona Mũrũ wa Mũndũ agĩũka arĩ igũrũ rĩa matu, na arĩ na hinya na riiri mũingĩ. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 27:13">Isa 27:13</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 15:52">1Akor 15:52</ref></char></note>Nake nĩagatũma araika ake na mũgambo mũnene wa karumbeta, nao nĩmakoongania arĩa ake aamũre moimĩte mĩena ĩna ĩrĩa yumaga rũhuho, kuuma gĩturi kĩmwe kĩa igũrũ nginya kĩrĩa kĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>“Na rĩrĩ, mwĩrutei na mũkũyũ: Rĩrĩa honge ciaguo ciarĩkia gũthundũka na ciaruta mathangũ-rĩ, nĩmũmenyaga atĩ hĩndĩ ya riũa ĩrĩ hakuhĩ. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 5:9">Jak 5:9</ref></char></note>Ũguo noguo rĩrĩa mũkoona maũndũ macio mothe, mũkaamenya atĩ ihinda rĩrĩ hakuhĩ, rĩrĩ o ta mũrango-inĩ. <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:28">Math 16:28</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, rũciaro rũrũ rũtigaathira nginya maũndũ macio mothe mahinge. <verse number="35" style="v"/>Igũrũ na thĩ nĩigathira, no ciugo ciakwa itigathira.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũthenya na Thaa Itiũĩkaine</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 1:7">Atũm 1:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũũĩ ũhoro wa mũthenya ũcio kana ithaa rĩu, o na araika a igũrũ matiũĩ, o na Mũriũ ndooĩ, tiga no Ithe wiki. <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 6:5">Kĩam 6:5</ref></char></note>O ta ũrĩa gwatariĩ matukũ-inĩ ma Nuhu, noguo gũkahaana hĩndĩ ya gũũka kwa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 22:30">Math 22:30</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo o ta ũrĩa gwatariĩ matukũ marĩa maarĩ mbere ya kĩguũ, andũ nĩmarĩĩaga na makanyua, na nĩmahikanagia na makahika, o nginya mũthenya ũrĩa Nuhu aatoonyire thabina; <verse number="39" style="v"/>nao matiamenyire nginya rĩrĩa kĩguũ gĩokire, gĩkĩmaniina othe. Ũguo noguo gũkahaana hĩndĩ ya gũũka kwa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ. <verse number="40" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:40 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 17:34">Luk 17:34</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo arũme eerĩ magaakorwo marĩ mũgũnda; ũmwe nĩakoywo na ũrĩa ũngĩ atigwo. <verse number="41" style="v"/>Andũ-a-nja eerĩ magaakorwo magĩthĩa hamwe; ũmwe nĩakoywo na ũrĩa ũngĩ atigwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:42 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 25:13">Math 25:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ikaragai mwĩiguĩte, tondũ mũtiũĩ mũthenya ũrĩa Mwathani wanyu agooka. <verse number="43" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:43 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 12:39">Luk 12:39</ref></char></note>No menyai atĩrĩ, korwo mwene nyũmba nĩamenyete thaa cia ũtukũ iria mũici angĩũka, angĩaikarire eiguĩte, nyũmba yake ĩtuuo. <verse number="44" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:44 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 5:6">1Athe 5:6</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio o na inyuĩ no nginya mũikarage mwĩhaarĩirie, tondũ Mũrũ wa Mũndũ agooka ithaa rĩrĩa mũtamwĩrĩgĩrĩire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:45 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 25:21">Math 25:21</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 25:23">23</ref></char>
    </note>“Ningĩ-rĩ, ndungata ya kwĩhokeka na njũgĩ nĩĩrĩkũ, ĩrĩa mwathi wayo angĩĩhokera kũroraga ndungata iria ingĩ cia nyũmba yake, na ĩciheage irio ihinda rĩrĩa rĩagĩrĩire? <verse number="46" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:46 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 16:15">Kĩam 16:15</ref></char></note>Kaĩ nĩũgaakorwo ũrĩ ũndũ mwega harĩ ndungata ĩyo, rĩrĩa mwathi wayo agooka akore ĩgĩĩka o ũguo-ĩ! <verse number="47" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, nĩakamĩĩhokera indo ciake ciothe. <verse number="48" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, ndungata ĩyo ĩngĩkorwo nĩ njaganu, na ĩĩre na ngoro atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathi wakwa nĩegũikara ihinda iraaya atacookete,’ <verse number="49" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:49 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 21:34">Luk 21:34</ref></char></note>na ĩkĩambĩrĩrie kũhũũra ndungata iria ingĩ, na kũrĩa na kũnyua hamwe na arĩĩu. <verse number="50" style="v"/>Mwathi wa ndungata ĩyo agooka mũthenya ũrĩa ĩtamwĩrĩgĩrĩire, na ithaa rĩrĩa ĩtooĩ. <verse number="51" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">24:51 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 8:12">Math 8:12</ref></char></note>Nake nĩakamĩherithia mũno, na amĩikie hamwe na andũ arĩa hinga, kũrĩa gũgaakorwo na kĩrĩro na kũhagarania magego.</para>
  <chapter number="25" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Airĩtu Ikũmi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:24">Math 13:24</ref>; <ref loc="REV 19:7">Kũg 19:7</ref>; <ref loc="REV 21:2">21:2</ref></char>
    </note>“Hĩndĩ ĩyo-rĩ, ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũkaahaananio na airĩtu ikũmi arĩa mooire matawa mao, makiumagara nĩguo magatũnge mũhikania. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Atano ao maarĩ akĩĩgu, na atano maarĩ oogĩ. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Acio akĩĩgu nĩmakuuire matawa mao, no matiakuuire maguta. <verse number="4" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, acio oogĩ, nĩmakuuire maguta na cuba, o hamwe na matawa mao. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">25:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 5:6">1Athe 5:6</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, Mũhikania nĩaikarire angĩgooka, na othe magĩcũnga, magĩkoma.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>“Na ũtukũ gatagatĩ gũkĩanĩrĩrwo atĩrĩ: ‘Mũhikania nĩ mũũku! Umai mũkamũtũnge!’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>“Hĩndĩ ĩyo airĩtu othe magĩũkĩra, magĩthondeka matawa mao. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">25:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 12:35">Luk 12:35</ref></char></note>Acio akĩĩgu makĩĩra acio oogĩ atĩrĩ, ‘Tũgaĩrei maguta manyu tondũ; matawa maitũ nĩmarahora.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>“No acio oogĩ makĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, ‘Aca, matingĩtũigana na mamũigane. Handũ ha ũguo-rĩ, thiĩi kũrĩ arĩa mendagia maguta mũkegũrĩre manyu.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>“No rĩrĩa maarĩ njĩra-inĩ magĩthiĩ kũgũra maguta-rĩ, mũhikania agĩkinya. Airĩtu arĩa mehaarĩirie magĩtoonya kĩhikanio-inĩ hamwe na mũhikania. Naguo mũrango ũkĩhingwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>“Thuutha ũcio airĩtu acio angĩ o nao magĩũka. Makiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathani! Mwathani! Tũhingũrĩre mũrango!’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>“Nowe agĩcookia atĩrĩ, ‘Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, niĩ ndimũũĩ.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 24:42">Math 24:42</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 24:44">44</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, mwĩhũgagei, tondũ mũtiũĩ mũthenya kana thaa.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngerekano ya Taranda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 21:33">Math 21:33</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 19:12">Luk 19:12</ref></char>
    </note>“Ningĩ, ũthamaki wa igũrũ ũkaahaananio na mũndũ wathiiaga rũgendo, nake agĩĩta ndungata ciake, agĩciĩhokera indo ciake. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">25:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 18:24">Math 18:24</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 18:25">25</ref></char></note>Akĩnengera ĩmwe yacio taranda ithano cia mbeeca, na ĩngĩ taranda igĩrĩ, na ĩrĩa ĩngĩ taranda ĩmwe, o ndungata kũringana na ũhoti wayo. Agĩcooka agĩthiĩ rũgendo. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Ndungata ĩrĩa yaneetwo taranda ithano ĩgĩthiĩ o hĩndĩ ĩyo, ĩkĩonjorithia mbeeca ciayo, na ĩkĩona uumithio wa taranda ingĩ ithano. <verse number="17" style="v"/>O nayo ĩrĩa yaheetwo taranda igĩrĩ ĩkĩonjorithia ĩkĩona uumithio wa ingĩ igĩrĩ. <verse number="18" style="v"/>No ndungata ĩrĩa yaheetwo taranda ĩmwe ĩgĩthiĩ, ĩkĩenja irima, ĩkĩhitha mbeeca cia mwathi wayo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 18:23">Math 18:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Thuutha wa ihinda iraaya, mwathi wa ndungata icio nĩacookire na agĩciĩta nĩguo iheane ũhoro wa mathabu ma mbeeca ciake. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Ndungata ĩrĩa yaheetwo taranda ithano ĩkĩrehe ingĩ ithano, ĩkiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathi wakwa, waheire taranda ithano. Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩĩthũkũmĩte ingĩ ithano.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 24:45">Math 24:45</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 24:47">47</ref></char>
    </note>“Nake mwathi wayo akĩmĩcookeria atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩwĩkĩte wega, wee ndungata ĩno njega na ya kwĩhokeka! Nĩũtuĩkĩte mwĩhokeku harĩ indo nini; nĩngũgũtua mũrori wa indo nyingĩ. Ũka ũtoonye gĩkeno-inĩ kĩa mwathi waku!’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>“Ndungata ĩrĩa yaheetwo taranda igĩrĩ o nayo ĩgĩũka. Ĩkiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathi wakwa waheire taranda igĩrĩ! Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩthũkũmĩte ingĩ igĩrĩ.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>“Nake mwathi wayo akĩmĩcookeria atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩwĩkĩte wega, wee ndungata ĩno njega na ya kwĩhokeka! Nĩũtuĩkĩte mwĩhokeku harĩ indo nini; nĩ ngũgũtua mũrori wa indo nyingĩ. Ũka ũtoonye gĩkeno-inĩ kĩa Mwathi waku!’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>“Nayo ndungata ĩrĩa yaheetwo taranda ĩmwe o nayo ĩgĩũka. Ĩkiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathi wakwa, nĩ ndooĩ atĩ wee wĩ mũndũ mwĩĩ, ũgethaga kũrĩa ũtahandĩte, na ũkongania kũrĩa ũtaahandire mbeũ. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio nĩndetigĩrire, ngĩthiĩ ngĩhitha taranda yaku thĩ. Atĩrĩrĩ, ĩno no ĩrĩa yaku ndagũcookeria.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>“Nake mwathi wayo akĩmĩcookeria atĩrĩ, ‘Wee ndungata ĩno njaganu na ngũũtaru! Ũguo nĩ wooĩ atĩ ngethaga kũrĩa itahaandĩte, na ngongania kũrĩa itaahurĩte mbeũ? <verse number="27" style="v"/>Gũkĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, wagĩrĩirwo nĩ kũiga mbeeca ciakwa bengi, na ndacooka-rĩ, nĩingĩacookerio mbeeca ciakwa irĩ hamwe na uumithio wacio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>“ ‘Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, mĩtunyei taranda ĩyo, mũmĩnengere ũrĩa ũrĩ na taranda ikũmi. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">25:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 13:12">Math 13:12</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ o wothe ũrĩ na indo nĩwe ũkoongererwo ingĩ nyingĩ na akĩrĩrĩrio. Nake ũrĩa ũtarĩ, o na kĩrĩa arĩ nakĩo nĩagatuunywo. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">25:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 8:12">Math 8:12</ref></char></note>Oyai ndungata ĩyo ĩtarĩ bata mũmĩikie nja kũu nduma-inĩ, kũrĩa gũgaakorwo kĩrĩro na kũhagarania magego.’</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngʼondu na Mbũri</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 17:30">Luk 17:30</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 19:28">Math 19:28</ref></char>
    </note>“Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ agooka arĩ na riiri wake, na araika othe marĩ hamwe nake, nĩagaikarĩra gĩtĩ gĩake kĩa ũnene na kĩrĩ riiri wa igũrũ. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">25:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 34:17">Ezek 34:17</ref>, <ref loc="EZK 34:20">20</ref></char></note>Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩigacookanĩrĩrio mbere yake, nake nĩakamũrania andũ kuuma kũrĩ arĩa angĩ, o ta ũrĩa mũrĩithi aamũranagia ngʼondu na mbũri. <verse number="33" style="v"/>Nĩakaiga ngʼondu mwena wake wa ũrĩo, na mbũri aciige mwena wake wa ũmotho.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 15:50">1Akor 15:50</ref>; <ref loc="REV 13:8">Kũg 13:8</ref></char>
    </note>“Ningĩ Mũthamaki nĩakeera arĩa marĩ mwena wake wa ũrĩo atĩrĩ, ‘Ũkai, inyuĩ mũrathimĩtwo nĩ Baba; oyai igai rĩa ũthamaki ũrĩa mwathondekeirwo kuuma rĩrĩa thĩ yombirwo. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">25:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 31:32">Ayub 31:32</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 13:2">Ahib 13:2</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ndaarĩ mũhũũtu mũkĩĩhe gĩa kũrĩa, na ndaarĩ mũnyootu mũkĩĩhe gĩa kũnyua, na ndaarĩ mũgeni mũkĩĩnyiita ũgeni, <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">25:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 58:7">Isa 58:7</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 2:15">Jak 2:15</ref>, <ref loc="JAS 2:16">16</ref></char></note>na ndaarĩ njaga mũkĩĩhe nguo, na ndaarĩ mũrũaru na inyuĩ mũkĩĩmenyerera, o na ndaarĩ njeera na mũgĩũka kũndora.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>“Hĩndĩ ĩyo arĩa athingu nĩmakamũcookeria mamũũrie atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathani, nĩ rĩ twakuonire ũrĩ mũhũũtu tũgĩkũhe gĩa kũrĩa, kana ũrĩ mũnyootu tũgĩkũhe gĩa kũnyua? <verse number="38" style="v"/>Na nĩ rĩ twakuonire ũrĩ mũgeni tũgĩkũnyiita ũgeni, kana ũrĩ njaga tũgĩkũhe nguo? <verse number="39" style="v"/>O na nĩ rĩ twakuonire ũrĩ mũrũaru kana ũrĩ njeera na tũgĩũka gũkũrora?’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:40 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:40">Math 10:40</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 10:42">42</ref></char>
    </note>“Nake Mũthamaki nĩagacookia, ameere atĩrĩ, ‘Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ũndũ wothe mwekĩire ariũ a Baba o na arĩa anini mũno, nĩ niĩ mwekĩire.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:41 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 7:23">Math 7:23</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 9:43">Mar 9:43</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 2:4">2Pet 2:4</ref></char>
    </note>“Ningĩ nĩakeera arĩa marĩ mwena wake wa ũmotho atĩrĩ, ‘Njehererai, inyuĩ mũrumĩtwo, mũthiĩ mwaki-inĩ wa tene na tene ũrĩa ũthondekeirwo mũcukani na araika ake. <verse number="42" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo ndaarĩ mũhũũtu na mũtiaheire gĩa kũrĩa, na ndaarĩ mũnyootu na mũtiaheire gĩa kũnyua, <verse number="43" style="v"/>na ndaarĩ mũgeni na mũtianyiitire ũgeni, ndaarĩ njaga na mũtiaheire nguo, ndaarĩ mũrũaru na ndaarĩ njeera na mũtiokire kũnyona.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v"/>“Nao nĩmagacookia, mamũũrie atĩrĩ, ‘Mwathani, nĩ rĩ twakuonire ũrĩ mũhũũtu, kana ũrĩ mũnyootu, kana ũrĩ mũgeni, kana ũrĩ njaga, kana ũrĩ mũrũaru, o na kana ũrĩ njeera na tũtiagũteithirie?’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:45 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 14:31">Thim 14:31</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 17:5">Thim 17:5</ref></char>
    </note>“Nake nĩakamacookeria atĩrĩ, ‘Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ũndũ o wothe mũteekire ũmwe wa aya anini mũno, nĩ niĩ mũteekĩire.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:46 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 19:29">Math 19:29</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 12:2">Dan 12:2</ref></char>
    </note>“Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩmagathiĩ kũrĩa andũ maherithagio tene na tene, no arĩa athingu mathiĩ muoyo-inĩ wa tene na tene.”</para>
  <chapter number="26" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gũciirĩra Kũũraga Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 7:28">Math 7:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aarĩkirie kuuga maũndũ macio mothe-rĩ, akĩĩra arutwo ake atĩrĩ, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 11:55">Joh 11:55</ref></char></note>“O ta ũrĩa mũũĩ, Gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka gĩtigairie matukũ meerĩ gĩkinye, nake Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩakaneanwo nĩgeetha aambwo mũtĩ-igũrũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 2:2">Thab 2:2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:47-53">Joh 11:47-53</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na athuuri a kĩrĩndĩ makĩgomana kwa mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene, wetagwo Kaiafa, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 12:14">Math 12:14</ref></char></note>nĩguo maciire ũrĩa mangĩnyiitithia Jesũ na njĩra ya wara, na mamũũragithie. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 27:24">Math 27:24</ref></char></note>No makiuga atĩrĩ, “Tũtingĩmũnyiita hĩndĩ ya Gĩathĩ, nĩguo andũ matikarute haaro.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũitĩrĩrio Maguta Bethania</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 21:17">Math 21:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩmwe Jesũ aarĩ Bethania, mũciĩ wa mũndũ wetagwo Simoni ũrĩa warĩ na mũrimũ wa mangũ, <verse number="7" style="v"/>na mũndũ-wa-nja warĩ na cuba ya maguta ma goro mũno na manungi wega, agĩũka kũrĩ Jesũ, akĩmũitĩrĩria maguta mũtwe arĩ metha-inĩ akĩrĩa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa arutwo moonire ũguo, makĩrakara, makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Ũitangi ũyũ nĩ wakĩ? <verse number="9" style="v"/>Maguta macio manungi wega nĩmangĩendio goro na mbeeca icio iheo athĩĩni.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ aamenya ũguo, akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Mũrathĩĩnia mũndũ-wa-nja ũyũ nĩkĩ? We nĩanjĩka ũndũ mwega. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 15:11">Gũcook 15:11</ref></char></note>Arĩa athĩĩni mũrĩkoragwo nao hĩndĩ ciothe, no niĩ-rĩ, mũtirĩkoragwo na niĩ hĩndĩ ciothe. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 19:40">Joh 19:40</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aitĩrĩirie mwĩrĩ wakwa maguta macio manungi wega, eekire ũguo nĩgeetha aathagathage ũrĩa ngaathikwo. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, kũrĩa guothe Ũhoro-ũyũ-Mwega ũkaahunjio thĩinĩ wa thĩ yothe-rĩ, ũndũ ũcio eeka nĩũkeeragwo andũ nĩgeetha aririkanagwo.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Judasi Gwĩtĩkĩra Gũkunyanĩra Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo ũmwe wa acio ikũmi na eerĩ, ũrĩa wetagwo Judasi Mũisikariota, agĩthiĩ kũrĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 11:12">Zek 11:12</ref></char></note>akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩĩ mũkũũhe ingĩmũneana kũrĩ inyuĩ?” Nao makĩmũtarĩra icunjĩ cia betha mĩrongo ĩtatũ, makĩmũnengera. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Kuuma hĩndĩ ĩyo Judasi akĩambĩrĩria gũcaria mweke wa kũmũneana.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 12:18-20">Thaam 12:18-20</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 16:5-8">Gũcook 16:5-8</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya wa mbere wa kwambĩrĩria kũrĩa Mĩgate ĩrĩa ĩtarĩ Mĩĩkĩre Ndawa ya Kũimbia-rĩ, arutwo magĩthiĩ kũrĩ Jesũ makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũkwenda tũkahaarĩrie irio cia Bathaka kũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Thiĩi itũũra-inĩ kũrĩ mũndũ mũna mũmwĩre atĩrĩ, ‘Mũrutani oiga atĩrĩ: Ihinda rĩakwa rĩrĩa rĩtuĩtwo rĩrĩ hakuhĩ. Ngũrĩĩra irio cia Bathaka nyũmba gwaku tũrĩ na arutwo akwa.’ ” <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio arutwo magĩĩka o ũrĩa Jesũ aamathĩte, na makĩhaarĩria irio cia Bathaka.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Gwakinya hwaĩ-inĩ-rĩ, Jesũ agĩikara metha-inĩ ya irio hamwe na arutwo ake acio ikũmi na eerĩ. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa maarĩĩaga, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ũmwe wanyu nĩekũngunyanĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nao makĩnyiitwo nĩ kĩeha mũno, makĩambĩrĩria kũmũũria o mũndũ atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ti-itherũ nĩ niĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:18">Joh 13:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũrĩa waikanĩria guoko na niĩ mbakũri-inĩ nĩwe ũrĩngunyanĩra. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 53">Isa 53</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 9:12">Mar 9:12</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 24:25-27">Luk 24:25-27</ref></char></note>Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩegũthiĩ o ta ũrĩa ũhoro wake wandĩkĩtwo. No mũndũ ũrĩa ũgũkunyanĩra Mũrũ wa Mũndũ kaĩ arĩ na haaro-ĩ! Nĩ kaba mũndũ ũcio atangĩaciarirwo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:4">Math 10:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Judasi, ũrĩa mũmũkunyanĩri, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Rabii, ti-itherũ nĩ niĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ, nĩwe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa maarĩĩaga, Jesũ akĩoya mũgate, agĩcookia ngaatho, akĩwenyũranga, akĩhe arutwo ake, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Oyai mũrĩe; ũyũ nĩ mwĩrĩ wakwa.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 10:16">1Akor 10:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Agĩcooka akĩoya gĩkombe, agĩcookia ngaatho, akĩmanengera, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nyuanĩrai inyuothe. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 9:20">Ahib 9:20</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 20:28">Math 20:28</ref></char></note>Ĩno nĩyo thakame yakwa ya kĩrĩkanĩro, ĩrĩa ĩgũitwo nĩ ũndũ wa andũ aingĩ nĩ ũndũ wa kũrekanĩrwo kwa mehia. <verse number="29" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, ndikũnyua rĩngĩ ndibei ya maciaro ma mũthabibũ kuuma rĩu nginya mũthenya ũrĩa ngaamĩnyuanĩra na inyuĩ ĩrĩ njerũ ũthamaki-inĩ wa Baba.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 21:1">Math 21:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na maarĩkia kũina rwĩmbo-rĩ, makiumagara magĩthiĩ Kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Mĩtamaiyũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kuuga ũrĩa Petero Akaamũkaana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 13:7">Zek 13:7</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:32">Joh 16:32</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Jesũ agĩcooka akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ũtukũ wa ũmũthĩ inyuothe nĩmũrĩĩndirika nĩgũkorwo nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“ ‘Nĩngaringa mũrĩithi,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio ngʼondu cia rũũru ihurunjũke.’</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 28:7">Math 28:7</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 28:10">10</ref></char>
    </note>No ndariũkio-rĩ, nĩngamũtongoria gũthiĩ Galili.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>No Petero akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “O na arĩa angĩ othe mangĩgũtirika, niĩ ndigagũtirika.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:38">Joh 13:38</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ũmũthĩ, ũtukũ o ũyũ ngũkũ ĩtanakũga, ũrĩkorwo ũngaanĩte maita matatũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:37">Joh 13:37</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No Petero akiuga atĩrĩ, “O na angĩkorwo nĩgũkua ndĩkuanĩra nawe, niĩ ndingĩgũkaana.” Nao arutwo arĩa angĩ othe makiuga o ũguo.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũgũnda wa Gethisemane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>Ningĩ Jesũ agĩcooka agĩthiĩ na arutwo ake handũ heetagwo Gethisemane, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ikarai haha, na niĩ thiĩ haarĩa ngahooe.” <verse number="37" style="v"/>Agĩthiĩ na Petero, na ariũ arĩa eerĩ a Zebedi, nake akĩambĩrĩria kũigua kĩeha na gũthĩĩnĩka ngoro. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:27">Joh 12:27</ref></char></note>Agĩcooka akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ngoro yakwa ĩrĩ na kĩeha mũno, o hakuhĩ gũkua. Ikarai haha mwĩiguĩte hamwe na niĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:39 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 20:22">Math 20:22</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:38">Joh 6:38</ref></char>
    </note>Agĩthiiathiia, agĩturumithia ũthiũ thĩ, akĩhooya, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Baba, kũngĩhoteka-rĩ, njehereria gĩkombe gĩkĩ. No ti ũrĩa niĩ ngwenda, no nĩ ũrĩa wee ũkwenda.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:40 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:38">Math 26:38</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo agĩcooka kũrĩ arutwo ake, agĩkora makomete, akĩũria Petero atĩrĩ, “Mũtingĩhota gũikara ithaa rĩmwe mwĩiguĩte hamwe na niĩ? <verse number="41" style="v"/>Mwĩhũgei na mũhooe nĩguo mũtikagwe magerio-inĩ. Ngoro nĩyenda, no mwĩrĩ ndũrĩ na hinya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v"/>Jesũ agĩthiĩ riita rĩa keerĩ, akĩhooya, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Baba, angĩkorwo gũtingĩhoteka njehererio gĩkombe gĩkĩ itakĩnyuĩrĩire-rĩ, wendi waku ũrohingio.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>Aacooka rĩngĩ akĩmakora makomete, tondũ nĩmahĩtĩtwo nĩ toro. <verse number="44" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio akĩmatiga, agĩthiĩ, akĩhooya rĩngĩ riita rĩa gatatũ, akiuga ciugo o ro icio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>Ningĩ agĩcooka kũrĩ arutwo akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “O na rĩu mũrĩ o toro mũhurũkĩte? Atĩrĩrĩ, ihinda rĩ hakuhĩ, na Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩakunyanĩirwo moko-inĩ ma andũ ehia. <verse number="46" style="v"/>Ũkĩrai, tũthiĩ! Ũrĩa ũkũngunyanĩra nĩarooka!”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũnyiitwo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:47 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:4">Math 10:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O akĩaragia-rĩ, Judasi, ũmwe wa arutwo arĩa ikũmi na eerĩ, agĩkinya. Ookire na gĩkundi kĩnene kĩa andũ, marĩ na hiũ cia njora na njũgũma, matũmĩtwo nĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na athuuri a kĩama. <verse number="48" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, ũcio wamũkunyanĩire nĩamaheete kĩmenyithia gĩkĩ: “Ũrĩa ndĩmumunya, ũcio nĩwe, mũnyiitei.” <verse number="49" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:49 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:25">Math 26:25</ref></char></note>Nake Judasi agĩthiĩ harĩ Jesũ o rĩmwe, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Rabii, ũrĩ mũhoro!” na akĩmũmumunya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:50 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 20:13">Math 20:13</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 22:12">Math 22:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũrata wakwa, ĩka ũrĩa ũũkire gwĩka.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao andũ acio makĩmũguthũkĩra, makĩmũnyiita. <verse number="51" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:51 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 22:36">Luk 22:36</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 22:38">38</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 18:10">Joh 18:10</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, mũndũ ũmwe wa arĩa maarĩ na Jesũ agĩcomora rũhiũ rwake rwa njora, agĩtinia gũtũ kwa ndungata ya mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:52 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 9:6">Kĩam 9:6</ref>; <ref loc="REV 13:10">Kũg 13:10</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Cookia rũhiũ rwaku njora nĩgũkorwo arĩa othe macomoraga rũhiũ makaaniinwo na rũhiũ. <verse number="53" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:53 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 6:17">2Ath 6:17</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 7:10">Dan 7:10</ref></char></note>Kana ũgwĩciiria ndingĩhota kũhooya Baba, na o rĩmwe andũmĩre araika makĩria ya mbũtũ ikũmi na igĩrĩ? <verse number="54" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:54 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:24">Math 26:24</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, Maandĩko mangĩkĩhinga atĩa marĩa moigĩte atĩ ũndũ ũyũ no nginya ũhinge na njĩra ĩno?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akĩũria kĩrĩndĩ kĩu atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ ndĩ mũtongoria wa akararia a watho, atĩ nĩkĩo muoka mũũnyiite mũrĩ na hiũ cia njora na njũgũma? O mũthenya ndĩrakoragwo hekarũ-inĩ ngĩrutana, na mũtingĩĩnyiita. <verse number="56" style="v"/>No ũndũ ũyũ wothe wĩkĩkĩĩte nĩguo ũhoro ũrĩa waandĩkĩtwo nĩ anabii ũhinge.” Nao arutwo othe makĩmũtiganĩria, makĩũra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũtwarwo Kĩama-inĩ kĩa Ayahudi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v"/>Nao acio maanyiitire Jesũ makĩmũtwara gwa Kaiafa, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene, kũrĩa arutani a watho na athuuri moonganĩte. <verse number="58" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:58 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 18:15">Joh 18:15</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 15:16">Mar 15:16</ref></char></note>Nowe Petero akĩmũrũmĩrĩra arĩ haraaya, o nginya agĩkinya nja ya kwa mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũcio mũnene. Agĩtoonya agĩikarania na arangĩri nĩguo amenye ũrĩa ũhoro ũgũthiĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="59" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na Kĩama kĩrĩa Kĩnene gĩothe nĩmacarĩrĩirie ũira wa maheeni nĩguo mamũũragithie. <verse number="60" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:60 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 27:12">Thab 27:12</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 35:11">35:11</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 19:15">Gũcook 19:15</ref></char></note>No makĩaga ũira ta ũcio, o na gũkorwo andũ aingĩ nĩmarutĩte ũira wa maheeni.</para>
  <para style="p">Thuutha-inĩ andũ eerĩ makĩrũgama, <verse number="61" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:61 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 2:19">Joh 2:19</ref></char></note>makiuga atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ nĩoigire atĩrĩ, ‘No hote gũtharia hekarũ ya Ngai, na ndĩmĩake rĩngĩ na mĩthenya ĩtatũ.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v"/>Ningĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene akĩrũgama, akĩũria Jesũ atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ wee ũtarĩ na ũndũ ũgũtũcookeria? Nĩ ũhoro ũrĩkũ ũyũ ũrathitangĩrwo?” <verse number="63" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:63 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 5:1">Alaw 5:1</ref></char></note>No Jesũ agĩkira ki.</para>
  <para style="p">Mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ndakwĩhĩtithia na Ngai ũrĩa wĩ muoyo: Twĩre kana wee nĩwe Kristũ, Mũrũ wa Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="64" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:64 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:11">Math 27:11</ref>; <ref loc="REV 1:7">Kũg 1:7</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ, wee nĩwoiga, no ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, inyuĩ inyuothe nĩmũkona Mũrũ wa Mũndũ aikarĩte guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo kwa Ũrĩa-ũrĩ-Hinya, agĩũka arĩ igũrũ rĩa matu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="65" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũcio mũnene agĩtembũranga nguo ciake, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩaruma Ngai! Tũgũkĩbatario nĩ aira angĩ aakĩ? Atĩrĩrĩ, inyuĩ nĩmweiguĩra akĩruma Ngai. <verse number="66" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:66 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 24:16">Alaw 24:16</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 19:7">Joh 19:7</ref></char></note>Mũgwĩciiria atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">Magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Aagĩrĩirwo nĩ kũũragwo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="67" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:67 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:21">Math 16:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Magĩcooka makĩmũtuĩra mata ũthiũ, na makĩmũhũũra na ngundi. Angĩ makĩmũhũũra na hĩ, <verse number="68" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:68 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 22:63-65">Luk 22:63-65</ref></char></note>makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Wee Kristũ, tũrathĩre ũhoro ũtwĩre, nũũ wakũgũtha!”</para>
  <para style="s1">Petero Gũkaana Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="69" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, Petero aikarĩte nja, nake mũirĩtu warĩ ndungata akĩmũkora, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “O nawe uuma hamwe na Jesũ ũcio wa Galili.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="70" style="v"/>Nowe agĩkaana ũhoro ũcio mbere yao othe, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndiũĩ ũrĩa ũroiga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="71" style="v"/>Ningĩ akiumagara, agĩthiĩ kĩhingo-inĩ, harĩa mũirĩtu ũngĩ aamuonire, akĩĩra andũ arĩa maarĩ hau atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ moima na Jesũ wa Nazarethi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="72" style="v"/>Agĩkaana ũhoro ũcio o rĩngĩ, na akĩĩhĩta, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndiũĩ mũndũ ũcio!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="73" style="v"/>Thuutha wa kahinda kanini, arĩa maarũgamĩte hau magĩthiĩ harĩ Petero, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ti-itherũ wee ũrĩ ũmwe wao, tondũ mwarĩrie waku nĩũrakumbũra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="74" style="v"/>Nake akĩambĩrĩria kwĩhĩta, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ mũndũ ũcio ndimũũĩ!”</para>
  <para style="p">Kahinda o kau ngũkũ ĩgĩkũga. <verse number="75" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">26:75 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:34">Math 26:34</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:38">Joh 13:38</ref></char></note>Nake Petero akĩririkana ũhoro ũrĩa Jesũ aamwĩrĩte atĩrĩ, “Ngũkũ ĩtanakũga, ũrĩkorwo ũngaanĩte maita matatũ.” Akiuma nja, akĩrĩra mũno.</para>
  <chapter number="27" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Judasi Kwĩita</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 15:1">Mar 15:1</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 22:66">Luk 22:66</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, rũciinĩ tene, athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene othe na athuuri a andũ makĩiguithania atĩ matuĩre Jesũ kũũragwo. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 20:19">Math 20:19</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 3:13">Atũm 3:13</ref></char></note>Makĩmuoha na mĩnyororo; makĩmũruta kũu, makĩmũtwara kũrĩ Pilato, ũrĩa warĩ barũthi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:14">Math 26:14</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 26:15">15</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Judasi, ũcio wamũkunyanĩire oonire atĩ Jesũ nĩatuĩrwo gũkua-rĩ, akĩĩrira na agĩcookeria athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na athuuri mbeeca icio cia betha mĩrongo ĩtatũ. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 27:24">Math 27:24</ref></char></note>Akiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩnjĩhĩtie, nĩgũkorwo nĩngunyanĩire thakame ĩtarĩ na mahĩtia.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makĩmũcookeria makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũcio ũkĩrĩ ũhoro witũ? Ũcio nĩ ũhoro waku.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 1:9">Luk 1:9</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 1:21">21</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 1:18">Atũm 1:18</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Judasi agĩikania mbeeca icio thĩinĩ wa hekarũ, agĩĩthiĩra. Agĩcooka agĩthiĩ akĩĩita.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Athĩnjĩri-Ngai acio anene makĩoya mbeeca icio makiuga atĩrĩ, “Kũiga mbeeca ici kĩgĩĩna-inĩ nĩ kuuna watho, nĩgũkorwo nĩ mbeeca cia thakame.” <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makĩiguithania mahũthĩre mbeeca icio na kũgũra gĩthaka kĩrĩa kĩa mũũmbi nyũngũ gĩtuĩke gĩa gũthikagwo ageni. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 1:19">Atũm 1:19</ref></char></note>Kĩu nĩkĩo gĩtũmaga gĩthaka kĩu gĩĩtwo Gĩthaka gĩa Thakame nginya ũmũthĩ. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩguo ũhoro ũrĩa waarĩtio nĩ Jeremia ũrĩa Mũnabii wahingire, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ: “Nao nĩmoire icunjĩ icio mĩrongo ĩtatũ cia betha, thogora ũrĩa andũ a Isiraeli maatuĩte wa kũmũgũra, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 11:12-13">Zek 11:12-13</ref></char></note>nao magĩcihũthĩra na kũgũra gĩthaka kĩa mũũmbi nyũngũ, o ta ũrĩa Mwathani aanjathire gwĩkwo.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Mbere ya Pilato</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 2:2">Math 2:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, Jesũ akĩrũgama mbere ya barũthi, nake barũthi ũcio akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee nĩwe Mũthamaki wa Ayahudi?”</para>
  <para style="p">Jesũ agĩcookia atĩrĩ. “Ĩĩ, wee nĩwoiga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa aathitangirwo nĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na athuuri, ndarĩ ũndũ aacookirie. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:62">Math 26:62</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Pilato akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ ũtaraigua ũira wa maũndũ marĩa maragũthitangĩra?” <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nowe Jesũ ndaigana gũcookia ũndũ o na ũmwe wa macio; nake barũthi akĩgega mũno.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 18:39">Joh 18:39</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ya Gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka, barũthi ũcio nĩamenyerete kuohora mũndũ ũmwe wa arĩa oohe, o ũrĩa kĩrĩndĩ kĩngĩathuurire. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩ maarĩ na mũndũ kĩmaramari wohetwo na woĩkaine mũno, wetagwo Baraba. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa kĩrĩndĩ kĩagomanire, Pilato agĩkĩũria atĩrĩ, “Nũũ mũkwenda ndĩmuohorere; nĩ Baraba, kana nĩ Jesũ ũrĩa wĩtagwo Kristũ?” <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo we nĩamenyaga atĩ maatwarĩte Jesũ kũrĩ we nĩ ũndũ wa ũiru.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 19:13">Joh 19:13</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:24">Math 27:24</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 20:6">Kĩam 20:6</ref></char>
    </note>Na hĩndĩ ĩyo Pilato aikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩa ciira, mũtumia wake akĩmũtũmĩra mũndũ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: “Ndũkae gwĩka mũndũ ũcio ũndũ tondũ ndarĩ na mahĩtia, nĩgũkorwo ũmũthĩ nĩthĩĩnĩtio nĩ kĩroto mũno nĩ ũndũ wake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 3:14">Atũm 3:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na athuuri makĩringĩrĩria kĩrĩndĩ gĩĩtie Baraba, nake Jesũ ooragwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Barũthi ũcio akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Andũ aya eerĩ nĩ ũrĩkũ mũkwenda ndĩmuohorere?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makiuga atĩrĩ, “Tũkwenda Baraba.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 1:16">Math 1:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Pilato akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Ngũgĩĩka atĩa na Jesũ ũyũ wĩtagwo Kristũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Othe magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Mwambe mũtĩ-igũrũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Nake Pilato akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nĩkĩ? Nĩ ngero ĩrĩkũ agerete?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao magĩkĩrĩrĩria kwanĩrĩra, makiugaga atĩrĩ, “Mwambe mũtĩ-igũrũ!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:5">Math 26:5</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 21:6-8">Gũcook 21:6-8</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Pilato oonire atĩ matiraiguithania, na akĩona atĩ nĩ ngũĩ yambagĩrĩria-rĩ, akĩoya maaĩ, agĩĩthamba moko hau mbere ya kĩrĩndĩ, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndikoorio thakame ya mũndũ ũyũ ũtarĩ na mahĩtia. Ũcio nĩ ũhoro wanyu!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOS 2:19">Josh 2:19</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 5:28">Atũm 5:28</ref></char>
    </note>Nao andũ acio othe magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Thakame yake ĩrotũcookerera hamwe na ciana ciitũ!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 53:5">Isa 53:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Pilato akĩmohorera Baraba. No akĩhũũrithia Jesũ iboko, agĩcooka akĩmũneana akaambwo mũtĩ-igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Thigari Kũnyũrũria Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Ningĩ thigari cia barũthi cigĩtwara Jesũ thĩinĩ wa gĩikaro kĩa barũthi, nacio cigĩcookanĩrĩria mbũtũ yothe ya thigari, cikĩmũrigiicĩria. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Cikĩmũruta nguo ciake, cikĩmũhumba nguo ndune, <verse number="29" style="v"/>cigĩcooka cigĩtuma thũmbĩ ya mĩigua, cikĩmwĩkĩra mũtwe. Cikĩmũnengera kamũrangi guoko-inĩ gwake kwa ũrĩo, cikĩmũturĩria ndu, na cikĩmũnyũrũria, cikiuga atĩrĩ, “Wĩ mũhoro, mũthamaki wa Ayahudi!” <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:21">Math 16:21</ref></char></note>Cikĩmũtuĩra mata, cikĩoya kamũrangi kau, na cikĩmũhũũra nako mũtwe. <verse number="31" style="v"/>Ciarĩkia kũmũnyũrũria, cikĩmũruta nguo ĩyo, na cikĩmũhumba nguo ciake mwene. Cigĩcooka cikĩmumagaria cikamwambe mũtĩ-igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kwambwo kwa Jesũ Mũtĩ-Igũrũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 13:12">Ahib 13:12</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 2:10">Atũm 2:10</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 15:21">Mar 15:21</ref></char>
    </note>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa moimagaraga-rĩ, magĩcemania na mũndũ woimĩte Kurene, wetagwo Simoni, nacio thigari cikĩmũkuuithia mũtharaba ũcio na hinya. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 19:17">Joh 19:17</ref></char></note>Magĩthiĩ, magĩkinya handũ heetagwo Gologotha (ũguo nĩ kuuga Handũ hahaana ta Ihĩndĩ rĩa Mũtwe). <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 69:21">Thab 69:21</ref></char></note>Nacio cikĩhe Jesũ ndibei anyue, ĩtukanĩtio na kĩndũ kĩrũrũ ta maaĩ ma nyongo; no aamĩcama akĩrega kũmĩnyua. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 22:18">Thab 22:18</ref></char></note>Ciarĩkia kũmwamba mũtĩ-igũrũ, cikĩgayana nguo ciake na njĩra ya gũcicuukĩra mĩtĩ. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 27:54">Math 27:54</ref></char></note>Nacio cigĩikara thĩ hau, cikĩmũrangĩra. <verse number="37" style="v"/>Na hau igũrũ rĩa mũtwe wake, nĩhandĩkĩtwo maũndũ marĩa aathitangĩirwo, atĩrĩ: ŨYŨ NĨWE JESŨ, MŨTHAMAKI WA AYAHUDI. <verse number="38" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, atunyani eerĩ nĩmambirwo mĩtĩ-igũrũ hamwe nake, ũmwe mwena wake wa ũrĩo, na ũcio ũngĩ mwena wake wa ũmotho. <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 22:7">Thab 22:7</ref></char></note>Nao andũ arĩa maahĩtũkagĩra hau makamũrumaga, makĩinagia mĩtwe yao, <verse number="40" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:40 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 2:19">Joh 2:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:3">Math 4:3</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 4:6">6</ref></char></note>makiugaga atĩrĩ, “Wee ũngĩratharirie hekarũ na ũcooke ũmĩake na mĩthenya ĩtatũ-rĩ, kĩĩhonokie! Harũrũka uume mũtharaba-inĩ, aakorwo wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>O ũndũ ũmwe athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene, na arutani a watho, na athuuri o nao makĩmũnyũrũria. <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:49">Joh 1:49</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:15">Joh 3:15</ref></char></note>Makiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩarahonokagia andũ arĩa angĩ, no ndangĩhota kwĩhonokia we mwene! Nĩwe Mũthamaki wa Isiraeli! Nĩakiume rĩu mũtharaba-inĩ, na ithuĩ nĩtũkũmwĩtĩkia. <verse number="43" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:43 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 22:8">Thab 22:8</ref></char></note>Nĩehokete Ngai, nĩakĩmũhonokie rĩu aakorwo nĩamwendete, nĩgũkorwo oigire atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ ndĩ Mũrũ wa Ngai.’ ” <verse number="44" style="v"/>O na atunyani arĩa maambanĩirio hamwe nake o nao makĩmũruma.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũkua kwa Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:45 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="AMO 8:9">Amos 8:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, kuuma thaa thita cia mũthenya nginya thaa kenda bũrũri wothe ũkĩgĩa nduma. <verse number="46" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:46 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 22:1">Thab 22:1</ref></char></note>Na ta thaa kenda Jesũ akĩgũthũka na mũgambo mũnene, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Eli, Eli, lama sabakithani?” (Ũguo nĩ kuuga, “Ngai wakwa, Ngai wakwa, ũndiganĩirie nĩkĩ?”)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v"/>Nao andũ amwe a arĩa maarũngiĩ hau rĩrĩa maiguire ũguo, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Areeta Elija.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:48 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 69:21">Thab 69:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na o rĩmwe, ũmwe wao agĩtengʼera akĩoya thibũnji. Akĩmĩtobokia thiki-inĩ, akĩmĩthecerera kamũrangi-inĩ, akĩhe Jesũ anyue. <verse number="49" style="v"/>Arĩa angĩ nao makiuga atĩrĩ, “Tiganai nake. Nĩtũkuona kana Elija nĩegũũka kũmũhonokia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩgũthũka rĩngĩ na mũgambo mũnene, agĩtuĩkana.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:51 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 26:31-33">Thaam 26:31-33</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ihinda o rĩu gĩtambaya kĩa hekarũ gĩgĩatũkana icunjĩ igĩrĩ kuuma igũrũ nginya thĩ. Nayo thĩ ĩgĩthingitha, nacio ndwaro cia mahiga igĩatũkana. <verse number="52" style="v"/>Mbĩrĩra nacio ikĩhingũka, nao andũ aingĩ arĩa atheru arĩa maarĩkĩtie gũkua makĩriũka, <verse number="53" style="v"/>makiuma thĩinĩ wa mbĩrĩra. Na thuutha wa kũriũka kwa Jesũ, magĩthiĩ itũũra rĩu inene itheru, na makiumĩrĩra andũ aingĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:54 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:36">Math 27:36</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:3">Math 4:3</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa mũnene-wa-thigari-igana na arĩa maarĩ nake makĩrangĩra Jesũ moonire gĩthingithia na maũndũ mothe marĩa meekĩkire-rĩ, makĩnyiitwo nĩ guoya, makĩanĩrĩra, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Ti-itherũ mũndũ ũyũ oima Mũrũ wa Ngai!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:55 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 8:2">Luk 8:2</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 8:3">3</ref></char>
    </note>Na nĩ haarĩ andũ-a-nja aingĩ meeroragĩra marĩ o haraaya. Maarũmĩrĩire Jesũ kuuma Galili nĩguo mamũtungatagĩre. <verse number="56" style="v"/>Thĩinĩ wao haarĩ Mariamu Mũmagidali, na Mariamu ũrĩa nyina wa Jakubu na Jose, na nyina wa ariũ a Zebedi.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũthikwo kwa Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v"/>Na hwaĩ-inĩ wakinya-rĩ, mũndũ warĩ gĩtonga wa kuuma Arimathea, wetagwo Jusufu, ũrĩa watuĩkĩte mũrutwo wa Jesũ agĩũka. <verse number="58" style="v"/>Nake agĩthiĩ kũrĩ Pilato, na akĩhooya aheo mwĩrĩ wa Jesũ, nake Pilato agĩathana anengerwo mwĩrĩ ũcio. <verse number="59" style="v"/>Jusufu akĩoya mwĩrĩ ũcio, akĩwoha na taama mũtheru wa gatani, <verse number="60" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:60 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 16:4">Mar 16:4</ref></char></note>akĩũiga thĩinĩ wa mbĩrĩra yake njerũ ĩrĩa eenjithĩtie rwaro-inĩ rwa ihiga. Akĩgaragaria ihiga inene mũromo-inĩ wa mbĩrĩra ĩyo, na agĩĩthiĩra. <verse number="61" style="v"/>Mariamu Mũmagidali na Mariamu ũcio ũngĩ maikarĩte hau mangʼetheire mbĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Arangĩri Mbĩrĩra-inĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v"/>Na mũthenya ũyũ ũngĩ ũrĩa ũrũmagĩrĩra Mũthenya wa Ihaarĩria, athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na Afarisai magĩthiĩ kwa Pilato. <verse number="63" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:63 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:21">Math 16:21</ref></char></note>Makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathi witũ, nĩtũkũririkana atĩ rĩrĩa mũheenania ũcio aarĩ muoyo. nĩoigire atĩrĩ, ‘Thuutha wa matukũ matatũ nĩngariũka.’ <verse number="64" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ruta watho nĩguo mbĩrĩra ĩyo ĩrangĩrwo nginya mũthenya wa gatatũ. Kwaga ũguo, arutwo ake maahota gũthiĩ maiye mwĩrĩ ũcio macooke meere andũ atĩ nĩariũkĩtio kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ. Maheeni macio maahota gũtuĩka mooru gũkĩra marĩa ma mbere.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="65" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:65 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 28:11">Math 28:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Pilato akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Oyai arangĩri, mũthiĩ mũrangĩre mbĩrĩra ĩyo wega o ta ũrĩa mũngĩhota.” <verse number="66" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">27:66 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DAN 6:17">Dan 6:17</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 28:11">Math 28:11</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio magĩthiĩ, makĩhinga ihiga rĩa mbĩrĩra ĩyo biũ, na makĩrĩĩkĩra rũũri rwa mũhũra, na makĩiga arangĩri ho.</para>
  <chapter number="28" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">1 Kũriũka kwa Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:56">Math 27:56</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thuutha wa Thabatũ, gwatua gũkĩa mũthenya wa mbere wa kiumia, Mariamu Mũmagidali na Mariamu ũcio ũngĩ magĩthiĩ kũrora mbĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:51">Math 27:51</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 5:19">Atũm 5:19</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, nĩ kwagĩire na gĩthingithia kĩnene, nĩgũkorwo mũraika wa Mwathani nĩaikũrũkire oimĩte igũrũ na agĩthiĩ mbĩrĩra-inĩ, akĩgaragaria ihiga akĩrĩeheria na akĩrĩikarĩra. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DAN 10:6">Dan 10:6</ref></char></note>Oonekaga ahaana ta rũheni, na nguo ciake cierũhĩte o ta ira. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nao arangĩri acio makĩmwĩtigĩra mũno nginya makĩinaina makĩhaana, ta andũ akuũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nake mũraika ũcio akĩĩra andũ-a-nja acio atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ-rĩ, tigai gwĩtigĩra, nĩgũkorwo nĩnjũũĩ atĩ nĩ Jesũ ũrĩa ũraambirwo mũtĩ-igũrũ mũracaria. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:21">Math 16:21</ref></char></note>Ndarĩ haha, nĩariũkĩte, o ta ũrĩa oigire. Ũkai muone harĩa arakomete. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:32">Math 26:32</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, thiĩi narua mũkeere arutwo ake atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩariũkĩte akoima kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, na nĩegũthiĩ Galili mbere yanyu. Kũu nĩkuo mũrĩmuona.’ Ririkanai ũguo ndaamwĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, andũ-a-nja acio makiuma mbĩrĩra-inĩ mahiũhĩte marĩ na guoya, no ningĩ maiyũrĩtwo nĩ gĩkeno, makĩhanyũka makeere arutwo ake ũhoro ũcio. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 20:14-18">Joh 20:14-18</ref></char></note>Na o rĩmwe Jesũ agĩtũngana nao, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩndamũgeithia.” Nao magĩthiĩ harĩ we, makĩmũnyiita nyarĩrĩ, makĩmũhooya. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:29">Arom 8:29</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 2:11-13">Ahib 2:11-13</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 2:17">17</ref></char></note>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Tigai gwĩtigĩra. Thiĩ mũkeere ariũ na aarĩ a Baba mathiĩ Galili; kũu nĩkuo marĩnyona.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũhoro wa Arangĩri</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa andũ-a-nja acio maathiiaga-rĩ, arangĩri amwe a arĩa maarangĩrĩte mbĩrĩra magĩtoonya itũũra inene na makĩĩra athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene maũndũ mothe marĩa mekĩkĩte. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nao athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene magĩcemania na athuuri, magĩthugunda ũrĩa megwĩka; makĩhe thigari icio mbeeca nyingĩ, <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 27:64">Math 27:64</ref></char></note>magĩciĩra atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ mũkuuga atĩrĩ, ‘Arutwo ake marookire ũtukũ maramũiya twĩ toro.’ <verse number="14" style="v"/>Ũhoro ũyũ ũngĩkinyĩra barũthi, nĩtũkamũiguithia, na tũmũgitĩre mũtikone ũũru.” <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio thigari ikĩoya mbeeca icio, igĩĩka o ta ũrĩa cierĩtwo. Naguo ũhoro ũcio ũkĩhunjio kũrĩ Ayahudi, na nĩũhunjagio o nginya ũmũthĩ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũtũmwo Gũtungata</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 28:7">Math 28:7</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 28:10">10</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo arutwo arĩa ikũmi na ũmwe magĩthiĩ Galili, kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩrĩa Jesũ aamerĩte mathiĩ. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa maamuonire-rĩ, makĩmũhooya, no amwe maarĩ na nganja. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DAN 7:13">Dan 7:13</ref>, <ref loc="DAN 7:14">14</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:9">Afil 2:9</ref>, <ref loc="PHP 2:10">10</ref></char></note>Nake Jesũ agĩthiĩ kũrĩ o akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩheetwo ũhoti wothe igũrũ na gũkũ thĩ. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 16:15">Mar 16:15</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 16:16">16</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 1:8">Atũm 1:8</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio thiĩi mũgatũme andũ a ndũrĩrĩ ciothe matuĩke arutwo akwa, mũkĩmabatithagia thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Ithe na rĩa Mũriũ na rĩa Roho Mũtheru, <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">28:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:42">Atũm 2:42</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 8:57">1Ath 8:57</ref></char></note>na mũkĩmarutaga gwathĩkĩra maũndũ marĩa mothe ndĩmwathĩte. Na ti-itherũ ndĩ hamwe na inyuĩ hĩndĩ ciothe, o nginya mũthia wa mahinda maya.”</para>
</usx>
